\id GEN - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG Genesis 01 30/8/91 Macnaughtan
\h KINI PIEKE
\toc1 Alaęž‰taęž‰ Alaęž‰taęž‰ Paeyaonaęž‰ Kini Piekeekie
\toc2 Kini Pieke
\toc3 Kini Pieke
\mt1 Alaęž‰taęž‰ Alaęž‰taęž‰ Paeyaonaęž‰ Kini Piekeekie
\c 1
\s1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao wepiekeeki
\p 
\v 1-2 Titi panake paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kenke ya yaapo wepieke dinaęž‰ do kenketaęž‰ homeke hau hondaęž‰ lupa pua aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na wiekeme. Kutupa mo dawalataęž‰ timbaęž‰ kiti laęž‰pa peeke alenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitiditaęž‰ manda hayekeme.
\v 3 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ PaĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki winaęž‰e leeke handaataęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± piekeme.
\v 4 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kutu piekeeki handolo hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo mo timbaęž‰ alaęž‰eki pitaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo putupaalu pinaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 5 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Natee laataęž‰ timbaęž‰ alaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Timbae leekeme. Kotaęž‰ timbaęž‰ laa da kelepeeketaęž‰ titinaęž‰ nate yeekeme.
\p 
\v 6-7 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo ikalitaęž‰ putupaalu pinaęž‰ yeke dopu miaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handeke ale winaęž‰e leeke handaataęž‰ kutu piekeme. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do wieke alemaęž‰taęž‰ mo ikalitaęž‰ putupaęž‰alu pea manda make oto nane make winaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 8 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto dopu miaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handeke alenaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Yae leekeme. Kotaęž‰ timbaęž‰ laa da kelepeeketaęž‰ yaapo peao nate yeekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ mo ya oto nane ulaęž‰ ikali paęž‰taęž‰ yu peneme yao opaęž‰liao winaęž‰ yeke mo ikalitaęž‰ homeke alenaęž‰ mombelenaęž‰e laa leeke handaataęž‰ kutu piekeme.
\v 10 Kutupa mo yunaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Kenkee laa mo homeke alenaęž‰ mombeleeke ikalinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Dawalae leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ moeki hando haotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do kenkemaęž‰taęž‰ mo kenkenaęž‰ opaęž‰laęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki ti potekemanu make kiliki aęž‰etaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu make opaenaęž‰e laa leeke handaataęž‰ kutu piekeme.
\v 12 Kenkemaęž‰ kutu piekeeki hando haotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 13 Timbaęž‰ laa da kelepeeketaęž‰ tepo peao nate yeekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo nate pitaęž‰ timbaęž‰ alaęž‰eki yaapo putupaęž‰alu pinaęž‰ yeke oli ya nane paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu winaęž‰e laataęž‰ koto paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo natemanu make bapimanu make ne pambaęž‰laęž‰eki manunaęž‰ dimanu kini peaenaęž‰ yeke winaęž‰e laa leekeme.
\v 15 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke paĚ±aĚ± pealuekemaęž‰ oli ya nanemaęž‰ hataęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pilieke laa leeke handaa kutu piekeme.
\v 16 Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tieke yaapo wepiekeme. Mo natemaęž‰taęž‰ natepa handeteke haenaęž‰ make mo kaisepomaęž‰taęž‰ timba handeteke haenaęž‰ piekeme. Kutupa hombulankaęž‰manu make wepiekeme.
\v 17 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo kenkenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaenaęž‰ yeke oli ya nane haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 18 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo natepa pitaęž‰ timba yaapo handeteke haenaęž‰ make paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ timbaęž‰ alaęž‰eki yaapo putupaęž‰alu pinaęž‰ yeke piekeme. Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kotoeki hando haotaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 19 Timbaęž‰ laa da kelepeeketaęž‰ tonko peao nate yeekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo ikali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pa pitiki ale manumaęž‰ tumbinaęž‰e laataęž‰ yanaęž‰taęž‰ ba titimaęž‰ tumbinaęž‰e laa leekeme.
\v 21 Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo dawalanaęž‰ pilaęž‰ si tieke hombelekemanu make oni ikali paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki pa pitiki alemanu make taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki bamanu make wepiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo alemanu hando haotaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 22 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiaasaęž‰ pimaęž‰ mo ikali paęž‰taęž‰ pilimi pa pitiki alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo dawala paęž‰taęž‰ sembelomenaęž‰ pa mendiolo ombu hapaęž‰peke laataęž‰ mo bamanu paęž‰taęž‰ make alotaęž‰ Wopu yomenaęž‰ pa mendiolo ombu hapaęž‰peke laa leekeme.
\v 23 Timbaęž‰ laa da kelepeeketaęž‰ yunki peao nate yeekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo kenke paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki ponaęž‰laęž‰ hotekemanu make tikene halaęž‰ hotekemanu make tieke make hosikale sunu make haenaęž‰e laa leeke handaa kutu piekeme.
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto alemanu paeyao wepiakaęž‰naęž‰ mo alemanu hando haotaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\p 
\v 26 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ ametaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimanu wepumanaęž‰e laa leekeme. Ikitaęž‰ nikimaęž‰ handaa nikaęž‰ hau hondenaęž‰e laa leekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo taęž‰pelimanu make bamanu make ponaęž‰laęž‰ hotekemanu make tikene halaęž‰ hotekemanu make tieke make hosikale sunu make paeya tapaotaęž‰ kilu tombuao haenaęž‰e laa leekeme.
\v 27 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ipikimaęž‰ kone handenaęž‰ wepiekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hali tapake pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰ tapake yaapo wepiekeme.
\v 28 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiliki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiaasaęž‰ pimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipilikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ do kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao kilu tombuao haenaęž‰ yeke wekiwandiki wopu mendiaęž‰paęž‰peke laa leekeme. IĚ±maęž‰ ipilikitaęž‰ mo taęž‰pelimanu make bamanu make tikene halaęž‰ hotekemanu make handeteke hapenaęž‰ yeke alome leekeme.
\v 29 Kutupa ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ nopenaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ mo taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki konimaęž‰ handeke kilikimanu make taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki ti potekemanu make amu pea wepia winaęž‰ lolome leekeme.
\v 30 Pate mo tikene halaęž‰ hoteke manumaęž‰ make ba manumaęž‰ make nenaęž‰taęž‰ mo ambumanu make katake hake timanu wepia winaęž‰ laalome leeke handaataęž‰ kutu piekeme.
\v 31 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ wepia winaęž‰ leeke alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao handolo hataęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ wopu homeekeme. Kotaęž‰ timbaęž‰ laa da kelepeeketaęž‰ yunki mindiki peao nate yeekeme.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Kutupa kotaęž‰ mo kenke nane ulaęž‰ alemanu make oli ya nane halaęž‰ alemanu make paeyao wepu paeyaeyekeme.
\v 2 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ pokaęž‰tia epeeke etaęž‰ poko paeyao mo wataake natenaęž‰taęž‰ e na pokeke hoto pitiekeme.
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wataake peao natetaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiaasaęž‰ pimaęž‰ Taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ piki natee laa tombo winaęž‰ leekeme. Pa ekipeke koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao weputia aęž‰pa e pokaęž‰laęž‰eki minaęž‰paęž‰laeyeke natee.
\v 4 Mo kenke ya yaapo make mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao wepieke tupaęž‰taęž‰ kotoe.
\s1 Mo Ideni E
\p 
\v 5 Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo kenke ya yaapo wepia dinaęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ lako na tapaeyekeeki yalo make yu lu wiaęž‰peke wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yeke ekimaęž‰ do kenkemaęž‰taęž‰ wae alemanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ na hao make kilikimanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ na opeekeme.
\v 6 Pate mo kenke oto nane wieke ikalimaęž‰taęž‰ opaęž‰liao mo kenke tenke latiki piekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Kutupa mo Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ dokolo mea hali au laa wepiataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mineke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki halaęž‰laęž‰ pomo po lo pambeeke handaataęž‰ mo halitaęž‰ tiao daęž‰taa hayekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Kutupa mo Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nane wieke Ideni kenke paęž‰taęž‰ e pokaataęž‰ mo hande wepieke hali koto e paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 9 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto e paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki epeke au leke timanu opaotaęž‰ epeke ti potekemanu eiyaeyekeme. Koto e tukikinaęž‰taęž‰ mo daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kitaęž‰laęž‰ ti make mo epeke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki yaaponaęž‰ hone u tiaasaęž‰ ti make hayekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Mo Ideni e paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ yopulu halaęž‰ ikali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo e ikali halo hayekeme. Mo ikalitaęž‰ Ideni mo pate leketaęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ tonkopu piekeme.
\v 11 Mo titinaęž‰ ikalitaęž‰ Pisoni ikalie. Ipikitaęž‰ mo Haęž‰pila kenke popei yao yapeekeme.
\v 12 Mo alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taĚ±leke kolo make totopo piki wetaęž‰ make seliapo piki toopimanu make koto paęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 13 Mo yaapo peao ikalitaęž‰ Kioni ikalie. Ipikitaęž‰ mo Kusu kenke popei yao yapeekeme.
\v 14 Mo tepo peao ikalitaęž‰ Taikitisi ikalie. Ipikitaęž‰ mo Aęž‰sitia kenkenaęž‰ nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nanemaęž‰ yapeekeme. Kutupa mo tonko peao ikalitaęž‰ Yupoteitisi ikalie.
\p 
\v 15 Kutupa Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande halitaęž‰ Ideni e paęž‰taęž‰ yu lia handeteke haenaęž‰yeke hawayekeme.
\v 16 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo enaęž‰ halaęž‰ ti poteke paeyaotaęž‰ napeke yaęž‰laęž‰patetaęž‰
\v 17 mo epeke hau pitaęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki yaaponaęž‰ hone u tiaasaęž‰ ti poteke homeke homeke diaęž‰me. Mo koto tinaęž‰ poteketaęž‰ otaęž‰ na napeke laataęž‰ Nekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo nelipi natenaęž‰ kone homilipikie laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Kutupa mo Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hali ipikaęž‰ siki hataęž‰taęž‰ hoelaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki tambaęž‰ minaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke taęž‰maęž‰ni maęž‰ndaęž‰ wepulueke laa leekeme.
\v 19 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mandane dokolomanu mea hoteke paeyao make ba paeyao make wepiekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo alemanu mo halimaęž‰ handaa biki lomaęž‰ lomaęž‰ pinaęž‰ yeke hatuku epeekeme. Kototaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hande biki mimiki tupaęž‰e.
\v 20 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo bamanu paeyao make hotekemanu paeyao make biki hale hale piekeme. Pate koto ale manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo ipiki tambaęž‰ meaęž‰peke taęž‰maęž‰ni maęž‰ndaęž‰ na hayekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hali uĚ± yokaęž‰lupa penaęž‰ leekeme. Kutupa u pelia haenaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰liki homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipilaęž‰ mea mo loke aęž‰mbaeyekeme.
\v 22 Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰likimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ wepia mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epeekeme.
\v 23 Kutu pieke mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ wetepe siki nane IĚ±maęž‰ handeke yankeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ doe. Ipikaęž‰ holikitaęž‰ yaka holiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ kone mea ipikaęž‰ loketaęž‰ yaka loke paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ kone maęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ kone miekeeki yalo hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ wandaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 24 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni peaataęž‰ ipilikitaęž‰ homeke kone halepeme.
\p 
\v 25 Mo hali pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapotaęž‰ pa tia haepekepate kone ipilikitaęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ na homepekeme.
\c 3
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi tunkuliekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wepieke hotekemanu paeyao tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ keto homeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ hone wopu u lenkene piki hoteke wepiekeme. Koto ketomaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ do e paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ ti maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ poteke na napaęž‰peke laa otaęž‰ leaęž‰pe laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 2 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Dikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do e paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ ti poteke paeyao nolo polopaęž‰patetaęž‰
\v 3 mo e tukikinaęž‰ halaęž‰eki homeke homeke diaęž‰me laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ diki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto ti poteke homeke otaęž‰ na napaęž‰peke make otaęž‰ na wataapaęž‰peke. Kutu pipikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ homilipipikie laa leaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Mo ketomaęž‰ pi lu moneaaso alotaęž‰ Kototaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi diaęž‰me. Ipiliki na homilipipikie.
\v 5 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto leke hautaęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto ti poteke nepekenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikimaęž‰ kone handaa mo epeke hau pitaęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hone u tiaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone wilipipiki yeke handa leaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ mo ti handeeketaęž‰ au epeke laa mo ti poteke nalotaęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa handeekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ hone wopu u lenkene pitolotaęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me hone wiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo mandane ti potekemanu mea neekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mandane ekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliki haleeketaęž‰ halikimaęž‰ make neekeme.
\v 7 Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ti poteke nepe ale paęž‰taęž‰ konetaęž‰ hone u tiaasaęž‰eki halaa ipilikitaęž‰ pa tia hataęž‰ pupaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me hone wipikime. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ nose katake tombula ipiliki loke aęž‰mbaepekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Koto nate pambolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Tekehali Kodaęž‰taęž‰ e paęž‰taęž‰ pomiaęž‰eki opitolo hataęž‰ ipiki aęž‰mbao oni ti polu paęž‰taęž‰manu panko pitipikime.
\v 9 Pate Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ wi laęž‰moneaaso alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ halepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Mo halimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke oni e paęž‰taęž‰ pomieki opu hao IĚ± pa tia haowaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ paalaęž‰ pieke neke aęž‰mbao panko pilume leekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Koto leeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ pa tia haleme laataęž‰ Epimaęž‰ la kiaęž‰pe. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo IĚ±maęž‰ na napeke loaęž‰ ti poteketaęž‰ nepee leekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Mo halimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do hande IĚ± yaapo hapono lele wandaęž‰maęž‰ mo ti poteke mea kieke handa noaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Mo Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do ekitaęž‰ ekipeke pea pelepe leekeme. Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ nono yeke handa mo ketomaęž‰ IĚ± makeayaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Hoke Yenki Haleekeeki
\p 
\v 14 Kutupa mo Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo keto paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hau pele ekinaęž‰ hoke yenki kitolome. Mo hoteke manumaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa neke homeke homekemaęž‰taęž‰ dupiki esihou pi mie. Neketaęž‰ ame do kini pea pulutaęž‰ nakaęž‰ weleketaęž‰ yolaęž‰ tia pominolo hataęž‰ neke pa ha pelia haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ dokolo no halipikie.
\v 15 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ neketaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkulaęž‰ alu peao ipikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ piliaęž‰ wekiwandikimaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkulaęž‰ alu alu pu haenaęž‰ lolueke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ you daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ tombuaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ anke kinuku handulu nelipikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neketaęž‰ nakaęž‰ weki loke lombilipi ale paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki hakaęž‰taęž‰peao make weki milipi ale paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ tanda paęž‰laęž‰eki make hakaęž‰taęž‰palueke. Dupinaęž‰ kone nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ haliki hone wopu wia ipiki oto paęž‰taęž‰ halipikie.
\p 
\v 17 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ pi opua mo IĚ±maęž‰ na napeke loaęž‰ ti poteke neleme. Koto hau pele ekinaęž‰ do kenketaęž‰ mo esihou pi oto paęž‰taęž‰ wilieke. Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ pa hapaęž‰lia haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo kenkemaęž‰ nakaęž‰ ne anaęž‰naęž‰ opaenaęž‰ e honkopu hao poko halipikie.
\v 18 Mo kenkenaęž‰taęž‰ ambumanu make tekeke hake alemanu make opaęž‰tiki pilieke. Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hapekenaęž‰ halaęž‰ wae alemanu no halipikie.
\v 19 Kutupa mo kenkemaęž‰ anemone ale openaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰li mendia honkopu hao e pokaęž‰tiki pilipikie. Dupiki hau putia pua mo neke waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ kenke paęž‰taęž‰ pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lalipikie. Neketaęž‰ dokolomaęž‰ wepiekeeki yalo hataęž‰ dokolo au kone lelipikie.
\p 
\v 20 Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Ipaęž‰ leekeme. Pa ekipeke ipikitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ inkikie.
\v 21 Kutupa mo Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hoteke manunaęž‰ yonkeleke mea akaęž‰ wepiaokaęž‰naęž‰ mo toolinaęž‰ yamaeyekeme.
\s1 Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰ Ipaęž‰ yaapo tolu liekeeki
\p 
\v 22 Kutupa mo Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ mo halitaęž‰ niki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondomaęž‰ handaataęž‰ mo epeke hau pitaęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo hone ulaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ pa hatia puaamaęž‰naęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰ tinaęž‰ poteke naamaęž‰naęž‰ waleke na halomanaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 23 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo halitaęž‰ Ideni e paęž‰taęž‰ tolu lia ipiki wepiaęž‰ kenke kone yu linaęž‰ haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo enaęž‰ nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nanetaęž‰ mandane honkopu hake enisolomanu haenaęž‰ laa make kutupa ti talo talo hake bainasi homeke mandane mandane lekeleke alo hakeeki haenaęž‰ leekeme. Do hau piki hautaęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰ ti teke paęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰paamaęž‰naęž‰ piekeme.
\c 4
\s1 Keini pitaęž‰ Eipolo yaapo
\p 
\v 1 Kutupa Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weteke yaapo loke apaęž‰tao mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ weki loke lombeekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ weki mendia alotaęž‰ Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ do weki mondolomaęž‰ laa mo wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Keinie leekeme.
\v 2 Pa hoki nanetaęž‰ weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Eipolo mondu wiekeme. Eipolotaęž‰ sipisipi handeteke hayekepate Keinitaęž‰ e hali hayekeme.
\v 3 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Keini ipikaęž‰ mandane ne napeke mea aęž‰pa Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke haleekeme.
\v 4 Kutupa Eipolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ sipisipimaęž‰ titinaęž‰ mendieke ikikitaęž‰ lia mo epeke mindiki manutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke haleekeme. Mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolomaęž‰ pa hameke haleeke ekinaęž‰ make ipiki yaapo taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 5 Kutu piekepate Keininaęž‰ pa hameke haleeke ekitaęž‰ kiayekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Keinitaęž‰ wenoko homaęž‰niao mineke wopu pankeekeme.
\v 6 Kutu pieke mo Tekehali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Keini lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ ekipeke mineke pankelepe laa Nakaęž‰ leke popeleketaęž‰ ekipeke homaęž‰nialepe.
\v 7 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pikaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ nakaęž‰ leke popeleke kipa baalo piaęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hoke hau pele ekimaęž‰taęž‰ hoke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ yu pamba halaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ neke dipula muluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ bepolapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Kutupa Keinimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kame Eipolo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Oni e paęž‰taęž‰ panaęž‰ epoe leekeme. Kutupa mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ oni enaęž‰ pua haepe dinaęž‰taęž‰ Keinimaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ moneao ipikaęž‰ hameke siki kone homenaęž‰ liekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ Keini lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kame Eipolotaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰pe leekeme. Koto leeke Keinimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ± mataęž‰laęž‰me. Yaka kametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ handeteke hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Koto leeke mo Tekehalimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipeke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ do hoke hau pea pelepe laataęž‰ Mo hoke hautaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ panisi peae laa nakaęž‰ kamenaęž‰ wemaęž‰taęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ leke oni kenkenaęž‰ hataęž‰ IĚ± wi alaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 11 Neketaęž‰ mo esihou pi oto paęž‰taęž‰ haleeki yalotaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ e otaęž‰ pa na pokilipikie laataęž‰ Pa ekipeke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ kame lilipi natenaęž‰ kone mo kenkemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ we dodopo lo noluekemaęž‰ kake alaęž‰pelia hake nono piaęž‰me.
\v 12 Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ e waemanu nokepekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ne napeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ na halieke. Kutupa neketaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ da teke diaęž‰ yalo hataęž‰ pomu lopaęž‰laęž‰ hali halipikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Koto leeke Keinimaęž‰ mo Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do kaęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mea tiaęž‰peketaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰
\v 14 kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± do kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao pono make nakaęž‰ leke tononaęž‰ na hake hano leke tolu liteleme. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ da teke diaęž‰yeke some hataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ IĚ± handaęž‰ wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± lilieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Koto leekepate mo Tekehalimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ neke liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto somenaęž‰ hoke yenkitaęž‰ wataake hataęž‰ peao hakaęž‰taęž‰pao homenaęž‰ lilieke leekeme. Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ mo Keini mandaęž‰hande piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ na linaęž‰e alo hataęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ mo somenaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ patehau maęž‰ndaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 16 Kutu pieke handaa Keinitaęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ tononaęž‰ na hake pao mo Ideni enaęž‰ nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nane mo Pominaęž‰laęž‰eki leeke kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua hayekeme.
\s1 Keininaęž‰ tapake
\p 
\v 17 Keini pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapomaęž‰ weki mondu wia bikitaęž‰ Inoko lepekeme. Kutupa Keinimaęž‰ daoni maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰eyaataęž‰ eiyekenaęž‰ biki taapaęž‰ tiao biki leekeme.
\v 18 Wetepenaęž‰ Inokomaęž‰taęž‰ biki Itado leke weki homeke mondu wiekeme. Itadotaęž‰ Mehudieilinaęž‰ ateke yekeme. Kutupa Mehudieilimaęž‰taęž‰ biki Meduseili leke weki mondu wiekeme. Meduseilitaęž‰ Laęž‰mekenaęž‰ ateke yekeme.
\v 19 Laęž‰mekemaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo Ada pitaęž‰ Sila yaapo miekeme.
\v 20 Adamaęž‰taęž‰ Dieibolo mondu wiekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ mo palai da paęž‰taęž‰manu hataęž‰ hotekemanu punieke ekinaęž‰ peayeke apaęž‰meinaęž‰ kini pieke hali hayekeme.
\v 21 Ipikaęž‰ hameketaęž‰ Diubolo yekeme. Koto sometaęž‰ mo hande kidamaęž‰ handeke ale pitaęž‰ puoĚ±loĚ± yaapo limiki tapakenaęž‰ kini peayeke hali hayekeme.
\v 22 Silamaęž‰taęž‰ weki Tubali Keini mondu wiekeme. Mo wekimaęž‰taęž‰ kopamaęž‰ handeke ale botonisi pitaęž‰ aeyaęž‰ni yaapomaęž‰ mo taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki kaiya sipeidimanu kini pea wepiekeme. Ipikaęž‰ belikitaęž‰ Nahama yekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Laęž‰mekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weteke yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Ada pitaęž‰ Sila yaapoo. Yaka pi opuaęž‰pe.
\q1 Mo panake hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± yombieke handaa IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki luaęž‰me.
\v 24 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Keini litaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ watake hataęž‰ haliweki homolo piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ IĚ± liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ tombotaęž‰ mo 77 haliwekitaęž‰ IĚ± lilaęž‰eki yenkinaęž‰ homilimikie leekeme.
\s1 Sedi pitaęž‰ Inosi yaapo
\p 
\v 25 Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰ weteke yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ mondu wipikime. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Keinimaęž‰ liaęž‰ weki Eipolonaęž‰ anketeke minaęž‰ yeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Sedie leekeme.
\v 26 Kutupa Sedimaęž‰taęž‰ biki Inosi leeke weki mondu wiekeme. Koto natenaęž‰ kini peaataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ yakopiki biki alo hataęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ lao haemekeme.
\c 5
\s1 Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ tapake
\p 
\v 1 Dotaęž‰ mo hande Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ tapakenaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ ekie. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hande wandaęž‰hali wepieke dinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikimaęž‰ kone handeke wandaęž‰hali wepitolotaęž‰
\v 2 hali pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo wepiekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo tooli taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaasaęž‰ pi laakaęž‰naęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halie laa wiekeme.
\v 3 Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bapi 130 mieketaęž‰ ipikimaęž‰ handeke weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ mondu wiaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Sedi leekeme.
\v 4 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ bapi 800 hayekeme. Koto bapi tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mandane wekiwandiki make mendiekeme.
\v 5 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ 930 bapinaęž‰taęž‰ homeekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Mo Sedi ipikaęž‰ bapi 105 yeketaęž‰ biki Inosi leeke weki mondu wiekeme.
\v 7 Kutupa bapi 807 tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mandane wekiwandiki make mondu wiaataęž‰
\v 8 ipikaęž‰ 912 bapinaęž‰taęž‰ homeekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Mo Inosi ipikaęž‰ bapi 90 yeketaęž‰ biki Kenana leeke weki mondu wiekeme.
\v 10 Kutupa bapi 815 tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mandane wekiwandiki make mondu wiaataęž‰
\v 11 mo 905 bapinaęž‰taęž‰ homeekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Mo Kenana ipikaęž‰ bapi 70 yeketaęž‰ Mahalale biki leeke weki mondu wiekeme.
\v 13 Kutupa bapi 840 tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mandane wekiwandiki make wopu mondu wiaataęž‰
\v 14 mo 910 bapinaęž‰taęž‰ homeekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Mo Mahalale bapi 65 yeketaęž‰ Diaęž‰tedi biki leeke weki mondu wiekeme.
\v 16 Kutupa bapi 830 tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mandane wekiwandiki make mondu wiaataęž‰
\v 17 mo 895 bapinaęž‰taęž‰ homeekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Mo Diaęž‰tedi ipikaęž‰ bapi 162 yeketaęž‰ biki Onoko leeke weki mondu wiekeme.
\v 19 Kutupa bapi 800 tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mandane wekiwandiki make mondu wiaataęž‰
\v 20 mo 962 bapinaęž‰taęž‰ homeekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Mo Inoko ipikaęž‰ bapi 65 yeketaęž‰ biki Medusela leeke weki mondu wiekeme.
\v 22 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ Inokotaęž‰ 300 bapi tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hataęž‰ mandane wekiwandiki mondu wiekeme.
\v 23 Ipikitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ 365 bapi hataęž‰
\v 24 Kodaęž‰ yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pipikime. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ miekeeki yalo hataęž‰ pa alu paeyekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Mo Medusela ipikitaęž‰ bapi 187 yeketaęž‰ biki Laęž‰meke leeke weki mondu wiekeme.
\v 26 Kutupa bapi 782 tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mandane wekiwandiki make mondu wiekeme.
\v 27 Kutupa 965 bapinaęž‰taęž‰ homeekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Mo Laęž‰meke ipikitaęž‰ bapi 182 yeketaęž‰ weki mondu wia hataęž‰
\v 29 alotaęž‰ Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ esihou pi wieke kenkenaęž‰ kone do wekimaęž‰taęž‰ do nikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paeyao mea baalo paęž‰laęž‰ wekie alo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Noa leekeme.
\v 30 Kutupa bapi 595 paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mandane wekiwandiki make mondu wiekeme.
\v 31 Kutupa 777 bapinaęž‰taęž‰ homeekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Kutupa Noa ipiki bapi 500 mieketaęž‰ weki tepo mondu wiekeme. Ikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Seme make Haęž‰me make Dieipedi yekeme.
\c 6
\s1 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hau
\p 
\v 1 Mo hande wandaęž‰hali paeyao kenke honiki honiki paeyaonaęž‰ putupieke handaataęž‰ wandiki titi make mendimikime.
\v 2 Kutupa mo wandiki tonutaęž‰ seliapo pimiki handaa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke tonumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone piaęž‰ tupaęž‰ mumaęž‰ mumaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 3 Kutupa Tekehalimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ pa na hao haenaęž‰ lolueke laataęž‰ Pa ekipeke ikitaęž‰ homaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ loke halemeke handa loaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ame do siki kini pea puataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ 120 bapi hakaęž‰taęž‰pao na haenaęž‰ lolueke leekeme.
\v 4 Koto nate ninaęž‰ make wetepe ninaęž‰ make do kenkenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande kenke wandaęž‰ pitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke yaaponaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke weki tititaęž‰ ankolomeke haliweki titimaęž‰ handemekeme. Ikitaęž‰ you hali tieke tieke hataęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ kiake haemeke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ biki kende tupaa wieke haliweki yekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ hoto paeyao ikaęž‰ putia peme hoke haumanu make ikaęž‰ temokonaęž‰ honemanu u tia peme ekimanu make hando haotaęž‰
\v 6 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ oni wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ pa ekipeke do kenkenaęž‰ haenaęž‰ wepia polope hone wiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ koto hone wotu witolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 7 IĚ±maęž‰ do wepolo wandaęž‰hali make hotekemanu make bamanu make paeyaotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ kone homenaęž‰ lia baalueke laa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ pa ekipeke wepia polope leekeme.
\v 8 Pate mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ Noa yaapotaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\s1 Noa
\p 
\v 9-10 Dotaęž‰ Noa tapakenaęž‰ pie. Ipikitaęž‰ weki tepo mondu wiekeme. Seme make Haęž‰me make Dieipedi make yekeme. Noa hayeke natenaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ pu ataęž‰kaęž‰ peayaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yalo hataęž‰ ipiki homeke homeke epeke some hayekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hayekeme.
\v 11 Pate Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ hoke haumaęž‰ tumbulu bao make haku na piki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰taęž‰ kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ putu piekeme.
\v 12 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handeekepate do kenketaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰pa wia wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ hokeeki paęž‰taęž‰ haemekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Noa paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao otaęž‰ hoeyaalueke hone witolome laataęž‰ Do kenkenaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ haku na piki hau manumaęž‰ tumbaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ iki paeyao siki hoeyaalueke.
\v 14 Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke timaęž‰ nakaęž‰ sisima aęž‰eyaa tukiki nanetaęž‰ da pandaęž‰manu wepiaataęž‰ oni tukiki nane make hamaęž‰ nane make otaęž‰ paeyao koloda liaęž‰peke.
\v 15 Kutupa hokulu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tombotaęž‰ 133 mida wepiaataęž‰ mo petipeke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tombotaęž‰ 22 mida wepia haliao halo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tombotaęž‰ 13 mida wepiaęž‰peke.
\v 16 Kutupa mo sisimanaęž‰taęž‰ holu wepia mo holu tukikinaęž‰ make paęž‰taęž‰liki yaaponaęž‰ make waleke 44 sendimida winaęž‰ lapeke. Kutupa mo sisimanaęž‰ tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ puku tepo wiaataęž‰ teaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ potaęž‰ kake lombapeke.
\v 17 Pa ekipeke IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ haleme pa pitiki ale paeyao siki hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ yeke ikali tieke aęž‰meinaęž‰ tapaaluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Kutupa do kenkenaęž‰ haleme aletaęž‰ otaęž‰ paeyao homilimikie.
\v 18 Pate IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ ya pi laęž‰ ulueke. Koto ekinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ ipiliki make nakaęž‰ weki tonu make ikaęž‰ wandaęž‰weki make oni sisima paęž‰taęž‰ pupe.
\v 19-20 Kutupa taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki hotekemanu make bamanu make homaamaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰eki meaęž‰tiki halieki meaęž‰tiki pea oni sisima paęž‰taęž‰ mea pupe.
\v 21 Kutupa ikaęž‰ ne make mo hoteke ba manunaęž‰ make nolo peleme nemanu make mea puaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 22 Koto leeke handaa Noamaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ peaęž‰peke leeke hau sunu paeyaęž‰ tapao anaęž‰naęž‰ piekeme.
\c 7
\s1 Mo ikali tieke teekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ Noa paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke homeke homeketaęž‰ mo tikitiki hau pu haleeki handaęž‰ ulu ekinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ wekiwandiki iki paeyao oni sisima paęž‰taęž‰ pupe leekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa neke ameĚ±leĚ±taęž‰ mo otaęž‰ haĚ±iĚ± na taĚ±leke taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki hoteketaęž‰ wataake hataęž‰ tooli tooli lo mea polo pelepatetaęž‰ mo haĚ±iĚ± taĚ±leke taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki hoteke manutaęž‰ tooli homeke lo meaęž‰peke.
\v 3 Kutupa mo taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki bamanu make wataake hataęž‰ tooli tooli lo meaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke kutupiki hau pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki hotekemanu make bamanu make na alupiki pa do kenkenaęž‰ mondu sembelaenaęž‰ lelipikie.
\v 4 Kutupa ame do natenaęž‰ kini pea yataęž‰polo mo wataake hataęž‰ peao nate paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo IĚ±maęž‰ wepolo pa pitiki alemanu paeyao hoeyaenaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ hali tieke yaapo natenaęž‰taęž‰ na to lenaęž‰ leke lako lopenaęž‰ lolueke leekeme.
\v 5 Koto leeke Noamaęž‰taęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ otaęž‰ peaęž‰peke leeke ekimanu paeyaęž‰ tapao piekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Noataęž‰ bapi 600 mieke dinaęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ mo ikali tieke aęž‰meiyekeeki epeekeme.
\v 7 Ipiliki tooli make ipilikaęž‰ weki tooli tooli make mo ikali tieke aęž‰meiyolo piekeeki wendiao oni sisima paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme.
\v 8 Kutupa mo taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki haĚ±iĚ± taĚ±leke make haĚ±iĚ± na taĚ±leke hotekemanu make bamanu make paeyao siki tooli tooli lo
\v 9 mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ piaęž‰peke leeke tupaęž‰ Noa ameĚ±leĚ± oni sisima paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambemekeme.
\v 10 Kutupa wataake hataęž‰ nate paeyeketaęž‰ mo ikali tieke kini pea teekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Noa ipikaęž‰ bapi 600 mieketaęž‰ mo hande yaapo peao opeeke kaiseponaęž‰ pula yaaponaęž‰ pa nate tepo mieketaęž‰ mo kenke tekilipulu bao oni kenke oto nane ulaęž‰ ikali paeyao opolu bao make oli ya nane wieke lakotaęž‰ potaęž‰ lombieke pitaęž‰taęž‰ lombolu baeyekeme.
\v 12 Kutupa mo lako pa ipulu ipulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ hali tieke yaapo nate pa mulu yapeekeme.
\v 13 Koto kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ puaęž‰peke leeke natenaęž‰taęž‰ Noa tooli make ipilikaęž‰ eiyeke tonu Seme make Haęž‰me make Dieipedi make ikaęž‰ weteke tonu make paeyao oni sisima paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambemekeme.
\v 14 Mo hosiki hosiki ale make aneke alemanu make ponaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ tikene halaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki hoteke make bamanu make mo Noa tapake ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pitulu pemekeme.
\v 15-16 Mo taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki pa pitiki alemanu tooli tooli lo mo Tekehalimaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ Noa ameĚ±leĚ± oni sisima tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme. Kutupa mo Tekehalimaęž‰ Noanaęž‰ hoki teli teli pu kone potaęž‰ pokaęž‰moneayekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Kutupa mo ikali tieketaęž‰ hali tieke yaapo natenaęž‰ epeeketaęž‰ mo sisima tia halo pieke tupaęž‰ ikali kendo anaęž‰naęž‰ wiekeme.
\v 18 Kutupa mo ikalitaęž‰ nokaęž‰ tieke wiekeeki yalo hataęž‰ mo sisimataęž‰ manda tia pomiekeme.
\v 19 Mo ikalitaęž‰ otaęž‰ nokaęž‰ tieke wiekeeki yalo hataęž‰ mo hokulupeke pote tumiki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ tote peao alu paeyekeme.
\v 20 Kutupa mo ikali tieketaęž‰ miĚ±li miĚ±li aęž‰meiyolo hataęž‰ mo otaęž‰ lombeipiki hokulupeke pote tumiki manutaęž‰ ikalimaęž‰taęž‰ pa 7 mida tupaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ tote piekeme.
\v 21 Kutu pieke handaa do kenkenaęž‰ pa pitiki alemanu paeyao homeekeme. Mo bamanu paeyao make hotekemanu paeyao make wandaęž‰hali paeyao make otaęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 22 Do kenkenaęž‰ pomo mea pitimiki alemanu paeyao homemekeme.
\v 23 Mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ pa pitiki alemanu paeyao hoeyaeyekeme. Wandaęž‰hali make hotekemanu make bamanu make paeyaęž‰ tapao hoeyaeyekeme. Pate Noa ameĚ±leĚ± oni sisima paęž‰taęž‰ pitimikieki homeke pa pambo haemekeme.
\v 24 Mo ikali tieketaęž‰ 150 natenaęž‰ kone pa taa hayekeme.
\c 8
\s1 Mo hande ikali tieke lomeekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Noa pitaęž‰ mo sisima paęž‰taęž‰ pitimiki tapake paeyaotaęž‰ hone na yonkaęž‰laeyekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ po epenaęž‰ leeketaęž‰ mo ikali kini pea oĚ± lomaęž‰ lomaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 2 Mo hande kenke oto nane aęž‰liaeyeke ikali pitaęž‰ oli ya nane lombolu baeyeke ikali yaapo telipinaęž‰ aęž‰mbeeketaęž‰ mo lako paeyekeme.
\v 3 Kutupa mo ikalitaęž‰ pa 150 nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ oĚ± lomaęž‰ lomaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 4 Kutupa mo wataake peao kaiseponaęž‰ pula yaaponaęž‰ nate teponaęž‰ mo sisimataęž‰ mo Aęž‰taęž‰taęž‰de tokonaęž‰ aęž‰pa wiekeme.
\v 5 Kutupa mo ikalitaęž‰ oĚ± laęž‰niatia pua kiki yaapo peao kaisepo opeeke titinaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo pote tumikimanu peneme yao waleekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Kutupa nate hali tieke yaapo paeyeketaęž‰ Noamaęž‰ da kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ lomba
\v 7 mo (daęž‰eĚ±iĚ±nkimaęž‰ handeke) ba homeke ipikaęž‰ biki leibeni tapaeyekeme. Mo hande ba paa na laęž‰kaęž‰la epeeketaęž‰ mo ikali oĚ± la halaęž‰paęž‰ winaęž‰yeke pa aĚ±yaĚ± pomu lopo hayekeme.
\v 8 Kutu pieketaęž‰ Noamaęž‰ mo ikali oĚ± laęž‰nialaęž‰pe la handenaęž‰ yeke paa ba maęž‰ndaęž‰ melipu tapaeyekepate
\v 9 mo kenketaęž‰ ikalimaęž‰ pa tote pea wiekeeki yalo mo melipu ipiki pitaęž‰peke alenaęž‰ diaęž‰yeke handaa paa mo sisima wieke alenaęž‰ pa laęž‰kaęž‰la peekeme. Kutu pieke handaa Noamaęž‰ kiki hamaęž‰ nane penaęž‰ laa mo ba handaęž‰ miekeme.
\v 10 Kutupa mo hoto wataake hataęž‰ nate pa yu wia haotaęž‰ mo hande melipu paa penaęž‰ tapaeyekeme.
\v 11 Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo melipumaęž‰taęž‰ nate oni pambolo pulu haenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ mo panake olipi katake hapula Noa paęž‰taęž‰ paa epeekeme. Kutu piekeeki handaa Noamaęž‰taęž‰ mo ikalitaęž‰ oĚ± laęž‰niayaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me hone wiekeme.
\v 12 Kutupa Noamaęž‰ wataake hataęž‰ natenaęž‰ pa hao mo melipu paa tapaeyekepate koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande bataęž‰ paa na laęž‰kaęž‰la epeekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Mo Noataęž‰ 601 bapi mieketaęž‰ mo titinaęž‰ kaiseponaęž‰ titinaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo ikalitaęž‰ otaęž‰ oĚ± laęž‰niayekeme. Kutu pieke handaa Noamaęž‰taęž‰ mo sisima aęž‰mbaeyeke ale mea bao lekemaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ piekepate mo kenketaęž‰ hapumaęž‰ hapumaęž‰ piaęž‰eki handeekeme.
\v 14 Mo yaapo peao kaiseponaęž‰ pula tepo paeya yunki mindiki hataęž‰ peao natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo kenketaęž‰ otaęž‰ hapupa peekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Noa paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 16 Nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ weki tooli tooli make hama opolu bao yopupe laataęž‰
\v 17 Mo ba manumaęž‰ make hoteke manumaęž‰ make mendiolo mendiolo ombu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ do kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ sembelenaęž‰ mea opolu bapee leekeme.
\v 18 Koto leeke Noa tooli make ipilikaęž‰ weki tooli tooli make mo sisima minaęž‰paęž‰lao hama opolu bao pemekeme.
\v 19 Kutupa mo hotekemanu make bamanu make ikaęž‰ homeke tapake sunu lo mandakenaęž‰ opolu baemekeme.
\s1 Noamaęž‰ hoteke lia haleekeeki
\p 
\v 20 Noamaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ oloda wepiataęž‰ mo haĚ±iĚ± na taĚ±leke hotekemanu make bamanu make tapake tapakenaęž‰ homeke homeke lo mea tieke tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mo olodanaęž‰ lu yanka haleekeme.
\v 21 Kutu pieke handaa mo lia haleeke hotekenaęž‰ totopo seliapomaęž‰taęž‰ mo Tekehali taęž‰naęž‰ homaęž‰ tiayeke handaa ipikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Do wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pu haleme ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do kenketaęž‰ esihou pi oto paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ paa na winaęž‰ lolueke. Pa ekipeke ikaęž‰ mo panake daetaęž‰laęž‰me ale paęž‰taęž‰ konetaęž‰ hoke honemanu wilimi ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulu ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ame do puaęž‰ tupaęž‰ mo do kenkenaęž‰ pa pitiki alemanu paeyao otaęž‰ paa aęž‰ndaęž‰ na hoeyaalueke.
\v 22 Kutupa do kenke pa winaęž‰taęž‰ nokaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ nate make ne napeke minaęž‰laęž‰ nate make wilieke. Kutupa make hoto paeyao kosaęž‰ make titipu make nate ki make lako ki make nate make timbaęž‰ make otaęž‰ pa uĚ± pelia halieke leekeme.
\c 9
\s1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Noa yaapo pi laęž‰ wiekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Noa aęž‰talaęž‰ aęž‰talaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ pimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilimi wekiwandikitaęž‰ do kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰maęž‰ wekiwandiki wopu mendiaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 2 laataęž‰ mo hotekemanu paeyao make bamanu paeyao make taęž‰peli paeyao make ikaęž‰ honkopu oto paęž‰taęž‰ haleme ekinaęž‰ iki paalaęž‰ halimikie.
\v 3 Kutupa ametaęž‰ mo tanimanu no haleme tupaęž‰ do hotekemanu paeyao make lia nomenaęž‰ yeke kitolopate
\v 4 pa mo we pa pitiki hoteke homeke na napaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke mo daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ koto we paęž‰taęž‰ pileke loaęž‰me.
\v 5 Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ hoke yenki halueke. Kutupa hoteke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke yenkitaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki halueke.
\v 6 Halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ leke wepieke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ homenaęž‰ liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ hali tonumaęž‰ kone lilimikie.
\p 
\v 7 Ikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilimi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ do kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰maęž‰ wekiwandiki wopu mendiaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 8 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Noa aęž‰talaęž‰ aęž‰talaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 9 Iki make ikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilimi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ dupiki pi laęž‰ witolome.
\v 10 Koto pitaęž‰ mo hande sisima paęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± epemeke pa pitiki alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ mo bamanu make hotekemanu make iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 11 Dupiki pi manumaęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± pi laęž‰ witolome. Mo kenkenaęž‰ pa pitiki alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ mo ikali tieke tiekemaęž‰ otaęž‰ paa na hoeyaenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo ikali tieke tiekemaęž‰ do kenke paeyao paa na hoeyaenaęž‰e laa IĚ±maęž‰ laęž‰ witolome.
\v 12 Kutupa do iki ameĚ±leĚ± make mo pa pitiki alemanu ameĚ±leĚ± make do otaęž‰ na paeyeke pa u halo paęž‰laęž‰ laęž‰ witolo patehau witolo ekitaęž‰
\v 13 oli koanaęž‰ yaka kaęž‰laęž‰daęž‰peiya witolo ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do kenke yaapo pi laęž‰ ulu ekinaęž‰ patehau ulueki yelieke.
\v 14 IĚ±maęž‰ oli yataęž‰ koa manumaęž‰ aęž‰mbatiki pitolo hataęž‰ mo kaęž‰laęž‰daęž‰peiya aęž‰paęž‰tiki piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 15 kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo hande iki ameĚ±leĚ± make mo hotekemanu ameĚ±leĚ± make ikali tieke tiekemaęž‰ mo pa pitiki alemanu paeyao paa na hoeyaalueke laa pi laęž‰ uaęž‰eki niminaalueke.
\v 16 Mo kaęž‰laęž‰daęž‰peiya oli koa manunaęž‰ peneme yatiki piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ haleme pa pitiki alemanu nikaęž‰ mo na paeyaęž‰peke pi laęž‰ umaęž‰eki paa niminatiki pulueke.
\v 17 Mo kaęž‰laęž‰daęž‰peiyataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo pa pitiki alemanu paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo ekinaęž‰ patehaue leekeme.
\s1 Noa aęž‰talaęž‰ aęž‰talaęž‰
\p 
\v 18 Mo sisima paęž‰taęž‰ pita pemeke Noanaęž‰ eiyeke tonutaęž‰ Seme make Haęž‰me make Dieipedi makee. Haęž‰metaęž‰ Keinaninaęž‰ atekee
\v 19 Mo Noanaęž‰ eiyeke tepotaęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ apaęž‰meie.
\v 20 Noataęž‰ e hali yalo ipikitaęž‰ titinaęž‰ waini pu noko peeke halie.
\v 21 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo waini ikali naa keaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ akaęž‰manu holo bao pa tu mea hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ palai da paęž‰taęž‰ pumbuniao wiekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Kutupa mo Keinaninaęž‰ ateke Haęž‰memaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ateke pa tia peliekeeki hando haotaęž‰ hameke yaapo lolo hamaęž‰ nane peekeme.
\v 23 Kutu pieke handaa Seme pitaęž‰ Dieipedi yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ ateke pa tia peliekeeki handaęž‰peke yeketaęž‰ dau homeke ipilikaęž‰ peiyokonaęž‰ pulumbao tia hoki laęž‰kaęž‰la oni palai da paęž‰taęž‰ pua pa ale handa hataęž‰ atekenaęž‰ loke manda lopamoneao aęž‰mbaepekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa Noa ipikaęž‰ hone paa epeeketaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ wetepe wekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ piekeeki handaęž‰ u hao
\v 25 Noamaęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Keinani paęž‰taęž‰ esihou pi witolomaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kame yaaponaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ hali halieke.
