\v 3 Kutupa ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Aęž‰e. Ametaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ kenkemaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la toopimaęž‰ handeke hankolaęž‰papeke alemanu wepumanaęž‰e lemekeme. Kutu pimikitaęž‰ mo wepimiki toopimanu make mo toopimanu tuna tuna pea miniki halo pieke koloda make wimikime.
