\v 9 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ mo Keinani kenkenaęž‰ kaęž‰waęž‰ nanemaęž‰ tilao da maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pomu lopeekeme.
\s1 Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ Idiepi pua hayekeeki
\p 
\v 10 Pate koto Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ teaęž‰ ki tieke epeeke handaa Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰waęž‰ nanemaęž‰ papate leke puo pu hao mo Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ pa taęž‰kaęž‰li halo peekeme.
\v 11 Kutupa ipiki mo Idiepi poluekemaęž‰ yu tombonaęž‰ pua hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weteke Saęž‰tai paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ wandaęž‰ seliapoe.
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Idiepi haliwekimaęž‰ neke handolotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ yaka wandaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa IĚ± litolo hataęž‰ neketaęž‰ pa halenaęž‰ lelimikie.
\v 13 Kutu paamaęž‰naęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ yaka anaęž‰e lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ na liki pa epeke tupaęž‰ hatuku halimikie leekeme.
\v 14 Koto eki laa mo yu tombo minaęž‰paęž‰lao oni Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ pepeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ kone mo Idiepi haliwekimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ seliapoe laa handemekeme.
\v 15 Kutupa mo kininaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ mandane kapomani haliwekimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ seliapo piekeeki mo ikaęž‰ kini paęž‰taęž‰ pua lemekeme. Kutu pimiki mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kininaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pemekeme.
\v 16 Kutupa mo kinimaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ mieke ekinaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau pitolo hataęž‰ sipisipi wopu make nanikosi wopu make kaomanu make donkimanu make pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make kemelomanu make haleekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Pate mo kinimaęž‰ Saęž‰tai mieke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ mo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make otaęž‰ hoke yeni kimanu yapenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 18 Kutu pieke mo kinimaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ epoe laa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ dotaęž‰ ekipiki hau pelepe laataęž‰ Do wandaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰e laa IĚ±taęž‰ ekipeke na lakipe.
\v 19 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ekipeke ipikitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ anaęž‰e le ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ yaka wandaęž‰ au lano laa pelepe. Nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ domaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± hatuku pao pue leekeme.
\v 20 Mo kinimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ Hatuku pupe leeke handaa mo haliwekimaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ wia hayeke alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao mea mo kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao penaęž‰ hatuku pemekeme.
\c 13
\s1 Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ Loda yaapo kaęž‰taęž‰alu pipikieki
\p 
\v 1 Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ wia hayeke alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao make mea Idiepi minaęž‰paęž‰lao Keinani kenkenaęž‰ kaęž‰waęž‰ nanemaęž‰ tilao peekeme. Loda make mandakenaęž‰ pemekeme.
\v 2 Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ sipisipimanu make nanikosimanu make kaomanu make silipa make kolo make koto ale paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ hamoko hali tieke hayekeme.
\v 3 Kutupa koto pate minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua mo Bedele nanemaęž‰ peekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ hande ipikaęž‰ palai da aęž‰eyeke alenaęž‰ mo Bedele pitaęž‰ Ai yaapo tukikinaęž‰
\v 4 mo hande oloda aęž‰eyeke alenaęž‰ opolo peekeme. Koto patetaęž‰ mo Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ layekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Lodataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandaęž‰ make sipisipimanu make nanikosimanu make pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make hayekeme.
\v 6 Kutupa ipilikitaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ hoteke wopu punupikieki yalo hataęž‰ mo ipilikaęž‰ hoteke manumaęž‰ napeke ambu opeeke kenketaęž‰ wopu diaęž‰ yekeme.
\v 7 Kutu piekeeki yalo hataęž‰ mo Eipolaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ hotekemanu handeteke haemeke haliweki pitaęž‰ mo Lodanaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ hotekemanu handeteke haemeke haliweki ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone ape ape laęž‰tiki pimikime. Koto nate ninaęž‰taęž‰ mo Keinani wandaęž‰hali make Petese wandaęž‰hali make pa haemekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Kutu pieke handaataęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Loda paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dikitaęž‰ homeke tapake yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ haliweki pitaęž‰ yaka haliweki yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ ape ape na lapeke alee.
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kaęž‰taęž‰alu pupanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ kenke maĚ±leke lia neke mandanemaęž‰ pekenaęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mandanemaęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Koto leeke Lodamaęž‰ mo Diodani hawete handomaęž‰ handomaęž‰ putia pua mo Soa pua hando naeyekepate oni kenketaęž‰ mo hande Tekehalinaęž‰ e o mo Idiepi kenkemaęž‰ handaa ikali wopu yapeekeeki handeekeme. Dotaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ mo Sodomo pitaęž‰ Komoto daoni yaapo aĚ±iĚ± na hoeyake haenaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 11 Koto ekinaęž‰ Lodamaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diodani hawete tieke ipikaęž‰ekie laa maĚ±leke liaataęž‰ mo nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nanemaęž‰ tilao peekeme. Kototaęž‰ mo hande hali yaaponaęž‰ kaęž‰taęž‰alu pipiki tupaęž‰e.
\v 12 Eipolaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰taęž‰ Lodataęž‰ mo hawetenaęž‰ hayeke daonimanu paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰tia pominolotaęž‰ mo Sodomo nanemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ palai da aęž‰eya pitiekeme.
\v 13 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ hoke wandaęž‰hali hataęž‰ make mo Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau pu haemekeme.
\s1 Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ mo Hebotoni nane peekeeki
\p 
\v 14 Mo Loda peaęž‰ hoki nane Tekehalimaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto neke hale alenaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ mo teaęž‰ paeyao siki epeke tupaęž‰ handaęž‰e.
\v 15 Koto handeleeki paeyaotaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ make nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wandaęž‰wekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰weki paęž‰taęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ kulu polo kenkee. Kutupa koto kenketaęž‰ hoto paeyao nakaęž‰eki utia pu halieke.
\v 16 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na yataęž‰paęž‰ taęž‰palo paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ wopu kulueke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ dokolo yataęž‰paęž‰ taęž‰payaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki make yataęž‰paęž‰ taęž‰paenaęž‰e.
\v 17 Koto paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do kenke neke kulu polo ekinaęž‰ mo kenke paeyao pua hando wie leekeme.
\v 18 Koto leeke Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ palai da yokaęž‰moneaotaęž‰ mo Hebotoni hali Maęž‰motenaęž‰ timanu tekepaęž‰taęž‰ leke pua pitaęž‰ koto patetaęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ oloda aęž‰eyekeme.
\c 14
\s1 Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Loda paęž‰taęž‰leekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Kini haliweki tonkoputaęž‰ mo Baęž‰biloninaęž‰ kini Aęž‰motapele make Aęž‰lasanaęž‰ kini Aęž‰tioko make Ilaęž‰menaęž‰ kini Siedolaoma make Koiminaęž‰ kini Taedolo make mo
\v 2 mandane yunki hataęž‰ kinitaęž‰ mo Sodomonaęž‰ kini Bita make mo Komotonaęž‰ kini Biesa make mo Aęž‰demanaęž‰ kini Sinaęž‰be make mo Seboiminaęž‰ kini Semebe make mo Bela biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Soanaęž‰ kini ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ pulu pemekeme.
\v 3 Do yunki hataęž‰ kini manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo Sidimi hawetenaęž‰ ametaęž‰ mo ikali leke maęž‰ndaęž‰ biki Homaęž‰laęž‰ dawala leleme alenaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ami haliweki mombaęž‰laemekeme.
\v 4 Ikitaęž‰ 12 bapinaęž‰taęž‰ hande kini Siedolaoma oto paęž‰taęž‰ haemekepate pa mo bapi 13 paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ipiki oto paęž‰taęž‰ na halumeke lemekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Kutupa mo bapi 14 paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Siedolaoma ipikaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ kinimanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ikaęž‰ ami haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mo Aęž‰saęž‰detodi Kanaimi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haleme Tepaęž‰imi wandaęž‰hali make mo Haęž‰mi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haleme Susimi tapake make mo homeke hau hondaęž‰ lupa peeke Kitiaęž‰tieimi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haleme Emimi tapake make
\v 6 mo Idomo pote paęž‰taęž‰manu haleme Ho tapake make otaęž‰ lu yombitolo hataęž‰ mo Elepaęž‰tani kenkenaęž‰ mo hapu papeke ale honikinaęž‰ pua tolu naemekeme.
\v 7 Kutupa paa mo Keidese kenke ambaęž‰taęž‰ Enemisipade leeke alenaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la epemekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Aęž‰maęž‰leke wandaęž‰hali bepolaotaęž‰ mo Hasasono Teima kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke Aęž‰mo wandaęž‰hali make bepolaemekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Kutu pieke mo Sodomo make Komoto make Aęž‰dema make Seboimi make Bela make koto da kini manumaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ami haliwekimanu mo Sidimi hawetenaęž‰ mombaęž‰laotaęž‰ mo
\v 9 Ilaęž‰me make Koimi make Baęž‰biloni make Elasa make koto tonkopu danaęž‰ kinimanu ameĚ±leĚ± mo yunki hataęž‰ danaęž‰ kini manumaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 10 Koto hawetenaęž‰taęž‰ kolodamaęž‰ wepiki naku manumaęž‰ tumbieke ekiyalo mo Sodomo Komoto da yaaponaęž‰ kini yaapotaęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ pindipa polueke alo pepekepate koto naku paęž‰taęž‰ pua lopepekeme. Pate mo pa haemeke kini tepotaęž‰ mo pote paęž‰taęž‰manu pindipa pemekeme.
\v 11 Kotaęž‰ mo kini tonkopumaęž‰taęž‰ mo Sodomo Komoto daoni yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ wieke ale paeyao make nemanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mea pemekeme.
\v 12 Kutupa make Eipolaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ hamekenaęž‰ eiyeke Lodataęž‰ koto Sodomo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke ekiyalo ipiki make ipikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mea hatuku pemekeme.
\v 13 Pate hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ pindipa pua mo Aęž‰mo tapake hali Maęž‰motenaęž‰ timanu hayeke ale nanemaęž‰ hayeke Hibulu hali Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mo koto haumanu la haleekeme. Maęž‰mote make ipikaęž‰ kame yaapo Esikolo pitaęž‰ Aęž‰naęž‰ maketaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki haemekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Kutupa Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kamenaęž‰ eiyeke hatuku pemekeeki opu haotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ mokaęž‰la hando haemeke 318 haliweki mombaęž‰lao mo hande kini tonkopu teliaęž‰ mea pua otaęž‰ mo Daęž‰ni kenke paęž‰taęž‰ tolu lopalo pemekeme.
\v 15 Koto patetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliweki putupaęž‰ putupaęž‰ pea mombaęž‰lao haenaęž‰ loma loma peaataęž‰ koto timba hataęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki tapake lia bepolaemekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo haliwekitaęž‰ mo Damasikasinaęž‰ okane nanemaęž‰ tilao otaęž‰ mo Hoba pua tolu lutia pemekeme.
\v 16 Kutupa mo mea pemeke alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao pa petolo mimikime. Kutupa make mo ipikaęž‰ kamenaęž‰ eiyeke Loda make ipikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao make wandaęž‰weki make mo mandane dipula mea pemeke wandaęž‰hali make paa hatuku epemekeme.
\s1 Melekisedekemaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ epeayekeeki
\p 
\v 17 Eipolaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Siedolaoma make mo mandane kinimanu ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea bepolao epeeketaęž‰ mo Sodomonaęž‰ kinimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Sape hawetenaęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Kininaęž‰ hawete laęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ mandaęž‰hande pulu peekeme.
\v 18 Kutupa mo Seiliminaęž‰ kini pitaęž‰ mo Manda Halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ yeni peao halaęž‰ hali Melekisedekemaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ betedi make waini ikali make mea aęž‰paeyekeme.
\v 19 Kutupa epeaasaęž‰ pi alo alotaęž‰ Mo kenke ya yaapo waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ Manda Halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ epeaenaęž‰e laataęž‰
\v 20 Mo nakaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki haliweki bepolaenaęž‰ leaęž‰ Manda Halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki minaęž‰liamanaęž‰e leekeme. Kutupa Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo miaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao telipa kiki yaapo yeketaęž‰ homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Melekisedeke paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Kutu pieke hoki nane mo hande Sodomo kinimaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo mi alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaotaęž‰ wia halo pelepate yaka wandaęž‰hali homeke kie leekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do kenke ya yaapo waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ Tekehali oli Manda Halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki alomaęž‰
\v 23 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke pepeleke alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ siki make otaęž‰ na wia halueke laataęž‰ Otaęž‰ mo kodoni pu kone o anke dake pu tunkuliki kone loaęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ mo nakanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ mea hamoko yawaęž‰maęž‰ pi na loelenaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 24 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na mulu polopate mo yaka haliwekimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ nemeke alemanu homeke mulueke. Kutupa make do IĚ± tambaęž‰ maęž‰laęž‰ hali tepo Aęž‰naęž‰ make Esikolo make Maęž‰mote ikaęž‰ putupiliki homeke minaęž‰e leekeme.
\c 15
\s1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ yaapo pi laęž‰ wiekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Do haumanu hoki nanetaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ upa piki nono pea Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeeki opiekeme. Eipolaęž‰maęž‰o. Paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰pee. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo ekiaęž‰ndaęž‰ piliaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hankaęž‰ tupaęž‰ hataęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ yenki tieke kulueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 2 Pate Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehali Kodaęž‰o. Mo IĚ±taęž‰ wekiwandiki make diaęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ pa ekipa epeke yenki kilipikipe. Yaka anke teke mulu paęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ mo Damasikasi hali Eliesa homeke halaęž‰me.
\v 3 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ wekiwandiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na kele ekinaęž‰ mo yaka pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ some maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ yaka anke teke milieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Kutupa Tekehalimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi paa leekeeki dupa opiekeme. Do pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ some Eliesamaęž‰ nakaęž‰ anketeke na mulu paęž‰laęž‰pate otaęž‰ nakaęž‰ wekimaęž‰ milieke leekeme.
\v 5 Kutupa mo Tekehalimaęž‰ ipiki hama hatuku pua alotaęž‰ Oli ya nane handaęž‰liao oli hombulankaęž‰manu yataęž‰paęž‰ handaęž‰e. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ oli hombulankaęž‰ manumaęž‰ handilimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaeyeke ekiyalo mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ tikitiki piki halie leekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Kutu pa mo Tekehalimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do kenke neke muelenaęž‰yeke neke mo Baęž‰biloni kenke paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ daoni Aęž‰e minaęž‰paęž‰lao hatuku epoaęž‰ Tekehalie leekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Pate Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Tekehali Kodaęž‰o. IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ yaka kenke laataęž‰ Ekipa hone wionope leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Tekehalimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo bapi tepo paeke kao make nanikosi make sipisipi halieki make mea kutupa melipu make dokolo make mea epoe leekeme.
\v 10 Koto leeke Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hotekemanu Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mea aęž‰pa tukikinaęž‰ halaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰tiki pea mandanetaęž‰ tombo maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ wiatiki mandanetaęž‰ tombo maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ wiatiki pea hoki tuna tuna pea winaęž‰ leekepate mo ba yaapotaęž‰ na halepeleekeme.
\v 11 Mo hoteke manutaęž‰ mo Idamaęž‰ handeke ba manumaęž‰ noluekemaęž‰ epemekepate Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ tolu liaęž‰tiki piekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Nate oni pambolo pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ uĚ± yokaęž‰lupa puaataęž‰ paalaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ pututu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epeekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Kutupa mo Tekehalimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ mo maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ pua hataęž‰taęž‰ leke popeleke na handeke tapake leke halimikie. Ikitaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pa pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ tapake hataęž‰ 400 bapinaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ handeteke halimikie.
\p 
\v 14 Pate kutu piliaęž‰ tapaketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ halo polopate mo nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikitaęž‰ koto kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao pemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ tieke mea pelimikie.
\v 15 Neketaęž‰ koke yaa pita yopu homupea homekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mea hoilimikie.
\v 16 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ haleme Aęž‰mo tapake wandaęž‰hali aĚ±iĚ± na tolu liki pa haotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau tieke piteleme ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ haluaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ mei tonkopu miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ do pate paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipilimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Mo nate oni pambolo pua timbaęž‰ leeketaęž‰ mo lumu opolo hake itikaęž‰pei pitaęž‰ talo talo hake olaęž‰pake yaapomaęž‰ aęž‰pa mo hotekemanu wieke ale tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ yapeekeme.
\v 18 Kutupa koto pate konetaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ yaapo pi laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do yataęž‰polo kenke paeyaotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ halueke laa pi laęž‰ witolome. Oni Idiepi yu tombonaęž‰ kini pea pua mo Yupoteitisi ikali puataęž‰
\v 19 mo Keni wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke make Kenisi wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke make Kadomono wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke make mo
\v 20 Hidi wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke make Petese wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke make mo Tepaęž‰imi wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke make
\v 21 mo Aęž‰mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke make Keinani wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke make Keakasi wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke make mo Diebusi wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke make paeyao halueke laa loaęž‰me leekeme.
\c 16
\s1 Heika pitaęž‰ Isimaęž‰elo yaapo
\p 
\v 1 Eipolaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ weteke Saęž‰taimaęž‰taęž‰ weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na mendiaeyekeme. Pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ Idiepi wandiki biki Heika hatuku hayekeme.
\v 2 Koto ekinaęž‰ Saęž‰taimaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ IĚ± weki na mendiono alaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mo yaka pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandiki yaapo peliaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰pe. Kutu pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka weki mendiaenaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme. Koto leeke Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Saęž‰taimaęž‰ leeke pinaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ Heikataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yaapo peao wandaęž‰ haenaęž‰ Saęž‰taimaęž‰ haliki haleekeme. Do hau piki hautaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ kiki yaapo bapi haenaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 4 Kutupa Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Heika yaapo pelia mo wandikitaęž‰ weki pitiekeme. Mo wandikimaęž‰ ipiki weki weleke hayekeeki handolotaęž‰ hakoko yamo baaso hataęž‰ Saęž‰tai lu pambaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Kutu pieke Saęž‰taimaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Heikamaęž‰ IĚ± lu pambaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kaęž‰taęž‰taęž‰e. IĚ±maęž‰ kone ipiki neke paęž‰taęž‰ ku hao ipiki weki weleke hayaęž‰eki hando haotaęž‰ IĚ± lu pambaasaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ diki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo tikitiki polopaęž‰me laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lenaęž‰e laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Eipolaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ mo wandikitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandiki yalo neke oto paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki pie leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Saęž‰taimaęž‰taęž‰ Heika hoke tupaęž‰ handeteke hayeke handaa pao pindipa peekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Mo Tekehalinaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰taęž‰ Heika oni Siaęž‰e nane pulaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ hapupapeke alenaęž‰ tunkulu pa pitieke ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ mandaęž‰hande piekeme.
\v 8 Kutupa alotaęž‰ Saęž‰tainaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaaso wandaęž‰ Heikao. Neketaęž‰ hanemaęž‰ aęž‰pa pelepe laataęž‰ hane pulipe leekeme. Heikamaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ya handeteke halaęž‰ wandaęž‰ kiao pindipa pulume leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Mo enisolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pao laęž‰kaęž‰la pua ipikaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰ hapeke leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Kutupa paa alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na yataęž‰polo paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ wopu kulueke.
\v 11 Neketaęž‰ hali weki mendilipikimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Isimaęž‰elo lapeke. Pa ekipeke mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo eĚ± leleeki opaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 12 Pate nakaęž‰ wekitaęž‰ mo sayale au laęž‰laęž‰ donkimaęž‰ handaa ipikitaęž‰ paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkulaa hataęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkulimikie. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ yankeke paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± na hao peliki taęž‰taęž‰ halieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Heikamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ otaęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ doeki la haluekemaęž‰ pa hao polope laa leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi la haleaęž‰ Tekehalitaęž‰ Hando Halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰e laa ipikaęž‰ biki kini pea taapaęž‰ wiayekeme.
\v 14 Koto ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo Keidese hao mo Betede tukikinaęž‰ ulaęž‰ naku ikalitaęž‰ Mo IĚ± Handaęž‰laęž‰ Pa Hao Halaęž‰ Halinaęž‰ Naku Ikalie lelememe.
\p 
\v 15 Heikamaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ weki mendiaeyeketaęž‰ Isimaęž‰elo leekeme.
\v 16 Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ bapi 86 yekeme.
\c 17
\s1 Sekemesaisi hautaęž‰ mo pi laęž‰ wieke ekinaęž‰ patehau
\p 
\v 1 Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ 99 bapi mieketaęž‰ mo Tekehali opolo pua alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Aneke Wele wopupiki Kodaęž‰ halome. IĚ±maęž‰ alo pi opua hoto paeyao tikitiki hau homeke peaęž‰peke.
\v 2 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke yaapo yaka pi laęž‰ wiaataęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ wopu kulueke leekeme.
\v 3 Koto leeke Eipolaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ you pandaęž‰puniao ipikaęž‰ popeleketaęž‰ oni yu wataeyeke handaa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 4 IĚ±maęž‰ neke yaapo do pi laęž‰ witolome. IĚ±maęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ tutu paeyao sikinaęž‰ apaęž‰mei halipikie.
\v 5 Nakaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Eipolaęž‰maęž‰ diaęž‰yalo ametaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰e. Pa ekipeke neketaęž‰ tutu paeyaonaęž‰ apaęž‰mei hawaasome.
\v 6 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki tieke kuaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mandanetaęž‰ kinimanu pitilimikie. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ tieke kuaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ tutu taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ halimikie.
\p 
\v 7 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ make nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ tapake paęž‰taęž‰ maketaęž‰ do laęž‰ witolo pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na paeke pa u halo paęž‰laęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolome. IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make halueke.
\v 8 Ame do neketaęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali leke hale kenketaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ make kia nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ make halueke. Do Keinani kenke paeyaotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hoto paeyao ikaęž‰ ekie la halaataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halueke.
\p 
\v 9 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ make nakaęž‰ wetepe ninaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikimaęž‰ maketaęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± do pi laęž‰ witolo ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ wia halumeke laa lapaęž‰peke.
\v 10 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ make nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikimaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ hali weki paeyaotaęž‰ sekemesaisi hau otaęž‰ pulumeke laa lapaęž‰peke.
\v 11-12 Ame do kini pea pulutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hali weki mondu wia pitinaęž‰ hoto ketepo hataęž‰ paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ sekemesaisi hau peapaęž‰peke. Kutupa mo iki haleme da paęž‰taęž‰ mendilimi pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hali weki make mo kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ hambaęž‰laęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ haliweki make sekemesaisi hau peapaęž‰peke. Do haumaęž‰taęž‰ neke IĚ± dikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolopaęž‰eki peneme yao walieke.
\v 13 Hali paeyao sikitaęž‰ sekemesaisi hau peapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa do manda lokenaęž‰ pitolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo na paeke pa u halo paęž‰laęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo ekinaęž‰ patehau pitoloeki walieke.
\v 14 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate iki maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi sekemesaisi hau na piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Ya tapakee pi na lolueke. Pa ekipeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yaka pi laęž‰ ulueki na wia haleke loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰taęž‰ Saęž‰tai pi paa na lapeke. Ame do kini peataęž‰ Seta lapeke.
\v 16 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki epeao make ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ nakaęž‰ weki kulueke. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki epeao make ipikitaęž‰ mandane tutunaęž‰ inkiki halieke. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ piliaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ kinimanu halimikie.
\p 
\v 17 Koto leeke Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ you pandaęž‰puniao ipikaęž‰ leke popeleketaęž‰ oni yu wataenaęž‰ leekepate ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ halimaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ 100 bapi yaęž‰naęž‰ kone weki mendiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe laa kutupa Setataęž‰ 90 bapinaęž‰ weki mendiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe laa ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone ki teekeme.
\v 18 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Pa ekipeke Isimaęž‰elomaęž‰ yaka anketeke na minaęž‰ alepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Setamaęž‰ nakaęž‰ weki mendiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke lelipikie. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki make ipikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ piliaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki ameĚ±leĚ± make hoto paeyao yaka pi laęž‰ witoloeki pa wia halumeke. Koto pi laęž‰ witolo ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na paeke pa u halo paęž‰laęž‰ekie.
\v 20 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Isimaęž‰elonaęž‰ honke leeki opuaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki epeaotaęž‰ wekiwandiki wopu halaa ipikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ piliaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki make wopu halueke. Ipikitaęž‰ 12 you haliweki tonunaęž‰ ateke haotaęž‰ kutupa ipikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ piliaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ tutu tieke hawalueke.
\v 21 Pate IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ weki Aisaęž‰ke yaapo yaka pi laęž‰ witoloeki miniki halueke. Ipikitaęž‰ do homeke natenaęž‰ kone mo bapinaęž‰ Setamaęž‰ mendilieke leekeme.
\v 22 Kutupa Kodaęž‰ ipiki Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ yaapo pi lo paeyaotaęž‰ ipiki minaęž‰paęž‰lao peekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Koto homeke natenaęž‰ kone Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi opuataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki Isimaęž‰elo make mo ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke haliwekimanu make apaęž‰tao mo ipikaęž‰ da kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke pa hameke e pokaemeke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ eiyeke tonu make mo hambeeke haliweki paeyao siki make sekemesaisi hau peayekeme.
\v 24 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ 99 bapinaęž‰ sekemesaisi hau piekeme.
\v 25 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ weki Isimaęž‰elotaęž‰ 13 bapinaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 26 Ipilikitaęž‰ mo homeke natenaęž‰ sekemesaisi hau pipikime.
\v 27 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaemeke haliweki make mandakenaęž‰ pimikime.
\c 18
\s1 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ wekinaęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Tekehalitaęž‰ mo Maęž‰motenaęž‰ timanu tekenaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ opolo peekeme. Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nate otaęž‰ titipu tieke pieke dinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ palai da potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰
\v 2 handaęž‰ liaeyekepate tepo hali haemekeeki handeekeme. Mo handeaęž‰ dinaęž‰ kone pototo la pua mo haliweki mandaęž‰hande piekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ leke popeleketaęž‰ oni yu wataenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰
\v 3 alotaęž‰ Haliwekio. Yaka da paęž‰taęž‰ hoto na pitiki pa na lombei peaęž‰paęž‰peke. IĚ±taęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ halome.
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ankemanu tandaęž‰pa do ti teke paęž‰taęž‰ hoto pitomenaęž‰ ikali mealo ponoe.
\p 
\v 5 Kutupa make mo ikaęž‰ potaęž‰ pelimi ale paęž‰taęž‰manu honkopu haminaęž‰ ne siki make mea aęž‰palueke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yaka da paęž‰taęž‰ epeleme ekitaęž‰ IĚ± taęž‰naęž‰ homaęž‰tiaasaęž‰ hau pelememe. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ mionoe leekeme. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa keiyae lemekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipupula mo palai da paęž‰taęž‰ pua Seta paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ wili palaowa tepo aęž‰ndaęž‰ mea aĚ±iĚ± betedi wepie leekeme.
\v 7 Koto laa ipikitaęž‰ oni kao banisi paęž‰taęž‰ pua loke panka wiki panake kao ikiki mea ipikaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme. Kutupa mo halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipupula pua yankeekeme.
\v 8 Kutupa yankeketaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ mo kao andu pankeke manda witaęž‰laęž‰ epeke imekemaęž‰ handeke ale make otaęž‰ kao andu pankeke make mo hande hoteke make mea pua mo haliweki pitieke alenaęž‰ pua wiekeme. Koto ti teke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo haliweki ne panaęž‰ peaotaęž‰ nenaęž‰ leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Kutupa mo haliwekimaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Setataęž‰ hande paęž‰laęž‰pe lemekeme. Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Oni palai da paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ame do kini pea kaisepo kiki homekenaęž‰ mandane ekinaęž‰ tonkopunaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paa epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Setataęž‰ weki mendilieke leekeme. Setataęž‰ mo halikinaęž‰ hoki nane mo palai da potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ opiekeme.
\v 11 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰ Seta yaapotaęž‰ otaęž‰ koke yepekeme. Kutupa Setataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kaisepo da handeekeeki make paeyekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰ Setamaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ oninaęž‰ tolumaęž‰ ki talo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ IĚ± make yaka haliki make koke yalo hataęž‰ honkopu paelaęž‰me. Ekipa taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ loke paa apaęž‰talupaęž‰pe leekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Ekipeke Setamaęž‰ ki talo hataęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ koke yolome ekipa weki monduluaęž‰pe alaęž‰pe.
\v 14 Koto mo Tekehalimaęž‰ na peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ ulaęž‰pe. Ambaęž‰ mo loaęž‰ handaęž‰e. Ame do kini pea kaisepo kiki homekenaęž‰ mandane ekinaęž‰ tonkopunaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paa epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Setamaęž‰ weki mendilieke laa loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Kotoeki leeke Seta ipikitaęž‰ paalaęž‰ pieke handa honiolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ki na toaęž‰me leekepate Tekehalimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ki temee leekeme.
\s1 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Sodomo da hoeyaapaęž‰naęž‰ honke laeyekeeki
\p 
\v 16 Kutupa mo hali wekitaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Sodomo da handaęž‰nialo pimiki alenaęž‰ pemeke handaa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo potaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰talo lo tapaaluekemaęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ pemekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Kutupa mo Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ oninaęž‰ tolumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pulu polo ekitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na aęž‰mbalueke.
\v 18 Ipikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ piliaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ honkopu wopu hake tutu tieke halieke. Kutupa make ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ mo tutu paeyao epealueke.
\v 19 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki titi make ipikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ piliaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ make IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea tikitiki hau make otaęž‰ hau make otaęž‰ piaęž‰paęž‰peke laa la halenaęž‰yeke ipiki maĚ±leke lulume. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ uaęž‰ tupaęž‰ hau paeyao peawalueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Koto hone wia mo Tekehalimaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Sodomo Komoto da yaaponaęž‰ pi laasaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ hokeeki laaloendi pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa ipilikaęž‰ hoke hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ tiekee.
\v 21 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo loloendi piteleme laasaęž‰eki opolo ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰pe laa handolo holopulueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Kutupa mo hali yaapotaęž‰ Sodomo nane pepekepate mo Tekehalitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ yaapo pa hayekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Tekehali handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰ tapake hoeyaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ mo tikitiki piki tapake make otaęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ hoeyalo pele ekinaęž‰ alepe.
\v 24 Oni daoni paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau na pu haleme wandaęž‰hali 50 hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa hoeyalipikipe. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto 50 wandaęž‰hali homaamaęž‰naęž‰ ya honemaęž‰taęž‰ na hoeyalenaęž‰e hone witolome.
\v 25 Otaęž‰ mo tikitiki piki tapaketaęž‰ mo hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± na lu homalipikipema. Kototaęž‰ otaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ haue. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kutupiki hau peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo da hoeyaekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo tikitiki piki tapaketaęž‰ mo hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰ tapake ameĚ±leĚ± kaęž‰ndaęž‰ pealipikie. Koto ekinaęž‰ kototaęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰ haue. Do kenke paeyaonaęž‰ pi yokaalu pitele halimaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ tikitiki yao kone peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 26 Koto leeke mo Tekehalimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo Sodomo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki pea halaęž‰ tapake 50 handoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ haunaęž‰ kone mo daoni na hoeyalueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 27 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ pi paa alo alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Pilisi IĚ±maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke pi paa alo ekinaęž‰ hone na wiaęž‰peke. IĚ±taęž‰ pa kenke hali yalo pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ lapeketaęž‰ na yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa
\v 28 mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ 50 diaęž‰ yaęž‰liaęž‰pate pa 45 tikitiki piki tapake homeke hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ 5 maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mo daoni paeyao hoeyalipikipe leekeme. Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ paa hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau na pu halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali 45 handaęž‰ uaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ na hoeyalueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ paa ombu alotaęž‰ Pa 40 tapake homeke hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ eki pilipikipe leekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ 40 tapake hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make otaęž‰ na hoeyalueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 30 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pilisi Tekehalio. IĚ±maęž‰ pi paa lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ mineke na pankaęž‰peke. Mo tapake 30 homeke hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ eki pilipikipe leekeme. Tekehalimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ 30 tapake handaęž‰ uaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ maketaęž‰ na hoeyalueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 31 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Pilisi IĚ±maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke neke paęž‰taęž‰ pi pa laęž‰tia pulu ekinaęž‰ hone na wiaęž‰peke. Mo paęž‰taęž‰ pa 20 homeke handaęž‰ wikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ eki pilipipe leekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ 20 handaęž‰ uaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make na hoeyalueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Pilisi otaęž‰ hoto homeke lotaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ mineke na pankaęž‰peke. Kiki yaapo homeke handaęž‰ wikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ eki pilipikipe leekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kiki yaapo handaęž‰ uaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make na hoeyalueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 33 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ yaapo pi lo paeyao mo Tekehali pu moneayeketaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ da laęž‰kaęž‰la peekeme.
\c 19
\s1 Sodomonaęž‰ hoke hau tieke
\p 
\v 1 Mo hande enisolo yaapo Sodomo opolo epepeketaęž‰ Lodataęž‰ mo daoninaęž‰ potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ pitiekeme. Lodamaęž‰ mo hali yaapo hando haotaęž‰ koto kone tiao handolo peekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali yaapo haepeke alenaęž‰ pua pandaęž‰puniaaso
\v 2 alotaęž‰ Hali yaapoo. IĚ±taęž‰ ipiliki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ halomaęž‰ pilisi ya da nane pomanaęž‰ ipupe. Ipilikaęž‰ anke tandepo peliaataęž‰ da kaęž‰laęž‰paasotaęž‰ timba tiao ipilikaęž‰ polo pelepe nane poepenaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme. Pate ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Dikitaęž‰ ame do timbataęž‰ do daoni wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ mombolo haleme alenaęž‰ polupekee lepekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Pate Lodamaęž‰taęž‰ mo hali yaapo honke paa laęž‰tiki pu haotaęž‰ wetepe nane ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku peekeme. Lodamaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do kimisu tapakenaęž‰ mandane betedimanu wepiao make epeke ne maęž‰ndaęž‰ wamo peape leekeme. Kutupa mo ne amu pea wieketaęž‰ nemekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Mo kimisu hali yaapo polu poluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Sodomo haliwekimaęž‰ mo da aęž‰pa popei yaemekeme. Mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke koke haliweki paeyao make paęž‰paęž‰naęž‰ weki paeyao make aęž‰pa haemekeme.
\v 5 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Loda paęž‰taęž‰ wi alo alotaęž‰ Mo neke ameĚ±leĚ± ame timba polu epeme haliwekitaęž‰ hando yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Niki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epoe lemekeme. Mo Sodomo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hali yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± loke apaęž‰taasaęž‰ hau puluekemaęž‰ lemekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Koto lemeke Lodataęž‰ hama opolu bao potaęž‰ pokaęž‰neayekeme.
\v 7 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yankeke tonuo. Dupiki temokonaęž‰ hau na piaęž‰paęž‰pee laa iki honke alome.
\v 8 Handaęž‰pe yaka moputali wandiki yaapo halaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki puemenaęž‰ hama hatuku eponoe. Pate do hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na piaęž‰paęž‰pee. Ipilikitaęž‰ yaka kimisu hali yaapo yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ handeteke hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Koto leekepate mo tapakemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali yaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ na hake wopu hae. Niki dupi dupi laa leeke hautaęž‰ neketaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ pulu pololomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pake tupaęž‰ pulumaęž‰maęž‰ wotu hae lemekeme. Mo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Loda wato lopao oni potaęž‰ kake yambuluekemaęž‰ pemekeme.
\v 10 Pate mo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pitipiki kimisu hali yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ kiki hokulu peao Loda yolaęž‰ mea oni da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ lopao potaęž‰ pokaęž‰peekeme.
\v 11 Kutupa mo hamaęž‰ nane haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ potaęž‰ na lombolo pimiki tupaęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke holu peaepekeme.
\s1 Lodamaęž‰ Sodomo minaęž‰paęž‰laeyekeeki
\p 
\v 12 Mo hali yaapomaęž‰ Loda paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi nakaęž‰ wekiwandiki tonu o nakaęž‰ mei tonu o nakaęž‰ yankeke do daoni paęž‰taęž‰ haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ na haenaęž‰ leke panane hatuku pue.
\v 13 Pa ekipeke do daonitaęž‰ dikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoeyalo polopaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ lopaęž‰me. Mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ do Sodomo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi laasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ opua do Sodomo hoeya ponoyeke diki tapaalaęž‰me lepekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Koto lepeke Lodataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandiki yaapo mulu pimiki haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ do da hoeyaliekemaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao otaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± yopupe leekepate mo haliwekinaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Lodamaęž‰ pa telepo alo alaęž‰maęž‰ hone wimikime.
\p 
\v 15 Da kelepolo haenaęž‰ mo enisolo yaapomaęž‰ Loda ipupulaaso alotaęž‰ AĚ±iĚ± aĚ±iĚ± pie. Nakaęž‰ wandiki ankulaęž‰ ankulaęž‰ otaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± hatuku pue. Pa ekipeke mo daoni hoeyaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki na homolo peleme tupaęž‰ lopaęž‰me lepekeme.
\v 16 Pate Lodamaęž‰taęž‰ kiao tapeke nono pieketaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ Loda aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ mo hali yaapomaęž‰ Loda make ipikaęž‰ waneke ankula ankula paeyao kikimaęž‰ mea hatuku mo daoni minaęž‰paęž‰lao pemekeme.
\v 17 Kutupa mo enisolo maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki weiya honkopu hao pototo laa pupe. Na handaęž‰neake make mo hawetenaęž‰ na pua hando hapaęž‰peke. Iki na lulu paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ oli pote paęž‰taęž‰manu pindipa pupe leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Pate Lodamaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Someo. Pilisi otaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupiki hau na piomono lapee.
\v 19 IĚ± aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± homaamaęž‰naęž‰ yeke otaęž‰ tambaęž‰ mipipate pa mo pote manutaęž‰ papate yalo hataęž‰ koto pate aĚ±iĚ± na opolo peke hano mo hoeyalo paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ IĚ± aęž‰pa teliminiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ homulueke.
\v 20 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo koto hosiki daoni sikitaęž‰ handelepe laa mo daonitaęž‰ pa hosiki da siki yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ± na homolo polo tupaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ pono lae leekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Mo enisolomaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ aowe alomaęž‰ koto daoni na hoeyalueke.
\v 22 Otaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± aĚ±iĚ± la aĚ±iĚ±ya pupema. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki mopate aĚ±iĚ± na opolo peke haminaęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na pulueke leekeme. Lodamaęž‰ koto daonitaęž‰ hosiki alesiki leeke handaa mo daoninaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Soa leekeme.
\s1 Sodomo Komoto yaapo hoeyaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 23 Mo nate opolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ Loda mo Soa da opolo peekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa koto kone Tekehalimaęž‰ talo talo hake lankaęž‰ biki solopamaęž‰ mo Sodomo pitaęž‰ Komoto daoni yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ lako leke lopenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰
\v 25 hoeyao mo hawete tieke make wandaęž‰hali paeyao make koto kenkenaęž‰ opeeke alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao make hoeyaeyekeme.
\v 26 Pate Lodanaęž‰ weteketaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ handaęž‰moneao hao ipikitaęž‰ epi punka au laa hayekeme.
\p 
\v 27 Da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso sikitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipupula pua mo hande Tekehalinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ pua hayeke alenaęž‰ paa peekeme.
\v 28 Kutupa mo Sodomo pitaęž‰ Komoto yaapo mo hawete tieke make handaęž‰niayekepate mo kenke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ po moyaĚ±laęž‰ alenaęž‰ piki nono pea lumu tieke opeekeeki handeekeme.
\v 29 Pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hande Loda hayeke daoni yaapo hoeyaeyeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ hone pa wia hataęž‰ Loda pindipa penaęž‰ leekeme.
\s1 Moaęž‰be pitaęž‰ Aęž‰mono tapake yaapo kini piekeeki
\p 
\v 30 Loda ipikitaęž‰ Soa hapeke paalaęž‰ pieketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandiki yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± pote eli paęž‰taęž‰manu pua tikene da paęž‰taęž‰ pelia haemekeme.
\v 31 Kutupa mo mupeke wandikimaęž‰ hakepiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diki mea wekiwandiki mendialo paęž‰laęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ do kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ na halaęž‰me. Kutupa make dikaęž‰ apaęž‰taęž‰ koke yalaęž‰me.
\v 32 Koto ekinaęž‰ dikaęž‰ apaęž‰ hoke ikali na keaenaęž‰ laa ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± polupaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ wekiwandiki mondupanaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 33 Koto timbataęž‰ ipiki waini ikali nenaęž‰ halaataęž‰ mo mupeke wandiki ateke yaapo peliekepate mo ateketaęž‰ ikali tieke neekeeki yalo ipikitaęž‰ hone na wiekeme.
\p 
\v 34 Mo da maęž‰ndaęž‰ kelepeeketaęž‰ mo mupeke wandikimaęž‰ hakepiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ambaneke timbataęž‰ ipiki yaapo IĚ± poluaęž‰maęž‰ ame timbataęž‰ neke poluepenaęž‰ ikali paa nenaęž‰ lopanaęž‰e. Kutu pupaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ diki telipunaęž‰maęž‰ dikaęž‰ apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ weki mondupanaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 35 Koto ekinaęž‰ koto timbataęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ ateke ikali nenaęž‰ laa mo wetepe nane wandiki ateke yaapo pelipipikime. Kutupa ateketaęž‰ ikali tieke ombu neekeeki yalo hone na wiekeme.
\v 36 Koto hau pipiki ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Lodanaęž‰ waneke yaapotaęž‰ weki loke lombaęž‰alu pipikime.
\v 37 Mo titinaęž‰ wandikimaęž‰ weki mendieketaęž‰ ipiki bikitaęž‰ Moaęž‰be leekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ ame do Moaęž‰be wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ apaęž‰meie.
\v 38 Mo wetepenaęž‰ wandikimaęž‰ make weki ombu mendieketaęž‰ ipiki bikitaęž‰ Benami leekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ ame do Aęž‰mono wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ apaęž‰meie.
\c 20
\s1 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰ Abimeleke yaapo
\p 
\v 1 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Maęž‰mote minaęž‰paęž‰lao Keinaninaęž‰ kaęž‰waęž‰ nanemaęž‰ tilao mo Keidese make Siaęž‰e kenke yaapo tukikinaęž‰ pua pitiekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kita kenke paęž‰taęž‰ pua hataęž‰ Setataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ beliki leekeme. Koto leeke handa mo Kita kenkenaęž‰ kini Abimelekemaęž‰ Setataęž‰ hatuku ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 3 Timba maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo some paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ upamaęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ do ambaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰ mele ekinaęž‰ neke homilipikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Pate Abimeleketaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ na epeeke ekinaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. IĚ±taęž‰ hokeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na polomaęž‰ IĚ± make yaka wandaęž‰hali make hoeyalipikipe.
\v 5 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ anaęž‰e leeke handa mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ make homeke pi kone leaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do hautaęž‰ yaka honemaęž‰ tikitiki pieke handa dupiki hau puaęž‰me. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na polome leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ upamaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Otaęž‰e. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ tikitiki pieke handaa pi ekinaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau pilipiki yeke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ na wataalenaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliki paęž‰taęž‰ paa halaęž‰peke. Mo halitaęž‰ potopede hali halekenaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ nekenaęž‰ yeni peayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neke na homilipikie. Pate mo wandaęž‰ pa na halekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neke kinki pitolomaęž‰ laa neke make nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make homilimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Da kelepeeketaęž‰ Abimeleke ipikaęž‰ you haliweki wi laęž‰ mepi pea mo piekeeki la haleeke handaa mo haliwekitaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme.
\v 9 Kutupa Abimelekemaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ wi laęž‰ mea alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ dotaęž‰ ekipiki hau pea pelepe. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ make yaka kilu tombuao halo paęž‰taęž‰ do hoeyaapekeeki epenaęž‰ leke hautaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ ekipiki ataęž‰kaęž‰ poleke pelepe. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ do IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pele ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na peaęž‰peke hau peleme.
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰ ekipeke do hau pea pelepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ do pate Kodaęž‰ paalaęž‰piki some maęž‰ndaęž‰ na halieke hone wia yaka wandaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ IĚ± limikie hone uaęž‰me.
\v 12 Pate mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ yaka anaęž‰e. Ipikitaęž‰ yaka apaęž‰naęž‰ waneke yaęž‰laęž‰pate amaęž‰ homeke taęž‰taęž‰e. Kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mea polome.
\v 13 Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± yaka apaęž‰naęž‰ da minaęž‰paęž‰lao maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ kenke paęž‰taęž‰ pu leeke pulutaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± oto paęž‰taęž‰ haleeki walolo hataęž‰ paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ anaęž‰e lapeke laa loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Kutupa Abimelekemaęž‰ Setataęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paa halolo hataęž‰ make homeke dinaęž‰ konetaęž‰ sipisipimanu make kaomanu make pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make apaęž‰tao haleekeme.
\v 15 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ yaka kenkemaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ hae leekeme.
\v 16 Kutupa Seta paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo neke ameĚ±leĚ± haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ neketaęž‰ hokeeki na ulaęž‰me laa waloelenaęž‰ make hokeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na peleme hone winaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mo silipa manimanu 1 daoseni do halolo handaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 17-18 Kutupa mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ weteke Seta paęž‰taęž‰ pieke ekinaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Abimelekenaęž‰ kini da paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰manu paeyaotaęž‰ weki mendiaęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ piekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Abimelekenaęž‰ yeni peayeke handa epeayekeme. Kutupa make mo ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ make mo ipikaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaemeke wandiki titi make weki mendinaęž‰ yeke epeayekeme.
\c 21
\s1 Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ mendiekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ wieke tupaęž‰ kone Seta epeayeketaęž‰
\v 2 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koke yaęž‰naęž‰ kone Setamaęž‰ weki loke lomba Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ hali weki mendiaeyekeme. Mo wekitaęž‰ hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mendiliekee laa laęž‰ wieke natenaęž‰ kone mendiekeme.
\v 3 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke leekeme.
\v 4 Kutupa mo weki nate ketepo hataęž‰ mieketaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ piaęž‰peke laa leeke tupaęž‰ sekemesaisi hau peayekeme.
\v 5 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ 100 bapi mieketaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke mendiekeme.
\v 6 Setamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki make ki talaęž‰eki make mea aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰mee. Epi amedamaęž‰ doeki opiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ ki talimikie.
\v 7 Kutupa pa pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ ombu alo alotaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Setamaęž‰ wekiwandiki andu haliaęž‰pe pitaęž‰ epimaęž‰ lolo piaęž‰pe. Kutu pinaęž‰ kone ipikitaęž‰ koke halinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ weki mendiawalome leekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Kutupa mo weki daeyaataęž‰ andu nalaęž‰eki minaęž‰paęž‰laeyeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ne tieke pambaeyekeme.
\s1 Heika pitaęž‰ Isimaęž‰elo yaapo tapaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 9 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ mo Idiepi wandaęž‰ Heikamaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ mendiaeyeke weki Isimaęž‰elotaęž‰ Setanaęž‰ eiyeke Aisaęž‰ke yaapo telepo lo pitipikime.
\v 10 Kutu pieke Setamaęž‰ moeki hando hao Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eiyeke yaapo tapae. Do wandaęž‰naęž‰ eiyekemaęž‰taęž‰ mo yaka weki Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ nakaęž‰ anketeke mulu paęž‰laęž‰ ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ na minaęž‰ lapeke leekeme.
\v 11 Doeki leeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme. Pa ekipeke Isimaęž‰elo make ipikaęž‰ wekie hone wieke ekimaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 12 Pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo nakaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Heika make mo weki Isimaęž‰elo yaaponaęž‰ pomomaęž‰ na homaęž‰peke. Mo Setamaęž‰ piaęž‰ alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ peaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke mo IĚ±maęž‰ pi laęž‰ uaęž‰ tupaęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipilieke.
\v 13 Kutupa make mo pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ make wekiwandiki wopu halaa tutu tieke halieke. Pa ekipeke mo weki make nakaęž‰ weki yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso sikitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Heika paęž‰taęž‰ ne make mo kao yonkelekemaęž‰ wepiki ikali kanakenaęž‰ ikali no tumbao haleekeme. Kutupa mo wekitaęž‰ Heikanaęž‰ hokinaęž‰ tu lao penaęž‰ tapaeyekeme. Kutu pieke mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ pua mo Biasiba hapekenaęž‰ pomu lopeekeme.
\v 15 Kutupa mo ikali paeyeketaęž‰ mo wekitaęž‰ hosiki ti teke maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ winaęž‰ laa
\v 16 Heikataęž‰ mo pate leke pua pitiekeme. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Yaka weki homaęž‰laęž‰eki handaęž‰peketaęž‰ IĚ± anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme. Kutupa koto pate pitinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ eĚ± leekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ eĚ± leekeeki opua hepeni nanemaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ Heika paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Heikao. Neketaęž‰ alekenaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homelepe. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ eĚ± opiaęž‰maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰pee.
\v 18 Tiao. Pua mo weki pua hopulu mea homupeae. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do weki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ piliaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ tutu tieke hawalueke leekeme.
\v 19 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ leke ki layeketaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ naku ikali handeekeme. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ mo kao yonkelekemaęž‰ wepiki ikali kanake pua mea ikali tumbao mandanetaęž‰ mo weki haleekeme.
\v 20 Kutupa mo weki daeyaęž‰liayeke ale paęž‰taęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo weki handeteke hayekeme. Mo wekitaęž‰ mo Paęž‰tani hapekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ eiyaęž‰nalaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ handa wiki some hayekeme.
\v 21 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ inkikimaęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰taęž‰ mo Idiepi wandaęž‰ meayekeme.
\s1 Abimeleke Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ yaapomaęž‰ pi tonkaepekeeki
\p 
\v 22 Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ Abimeleketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aminaęž‰ you hali Pikolo yaapo pua Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ pitele hau paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ neke yaapo halaęž‰me.
\v 23 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolotaęž‰ IĚ± make yaka wekiwandiki make yaka mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ puluaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki make na makealueke laa laęž‰ wie. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulapelia halomaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ make hone tulapelia halueke laa laęž‰ wie leekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolome laa leekepate
\p 
\v 25 pa mo Abimelekenaęž‰ e pokaeyeke haliwekimaęž‰ pendilayeke naku ikalinaęž‰ Abimeleke paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu piekeme.
\v 26 Abimelekemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do hau paęž‰laęž‰ sometaęž‰ epipe. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± na laa keleme. Kutupa ame do siki opitolome leekeme.
\v 27 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ mandane sipisipi make kaomanu make Abimeleke haleekeme. Kutupa hali yaapomaęž‰ pi tonkao wipikime.
\v 28 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ mo wataake hataęž‰ sipisipi ikiki manutaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ sipisipi ameĚ±leĚ± na haenaęž‰ leke taęž‰taęž‰ putupa haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 29 Kotoeki handaataęž‰ Abimelekemaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto hautaęž‰ ekipeke pipe leekeme.
\p 
\v 30 Koto leeke Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do wataake hataęž‰ sipisipi ikikimanu mie. Do hau pitolopaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ do naku ikalitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ awa polome loelenaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 31 Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo hali yaapomaęž‰ pi laęž‰ wipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yalo bikitaęž‰ Biasiba lemekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Koto pi lo tonkao wiataęž‰ Abimeleke pitaęž‰ Pikolo yaapotaęž‰ mo Pilisidia kenke nane paa pepekeme.
\v 33 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Biasiba paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo napu ti homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ nokaęž‰paataęž‰ mo Pa Hao Halaęž‰ Tekehali Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ layekeme.
\v 34 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nate hokulunaęž‰ Pilisidia kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme.
\c 22
\s1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke lia kie leekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ la handuluekemaęž‰ wi alotaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰o leeke Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaasotaęž‰ Wae laa alotaęž‰ IĚ± do handaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 2 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo otaęž‰ nakaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homele homeke weki Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ hatuku mo Motaeya kenke paęž‰taęž‰ pue. Kutupa koto pate IĚ±maęž‰ waluaęž‰ potenaęž‰ nakaęž‰ weki lia IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kuelenaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso sikitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo weki lia halopieke timanu poka ipikaęž‰ donkinaęž‰ hokinaęž‰ mendiao Aisaęž‰ke make ipikaęž‰ e pokaepeke hali yaapo make hatuku peekeme. Ikitaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ la haleeke alenaęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ pemekeme.
\v 4 Nate tepo peaonaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ mo hande leeke alenaęž‰ handaęž‰ moneayekeme.
\v 5 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo e pokaepeke hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do donki ameĚ±leĚ± do pate hape. Mo weki dikitaęž‰ mo pa pate leke pua pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ lao ipiliki halipi alenaęž‰ paa ipulupekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hau pitolo yankolo pipiki titaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke mea tiao ipikitaęž‰ kaiya make mo ti noyaęž‰ piaęž‰peke ti epeleke make miniekeme. Ipiliki mandakenaęž‰ pulu hataęž‰
\v 7 Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o leekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Alekekaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme. Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo ti noyaęž‰ pulu pele ale ti epeleke pitaęž‰ ti yaapotaęž‰ handolopate mo lia halo polopaęž‰ sipisipi ikikitaęž‰ handokaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Koto leeke Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kone kilieke leekeme. Kutupa telipunaęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ pepekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Kutupa mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ la haleeke alenaęž‰ opolo aęž‰pa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ oloda aęž‰eyaataęž‰ ti manda anaęž‰ layekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki tonkao mo olodanaęž‰ ti manda wiekeme.
\v 10 Kutupa mo weki luekemaęž‰ kaiya mea minaęž‰ liaeyekepate
\v 11 mo Tekehalinaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ ya paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ wi alo alotaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰o. Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰o leekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Wae. IĚ± do handaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Koto leeke mo enisolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo weki na liki ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na piaęž‰pee. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ homeke weki homeketaęž‰ na saęž‰saęž‰ pele ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homekaęž‰taęž‰me laa hone ulume leekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ lekemaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ piekepate sipisipi halieki mo ipikaęž‰ ekeketaęž‰ ti maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ mea hopaęž‰liayekeeki handeekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki yanka halo pieke tupaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ pua mea yanka haleekeme.
\v 14 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ koto pate bikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Anaęž‰ Lao Halaęž‰me leekeme. Kutupa ame do make wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ potenaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰ lao halaęž‰me lo halememe.
\p 
\v 15 Kutupa mo Tekehalinaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ ya paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paa yaapo peao wi alo alotaęž‰
\v 16 IĚ±taęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaka bikinaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke wopu epealueke. Pa ekipeke. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ homeke weki kone na saęž‰saęž‰piki IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kuluekemaęž‰ taape ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 17 IĚ±maęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ oli yanaęž‰ halaęž‰ hombulankaęž‰ manumaęž‰ o mo ikali tiekenaęž‰ teaęž‰naęž‰ ulaęž‰ hou manumaęž‰ handenaęž‰ lolueke leekeme. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ lu bepolalimikie.
\v 18 Mo nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka pi opele ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ mo tutu paeyao sikitaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰eki minaęž‰ lolueke leekeme.
\v 19 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali yaapo haepeke alenaęž‰ pua mandakenaęž‰ mo ipiki hayeke ale Biasiba nane pemekeme.
\s1 Neihonaęž‰ tapake
\p 
\v 20 Hao hao nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ ninaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ mo hameke Neihonaęž‰ weteke Milikamaęž‰ wekiwandiki ketepo hataęž‰ mendiaeyekeeki leeketaęž‰ opiekeme.
\v 21 Mupeke weki bikitaęž‰ Usu make hameke Busu kutupa mo Aęž‰tamonaęž‰ ateke Kemuele make
\v 22 Diesede make Heiso make Pilidaęž‰se make Didilaęž‰pe make
\v 23 kutupa Lepekanaęž‰ ateke Beduelo make koto weki tonu paeyaotaęž‰ Milikamaęž‰ Neihonaęž‰ mendiaeyekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa Neihonaęž‰ yaapo peao mieke wandaęž‰ Teumamaęž‰taęž‰ Diba make Kahaęž‰me make Dahaęž‰se make Maaka make mendiekeme.
\c 23
\s1 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ hali lapaęž‰ pulu pieke kenke hambeekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Setataęž‰ bapi 127 miekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ mo Keinani da kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ Hebotoni paęž‰taęž‰ homeekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ wia pitiekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo wetekenaęž‰ toko wieke alenaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Hidi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰
\v 4 IĚ±taęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali kone iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ do halomaęž‰maęž‰ yaka wandaęž‰ hoilu polo kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ hambono tapapee leekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Mo tapakemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰
\v 6 Someo. Niki paęž‰taęž‰ opie. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ neketaęž‰ nikaęž‰ aneke halie laa handaęž‰ lialomaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰taęž‰ do nikaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke lapaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ handa hoie. Niki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondomaęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ hoiyuelenaęž‰ lapaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ pa kuluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ mo tapake paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao hataęž‰
\v 8 alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka wandaęž‰ do pate hoiyonoe lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pilisi mo Sohanaęž‰ eiyeke Epotonimaęž‰
\v 9 mo Maęž‰kaęž‰pilanaęž‰ tikene da mo ipikaęž‰ e nepoko nane ulaęž‰eki lotaęž‰ peapee. IĚ±maęž‰ yaka hali hoiyu halo polo hali lapaęž‰ wialuekemaęž‰ do ikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tapao yenki mulu paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone tapaenaęž‰ loaęž‰me laa honke lapee leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Epotonitaęž‰ mo daoni potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ pi hotu haemeke ale paęž‰taęž‰ mo mandane Hidi tapake pitieke ale paeyaomaęž‰ opitolo haenaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰
\v 11 Someo. Opie. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ koto hamaęž‰ make koto paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ tikene da make paeyao neke kulueke. Do yaka da wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ hoiyuelenaęž‰ neke kulueke laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Pate Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ mo Hidi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao paeyaomaęž‰ opitolo haenaęž‰
\v 13 mo Epotoni paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pilisi yaka pi opie. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo hama paeyao hambolomaęž‰ mo kitolo yenkitaęž‰ na kiake mie. Kutupa yaka wandaęž‰ koto pate hoilueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Koto leeke Epotonimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰
\v 15 Someo. Mo kenketaęž‰ pa 400 silipa manimaęž‰ homeke hambaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ dikitaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Pa pinaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ hoie leekeme.
\v 16 Koto leekeeki Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa mo manitaęž‰ mo bisinisi haliwekimaęž‰ tombo mu haemeke tupaęž‰ tombo mea mo Epotonimaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ da wandaęž‰hali opu haenaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ 400 silipa mani haleekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Kototaęž‰ mo hande Maęž‰motenaęž‰ nate ipulaęž‰ nanemaęž‰ Epotoninaęž‰ Maęž‰kaęž‰pila kenke Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰eki au leeke ekie. Kotaęž‰ mo hamaęž‰ make mo hamaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ wieke tikene da make mo hamaęž‰naęž‰ pu hao naeyeke timanu make alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao miekeme.
\v 18 Koto pi hotimiki ale paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa pitimiki Hidi wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ ekie laa hone wimikime.
\p 
\v 19 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weteke Seta mo Keinani da kenke paęž‰taęž‰ wieke tikene da paęž‰taęž‰ lapaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 20 Koto ekinaęž‰ koto Hidi wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hamaęž‰ kenke make tikene da make Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ hali hoitaęž‰laęž‰ kenke au leekeme.
\c 24
\s1 Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ wandaęž‰
\p 
\v 1 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ametaęž‰ otaęž‰ koke yeekeme. Kutupa mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ piekeeki paeyao epeayekeme.
\v 2 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao handeteke hayeke titinaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kiki yaka paleke yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ wia hataęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰ wie laa alotaęž‰.
\v 3 Yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Tekehali do kenke ya waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ bikinaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolotaęž‰ yaka wekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰taęž‰ do Keinani wandaęž‰ na mealueke laa laęž‰ wie.
\v 4 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo IĚ± mendiaęž‰ alenaęž‰ pua yaka tapake paęž‰taęž‰ kone mo yaka weki Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ wandaęž‰ meapeke leekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Pate mo e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Mo wandikimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da minaęž‰paęž‰lao IĚ± yaapo do kenke nane aęž‰paęž‰peke kiayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa eki puluepe laataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ wekitaęž‰ mo neke epele kenke nane penaęž‰ tapaaluepe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka weki koto nane otaęž‰ paa na penaęž‰ lapeke.
\v 7 Mo Tekehali oli hepeninaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo yaka apaęž‰naęž‰ da kenke make mo yaka tapake manunaęž‰ kenke make minaęž‰paęž‰lao IĚ± hatuku epeaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo hataęž‰taęž‰ Do kenketaęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ halueke laa leaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka wekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰ mealenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enisolo ambaęž‰la tapaalieke.
\v 8 Pate mo wandiki neke yaapo aęž‰paęž‰peke kiayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ do pi laęž‰ witele ekitaęž‰ pakaęž‰lalipikie. Pate hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ kone yaka wekitaęž‰ koto nane otaęž‰ na hatuku puaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo e pokaeyeke halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you hali Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ paleke yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ kiki witolo hataęž‰ Otaęž‰ pulueke laa pi laęž‰ wiekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Koto laataęž‰ mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao handeteke hayeke halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you somenaęž‰ kiki yaapo kemelomanu mea mo Neiho hayeke daoni mo Mesopoteimianaęž‰ okane nanemaęž‰ tilao mea peekeme.
\v 11 Kutupa ipiki mo daoni hama nane opolo puataęž‰ mo kemelo manutaęž‰ mo daoninaęž‰ naku ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ tumiki yotuao pitinaęž‰ leekeme. Kototaęž‰ nate pambolo pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ ikali nolo aęž‰paęž‰tiki pimiki nate yekeme.
\v 12 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ yeni pitolo alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Yaka you some Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰o. Yaka you some paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ wili pi peneme yaaso hataęž‰ ame IĚ±maęž‰ weitolo ale kie.
\v 13 Ametaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo hande daoni paęž‰taęž‰ haleme moputali wandiki tonumaęž‰ ikali nolo epolo peleme naku ikali paęž‰taęž‰ do halo handaęž‰e.
\v 14 IĚ±maęž‰ mo wandiki homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lolueke. Pilisio. Nakaęž‰ ikali kanake minaęž‰niao IĚ± ikali nono lae lolueke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alo hataęž‰ Ikali nae laa Nakaęž‰ kemelo manunaęž‰ ikali make mea aęž‰ponoe leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ maĚ±leke lili wandaęž‰ yaęž‰naęž‰e. Dupiki hau peaekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo yaka you some paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ wili pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulueke laa yeni koto tupaęž‰ piekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Mo hali yeni pu paeyaaso haenaęž‰taęž‰ Lepekataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ peiyokonaęž‰ ikali kanake tia opolo epeekeme. Mo wandikitaęž‰ Beduelonaęž‰ waneke yekeme. Beduelotaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ hameke Neiho pitaęž‰ weteke Milika yaaponaęž‰ eiyeke yekeme.
\v 16 Mo wandikitaęž‰ moputali pa pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ seliapo piki wandiki yeekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ oni naku ikali paęž‰taęž‰ pua ipikaęž‰ ikali kanakenaęž‰ ikali no tumbao paa epeekeme.
\v 17 Kutupa mo hande e pokaasaęž‰ hali ankeao pua mo wandiki mandaęž‰hande pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pilisi nakaęž‰ kanake paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ ikali maęž‰ndaęž‰ nono lae leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Koto leeke mo wandikimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. Nae laa Koto kone mo ipikaęž‰ peiyokonaęž‰ tieke ikali kanake minaęž‰niao ikali nenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 19 Mo halimaęž‰ ikali no paeyaeyeketaęž‰ mo wandikimaęž‰ paa alotaęž‰ Mo nakaęž‰ kemelomanu make ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ nenaęž‰ ikali mea aęž‰ponope leekeme.
\v 20 Kutupa koto kone mo wandikimaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ ikali no haleme kawaso paęž‰taęž‰ ikali paeyao hoelao pototo la oni ikali paęž‰taęž‰ ikali wopu nalo puaęž‰tiki piekeme. Kutupa mo kemelo paeyao siki ikali anaęž‰naęž‰ nenaęž‰ lo paeyaeyekeme.
\v 21 Kutu pieke handaa mo halimaęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ ipiki epealaęž‰pe laa handuluekemaęž‰ yeke yopu siki hataęž‰ mo wandiki handaake wiekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Kutupa mo wandikimaęž‰ hande kemelo manunaęž‰ ikali na halo paeyaeyeketaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ yenki tieke wiki kolomaęž‰ wepiki mineke kanake mea mo wandikinaęž‰ minekenaęž‰ pankao kutupa kolomaęž‰ ombu wepiki topaęž‰ tieke aneke yaapo mea mo wandikinaęž‰ kiki yaaponaęž‰ pitaeyekeme.
\v 23 Kutupa alotaęž‰ Pilisi nakaęž‰ apaęž‰taęž‰ epikaęž‰taęž‰pe laataęž‰ IĚ± la kie. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± make do yaka haliweki make polu polome da pandaęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ ulaęž‰pe leekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Koto leeke mo wandikimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka apaęž‰taęž‰ Neiho pitaęž‰ weteke Milika yaaponaęž‰ eiyeke Bedueloe.
\v 25 Kutupa nikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ taa maęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ napeke ambumanu make yamaęž‰peke ambu saĚ± make ulaęž‰me. Kutupa make iki peliaęž‰peke da pandaęž‰ ulaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 26 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰taęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniao yeni pitolo alotaęž‰
\v 27 Mo yaka you some Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ Tekehali Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea minaęž‰lianoe. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yaka you some paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ peneme yalaęž‰me. Mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ yaka you somenaęž‰ tapake paęž‰taęž‰ kone mea hatuku mea aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Mo wandikimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ amaęž‰naęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pototo la puataęž‰ mo hande piaęž‰ haumanu paeyao pua leekeme.
\v 29-30 Lepekanaęž‰ belikitaęž‰ Leibeni hayekeme. Mo somemaęž‰ belikinaęž‰ minekenaęž‰ pankeeke mineke kanake make kiki yaaponaęž‰ pitaeyeke topaęž‰ make handolo hataęž‰ mo leeke pi aęž‰pa mokaęž‰laeyekeeki make opiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hande Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ e pokaeyeke halitaęž‰ mo naku ikali wieke alenaęž‰ hayeke handaa poluekemaęž‰ hama opolu bao pototo laa peekeme. Kutupa opolo polutaęž‰ mo hande some ipikaęž‰ kemelo tonu ameĚ±leĚ± mo naku ikali pitieke alenaęž‰ haemekeeki pua handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 31 Nikaęž‰ pomanaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± ipupee. Neketaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ epealaęž‰ halie. Ekipeke do paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ pitelepe. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ yaka da paęž‰taęž‰ iki peliaęž‰paęž‰peke da pandaęž‰ ambaęž‰ amu pealaęž‰me. Kutupa make ikaęž‰ kemelomanu hapeke da pandaęž‰ make ulaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Koto leeke mo halitaęž‰ oni da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Kutupa Leibenimaęž‰taęž‰ mo kemelonaęž‰ hokinaęž‰ wieke alemanu mu wia napeke ambumanu make halaa ambu saĚ±manu make wiaeyekeme. Kutupa mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali make ipikaęž‰ haliweki make ikaęž‰ anke tandepenaęž‰yeke ikali honke pea haleekeme.
\v 33 Kutupa mo ne mea aęž‰paeyeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ lolueke hone witolo pi ambaęž‰la laataęž‰ ne wetepenaęž‰ nolueke leekeme. Koto leeke Leibenimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ pi lae leekeme.
\p 
\v 34 Koto leeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi kini pu mea alo alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ e pokaaso halie.
\v 35 Mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ yaka you some otaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ epeao hamoko hali haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa make ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ mo sipisipi wopu make nanikosimanu make kaomanu make silipa make kolo make pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰weki make haliweki make kemelomanu make donkimanu make halaęž‰me.
\v 36 Yaka you somenaęž‰ weteke Setataęž‰ koke ya pitaęž‰ kone hali weki mondu wialeke handaa yaka you somemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao mo weki halaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 37 Koto ekinaęž‰ yaka you somemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ Nakaęž‰ le pi otaęž‰ pulueke laa laęž‰ witolo hano loluekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witoloeki piaęž‰peke laa dupa leaęž‰me. Yaka wekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰taęž‰ mo Keinani kenkenaęž‰ halaęž‰ wandiki tonu na meaęž‰peke.
\v 38 Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ mo yaka apaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali yaka tapake paęž‰taęž‰ pua mo wekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰ meapeke leaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 39 Koto leeke IĚ±maęž‰ yaka you some lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Mo wandikimaęž‰ IĚ± yaapo aęž‰paęž‰peke kiayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ eki puluaęž‰pe laa loaęž‰me.
\v 40 Koto loaęž‰eki ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo IĚ±maęž‰ hoto paeyao siki ipikaęž‰ pi opua pu halo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enisolo neke yaapo tapaaso hataęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pu epealenaęž‰ lelieke. Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka wekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰taęž‰ mo yaka tapake yaka apaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ kone mealipikie laa leaęž‰me.
\v 41 Kutupa alotaęž‰ Do nakaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ taęž‰pao halo peleeki homeketaęž‰ neke mo yaka tapake paęž‰taęž‰ pelipipate neke kiaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ taęž‰pao halipikie laa leaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 42 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ± ame mo naku ikali paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hataęž‰ yeni dupa puaęž‰me. Yaka you hali Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ Tekehali Kodaęž‰o. Pilisi IĚ±maęž‰ do pitolo ekitaęž‰ pu epeano lae.
\v 43 Ametaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ do naku ikali paęž‰taęž‰ do halo handaęž‰e. Kutupa mo moputali wandiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ ikali noluekemaęž‰ epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ikali kanake paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ ikali maęž‰ndaęž‰ kie laa honke lolueke.
\v 44 Kutupa mo wandikimaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa make mo yaka kemelo manunaęž‰ ikali mea aęž‰paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto wandikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo yaka you halinaęž‰ eiyekenaęž‰ maĚ±leke lili wandaęž‰ yaęž‰naęž‰e laa yeni puaęž‰me.
\v 45 Koto yaka oninaęž‰ honemaęž‰ yeni pa pitolo hano kone Lepekataęž‰ ikali kanake ipikaęž‰ peiyokonaęž‰ tia oni naku ikali paęž‰taęž‰ ikali nolo yapeaęž‰me. Kutu pieke IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pilisio. IĚ± ikali kie loaęž‰me.
\v 46 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto kone mo ikali kanake minaęž‰niao hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nae laataęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kemelo manunaęž‰ ikali make mea aęž‰palueke leaęž‰me. Koto leeke IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikali noaęž‰me. Kutupa yaka kemelomanu make ikali hale hale piaęž‰me.
\v 47 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ apaęž‰taęž‰ epipe loeke handaa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka apaęž‰taęž‰ Neiho pitaęž‰ weteke Milika yaaponaęž‰ eiyeke Bedueloe leaęž‰me. Koto leeke kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ minekenaęž‰ mo mineke kanake pankao make ipikaęž‰ kiki yaaponaęž‰ mo topaęž‰ pitaowaęž‰me.
\v 48 Kutupa IĚ±taęž‰ tumiki yotuao Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ lawaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo Tekehali yaka you some Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo yaka you somenaęž‰ tapake paęž‰taęž‰ kone hatuku epeaęž‰me. Kutupa ikaęž‰ wandiki yaka you somenaęž‰ eiyekenaęž‰ handaęž‰ wiano laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki minaęž‰liawaęž‰me.
\v 49 Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka you some paęž‰taęž‰ peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu anaęž‰naęž‰ kone pulumeke hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pilisi IĚ± la kipe. Diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ pulu polo hau hone wiono aĚ±iĚ± la kipe leekeme.
\p 
\v 50 Koto leeke Leibeni pitaęž‰ Beduelo yaapomaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do hautaęž‰ mo Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ dikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupumanaęž‰e laa pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 51 Koto ekinaęž‰ Lepeka do handaęž‰e. Ipikitaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ nakaęž‰ you somenaęž‰ eiyekenaęž‰ wandaęž‰ haenaęž‰e lepekeme.
\v 52 Koto lepekeeki mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰ opu haotaęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao Kodaęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ layekeme.
\v 53 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ daumanu make loke au laasaęž‰ silipa make kolomaęž‰ wepiki alemanu make mea aęž‰paataęž‰ Lepeka haleekeme. Kutupa make mo yenki tieke peke pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu mo wandikinaęž‰ beliki inkiki yaapo haleekeme.
\p 
\v 54 Kutupa mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali make ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± pemeke haliweki make ne ikali no pelimikime. Kutupa da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso tiao alotaęž‰ Yaka you some paęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pono lae leekeme.
\p 
\v 55 Pate Lepekanaęž‰ beliki pitaęž‰ inkiki yaapomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo wandikitaęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± pula homeke o nate kiki yaapomanu pa hao epenaęž‰ lolumeke lepekepate
\p 
\v 56 mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki paęž‰taęž‰ hosiki hao pomanaęž‰e pi na lapee. Mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ yaka potaęž‰ kimisu epoaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ epeaalaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ yaka you some paęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pono lae leekeme.
\p 
\v 57 Koto leeke hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ mo wandikimaęž‰ leliaęž‰eki opumanaęž‰ wi lomanaęž‰ pipee lepekeme.
\v 58 Koto ekinaęž‰ Lepeka wi laęž‰ mea lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ do hali yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pelimikipe lepekeme. Mo wandikimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Aowe leekeme.
\p 
\v 59 Koto leeke kotaęž‰ Lepeka pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰naęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone e pokao hayeke wandaęž‰ yaapo mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali make ipikaęž‰ haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± penaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 60 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Lepeka epeaasaęž‰ pi dupa la haleekeme.
\q1 Anaęž‰o. Neketaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tapake tiekenaęž‰ amaęž‰ hapekee. Kutupa nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki tapakenaęž‰ daonimanu bepolaenaęž‰e laa lemekeme.
\p 
\v 61 Kutupa Lepeka make ipikaęž‰ moputali wandiki titi tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali ameĚ±leĚ± poluekemaęž‰ yeke tikitiki yaaso hataęž‰ mo kemelo manunaęž‰ hokinaęž‰ pitulu puataęž‰ kini pea pemekeme.
\p 
\v 62 Kutupa Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ hapu halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ mo hande Handaęž‰laęž‰ Pa Hao Halaęž‰ Halinaęž‰ Naku Ikali ulaęž‰ alenaęž‰ mo Keinani kenkenaęž‰ kaęž‰waęž‰ nanemaęž‰ aęž‰pa hayekeme.
\v 63 Ipikitaęž‰ welealo nanemaęž‰ oni pate ninaęž‰ leke potaęž‰ pomuluekemaęž‰ peekepate kemelomanu epemekeeki handeekeme.
\v 64 Kutupa Lepekamaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke epeekeeki hando haotaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ kemelo minaęž‰paęž‰lao holaęž‰paęž‰niaeyekeme.
\v 65 Kutupa mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Mo niki handaęž‰ paleke ipulaęž‰ halitaęž‰ epi yakaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme. Koto leeke mo e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ yaka you somee leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo wandikimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you akaęž‰ mea ipikaęž‰ leke popeleke aęž‰mbaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 66 Kutupa mo e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pieke hau paeyao Aisaęž‰ke la haleekeme.
\v 67 Kotaęž‰ Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ inkiki Seta hao hayeke palai da paęž‰taęž‰ Lepeka hatuku peekeme. Kutupa mo wandikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ hayekeme. Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰taęž‰ Lepeka pukimaęž‰ homeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ amaęž‰ homeeke ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mieke ekitaęž‰ Lepekamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki keĚ±iĚ± layekeme.
\c 25
\s1 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ mandane mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke tapake
\p 
\v 1 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ biki Ketuta leeke wandaęž‰ miekeme.
\v 2 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ weki tonu biki Simitani make Diokosani make Medani make Midiani make Isibake make Sua make mondu wiayekeme.
\v 3 Diokosanitaęž‰ Siba pitaęž‰ Didani yaaponaęž‰ ateke yekeme. Kutupa mo Didanimaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke tapaketaęž‰ Aęž‰sutimu make Letusimi make Leumimi make yekeme.
\v 4 Mo Midianinaęž‰ eiyeke tonutaęž‰ Epa make Epe make Haęž‰noke make Abida make Eledaha make yekeme. Do tapake paeyaotaęž‰ Ketutanaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ piki wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikie.
\p 
\v 5 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wia hayeke alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke haleekeme.
\v 6 Pate ipiki aĚ±iĚ± na homeke pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ mendiaeyeke weki tonu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu haleekeme. Kutupa koto weki tonutaęž‰ mo nate ipulaęž‰ nane Aisaęž‰ke minaęž‰paęž‰lao penaęž‰ leekeme.
\s1 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ homeeke hoimikieki
\p 
\v 7-8 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koke ya 175 bapinaęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 9 Kutu pieke mo ipikaęž‰ weki yaapo Aisaęž‰ke pitaęž‰ Isimaęž‰elo yaapomaęž‰ mo hande Hidi hali Sohanaęž‰ eiyeke Epotoninaęž‰ Maęž‰motenaęž‰ nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nanemaęž‰ wieke Maęž‰kaęž‰pila tikene da paęž‰taęž‰ lapaęž‰ pipikime.
\v 10 Koto hamaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ mo Hidi tapake paęž‰taęž‰ hambeeke hamaęž‰e. Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Seta yaapotaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ lapaęž‰ pipikime.
\v 11 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ homeke hoki nanetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epeayekeme. Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ mo Handaęž‰laęž‰ Pa Hao Halaęž‰ Halinaęž‰ Naku Ikali teke paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme.
\s1 Isimaęž‰elonaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke tapake
\p 
\v 12 Mo Setanaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaeyeke Idiepi wandaęž‰ Heikamaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ mendiaeyeke weki Isimaęž‰elonaęž‰
\v 13 weki tonu dupa mondu wiekeme. Do ipikaęž‰ weki tonu ikaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ biki laalaęž‰me. Nebeioto make Keda make Aęž‰debielo make Mibisaęž‰mo make
\v 14 Misima make Duma make Maęž‰sa make
\v 15 Hadaęž‰de make Temaęž‰ make Diede make Napisi make Kedema makee.
\v 16 Ikitaęž‰ mo 12 tapakenaęž‰ apaęž‰meie. Kutupa ikaęž‰ biki manutaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ hosiki da sunu make ikaęž‰ polumaęž‰ polumaęž‰ pimiki da paęž‰taęž‰manu make tapaęž‰ wiamaęž‰ wiamaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 17 Isimaęž‰elotaęž‰ 137 bapi hao homeekeme.
\v 18 Isimaęž‰elomaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ mo Haęž‰pila kenke pitaęž‰ Siaęž‰e kenke yaapo tukikinaęž‰ pitiekeme. Koto kenketaęž‰ Idiepi nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nanemaęž‰ mo Aęž‰sitia poluekemaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ hayekeme. Ikitaęž‰ mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ mandane mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki ameĚ±leĚ± na hake papate haemekeme.
\s1 Iso pitaęž‰ Dieikope yaaponaęž‰ mendiekeeki
\p 
\v 19 Do tamenitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ ekie.
\v 20 Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ 40 bapinaęž‰taęž‰ Beduelonaęž‰ waneke Lepeka miekeme. Beduelotaęž‰ mo Mesopoteimia kenke nanemaęž‰ Aęž‰taęž‰mia hali hayekeme. Lepekataęž‰ Leibeninaęž‰ beliki yekeme.
\v 21 Kotaęž‰ Lepekataęž‰ weki aĚ±iĚ± na mendieke handaa Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peayekeme. Kutupa mo Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yeni hombo peaasotaęž‰ Lepeka weki loke lombeekeme.
\v 22 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hone yaapo wiki weki monduluekemaęž‰ piekeme. Kutupa aĚ±iĚ± na mendiki hataęž‰ pa weleke paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ kone tonkaęž‰neli pipikime. Kutu pieke mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ dupiki haumanu ekipeke pitaęž‰laęž‰pe laa Tekehalimaęž‰ hombo peaenaęž‰ yeke lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Koto leeke mo Tekehalimaęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Tutu yaapotaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰me. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ hone u alu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ tapake yaapo mondu wilipikie. Maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ honkopu wopu halieke. Mo mupeke halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo wetepe hali oto paęž‰taęž‰ halieke laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Mo weki mulupieke nate opolo epeeketaęž‰ hone yaapo wiki weki yaapo mondu wiekeme.
\v 25 Mo titinaęž‰ wekitaęž‰ we pea make ipikaęž‰ yonkeleketaęž‰ poĚ± hapeleke daumaęž‰ handeke itiki pelipa peekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Iso leekeme.
\v 26 Mo wetepe wekitaęž‰ Isonaęž‰ anke kinuku minaęž‰paleke mendieke ekiyalo ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Dieikope leekeme. Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ 60 bapinaęž‰ mo weki yaapo mendiekeme.
\s1 Iso ipikaęž‰ mulupieke anketeke kone tapaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 27 Mo weki yaapo daeyaataęž‰ Isotaęž‰ eiyaęž‰nalaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ handa wiki some hataęž‰ mo hamaęž‰ nane pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ puki wieke some hayekeme. Pate Dieikopetaęž‰ kesemaęž‰ hataęž‰ da hao hayeke some yekeme.
\v 28 Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰taęž‰ Iso paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeekeme. Pa ekipeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Isomaęž‰ liaęž‰tiki pieke hotekemanu tendemaęž‰ homa naęž‰tiki piekeme. Pate Lepekamaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Dieikopetaęž‰ potaęž‰kaęž‰ supu yankolo pitinaęž‰ Isotaęž‰ eiyaęž‰naęž‰ hao teaęž‰maęž‰ homa opolo epeekeme.
\v 30 Kutupa Isomaęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ homolomaęž‰ mo wepiki ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ kie leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Idomo lemekeme.
\p 
\v 31 Dieikopemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± mupeke wekinaęž‰ anke teke mulu polo ekinaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ kulueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Koto leeke Isomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ homolomaęž‰ koto mupeke wekinaęž‰ mulu polo anke tekemaęž‰ IĚ± eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ na piliekemaęž‰ pa aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ alome leekeme.
\p 
\v 33 Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰laęž‰ nakaęž‰ mupeke wekinaęž‰ mulu pele anke teketaęž‰ IĚ± kulueke laa pi ambaęž‰la laęž‰ wie leekeme. Kotaęž‰ Isomaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ mo mupeke wekinaęž‰ mulu pieke anke teketaęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme.
\v 34 Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ hameke paęž‰taęž‰ betedi make mandane supu make haleekeme. Kutupa Isomaęž‰ mo ne ikali naa minaęž‰paęž‰lao tiao peekeme. Kototaęž‰ Isomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mupeke wekinaęž‰ anketeke mulu pieke ekinaęž‰ hone wieke ekitaęž‰ pa koto yekeme.
\c 26
\s1 Aisaęž‰ke Kita daoni paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Koto kenke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ hayeke dinaęž‰ epeeke teaęž‰ kimaęž‰ handekeeki paa epeekeme. Kotaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ mo Kita daoni nane mo Pilisidaini wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kini Abimeleke hayeke nane peekeme. AĚ±iĚ± na peeke haenaęž‰taęž‰
\v 2 mo Tekehalimaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Idiepi kenke nane na peke do IĚ±maęž‰ hae alo kenkenaęž‰ kone hapeke.
\v 3 IĚ±maęž‰ neke yaapo hataęž‰ neke epealuekemaęž‰ do pate hapeke. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do kenke paeyaotaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ make kia nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ make halueke. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ apaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ yaapo laęž‰ upaęž‰ pitaęž‰ paa wilieke.
\v 4 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ oli yanaęž‰ halaęž‰ hombulankaęž‰manu halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ haenaęž‰ kulueke. Kutupa iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ do kenke paeyao halueke. IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ mo tutu paeyao sikitaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰eki minaęž‰ lolueke.
\v 5 Kotaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yaka pi make yaka lo pimanu make opua miniki hayaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke epealueke laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ Kita daoni paęž‰taęž‰ hao hayekeme.
\v 7 Kutupa koto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ epi yakaęž‰taęž‰pe lemeke handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ anaęž‰e leekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰e pi na leeke ekitaęž‰ Lepekataęž‰ wandaęž‰ seliapo yalo hataęž‰ koto pate haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Lepeka muluekemaęž‰ ipiki liaamaęž‰naęž‰ laa paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ leekeme.
\v 8 Kutupa Aisaęž‰ke koto kenke paęž‰taęž‰ natemanu hosiki haenaęž‰ laa mo kini hali Abimeleketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ winido paęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰niayekepate Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰taęž‰ Lepeka telepo laęž‰tiaaso pitipekeeki handeekeme.
\v 9 Kutupa Abimelekemaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke handaęž‰ mulu penaęž‰ la alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me. Pa ekipeke nakaęž‰ anaęž‰e la pelepe leekeme. Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ Yaka wandaęž‰e loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± limikie hone uaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Abimelekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ eki hau pea pelepe. Mo yaka hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo anaęž‰naęž‰ polu piaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto hoke hau pumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ teketaęž‰ neke kone yolo piaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 11 Kutupa Abimelekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ do hali o ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ handeteke hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ lu homaenaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke epeayeke ekiyalo hataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto kenke paęž‰taęž‰ wae alemanu nokopeeketaęž‰ mo nokopeeke bapinaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pake napeke tieke miaęž‰tiki piekeme.
\v 13 Kutupa alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ wopu mutia peaęž‰eki yalo hataęž‰ otaęž‰ hamoko hali hayekeme.
\v 14 Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ sipisipi wopu make kaomanu wopu make e pokaasaęž‰ haliweki wopu make yalo hataęž‰ mo Pilisidaini tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ we pambemekeme.
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande ipikaęž‰ ateke Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ pa hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaemeke haliwekimaęž‰ awemeke naku ikalimanu pa kenke ao tumbaemekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Kutupa Abimelekemaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ niki ankulake wele ulaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lae leekeme.
\v 17 Koto ekinaęž‰ Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Kita hadipinaęž‰ palai da pua aęž‰eyekeme. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ nate mandane ekinaęž‰
\v 18 Koto patetaęž‰ mo hande Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ hayeke natenaęž‰ naku ikalimanu aweekepate Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ homeeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Pilisidaini tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ ao tumbaemekeme. Koto naku ikali manutaęž‰ Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ pa aweekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo naku ikali biki manutaęž‰ atekemaęž‰ leekeeki kone paa leekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ e pokaemeke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hadipinaęž‰ panake naku ikali awa ikali handaęž‰ wimikime.
\v 20 Kutupa mo Kita kenke paęž‰taęž‰ sipisipi handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ mo Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ sipisipi handeteke haemeke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± hankiliki yololo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do ikalitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ ekie lemeke handaa Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ mo naku ikalinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Hankilikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Kutupa Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ e pokaemeke haliwekimaęž‰ naku ikali maęž‰ndaęž‰ awemekepate koto ekinaęž‰ make ape hankiliki ombu yolemeke handaa mo naku ikalinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Aęž‰ndaęž‰ Pitaęž‰laęž‰ekie leekeme.
\v 22 Kutupa Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰taęž‰ koto pate minaęž‰paęž‰lao pua naku ikali maęž‰ndaęž‰ aweekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ hankiliki na yolemeke handaa ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Lihobodi (nikaęž‰ da pitaęž‰ Kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ Tapaalaęž‰me) leekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki do kenkenaęž‰ hamono Tekehalimaęž‰ niki kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaalaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ do patetaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰manu anaęž‰naęž‰ kone wia halumeke leekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Kotoeki hoki nanetaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ pao mo Biasiba nane peekeme.
\v 24 Koto timba Tekehalimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ apaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰e. Koto ekinaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰pee. IĚ±taęž‰ neke yaapo halome. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ mo yaka e pokaeyaęž‰ hali Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ uaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ neke epeaaso hataęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ tieke kulueke leekeme.
\v 25 Koto patetaęž‰ Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ oloda wepia Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ yeni hau piekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ palai da koto pate aęž‰eyeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaemeke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ koto pate naku ikali maęž‰ndaęž‰ awemekeme.
\s1 Aisaęž‰ke pitaęž‰ Abimeleke yaapomaęž‰ pi tonkaepekeeki
\p 
\v 26 Abimeleketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone u tiao hayeke hali Ahusaęž‰de make ipikaęž‰ aminaęž‰ you hali Pikolo ameĚ±leĚ± Aisaęž‰ke handulueke alo Kita nanemaęž‰ epemekeme.
\v 27 Koto ekinaęž‰ Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Ambaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lia nakaęž‰ kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao pue le ale pa ametaęž‰ ekipeke IĚ± handolo aęž‰pa pelemepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ Tekehalitaęž‰ neke ameĚ±leĚ± halaęž‰eki handolo hataęž‰ nikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ neke niki ameĚ±leĚ± pi tonkao umanaęž‰e. Nikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ pi dupa laęž‰ uelenaęž‰e.
\v 29 Mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ neke na hoeyaomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ niki make na hoeyalenaęž‰ pi laęž‰ uelenaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ yopu kone minaęž‰paęž‰lao poelenaęž‰ lomaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke epealaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ peneme yalaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 30 Kutupa Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ ne pambaeyeke handaa ne ikali nemekeme.
\v 31 Da kelepeeketaęž‰ hali homeke homekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ la wimiki pitaęž‰ keke pimaęž‰ tonkao wimikime. Kutupa Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taloe leeketaęž‰ yankeke tonu au laa pemekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Koto natenaęž‰ kone Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ e pokaemeke haliwekimaęž‰ naku ikali maęž‰ndaęž‰ awemekeeki aęž‰pa la halolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikali handaęž‰ ulumaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 33 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto naku ikalinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Pi Laęž‰ Witaęž‰laęž‰ Ekie leekeme. Kototaęž‰ mo hande Biasiba daoni ipikaęž‰ biki mieke tupaęž‰e.
\s1 Isomaęž‰ kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo miekeeki
\p 
\v 34 Iso ipiki 40 bapi mieketaęž‰ Hidi wandaęž‰ yaapo miekeme. Ipilikitaęž‰ Bitinaęž‰ waneke Diudi make Eloninaęž‰ waneke Basemaęž‰de yekeme.
\v 35 Mo wandaęž‰ yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke pitaęž‰ Lepeka yaapo kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaepekeme.
\c 27
\s1 Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ Dieikope epeayekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ ametaęž‰ koke yaa leke holu piekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mupeke weki Iso wi laęž‰ mea alotaęž‰ Yaka wekio leekeme. Mo wekimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Wae leekeme.
\v 2 Koto leeke Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ IĚ± koke ya homolo poloeki teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do handele handaęž‰e.
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ semoko aęž‰ndeli mea oni hapekenaęž‰ pua hoteke maęž‰ndaęž‰ lia aęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 4 Kutupa mo yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰ tendepiki ne yankao IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ mea aęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutupa naa pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo IĚ± homuluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰ yaka paeyaaso epeaasaęž‰eki neke kuluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Kutupa Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ Iso paęž‰taęž‰ pi la haleeketaęž‰ Lepekamaęž‰ opu hayekeme.
\v 6 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ apaęž‰maęž‰ Iso paęž‰taęž‰ leaęž‰eki IĚ±maęž‰ dupa opolome.
\v 7 Hoteke maęž‰ndaęž‰ mea aęž‰pa yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰ tendepiki ne yankapeke. Kutupa naa pitaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± homuluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ yaka epeaasaęž‰eki kuluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me leaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 8 Kutupa Lepekamaęž‰ ombu alotaęž‰ Yaka wekio. Ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo pi opua pie.
\v 9 Oni maęž‰naęž‰manu halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua panka wiki nanikosi ikiki yaapo mea epoe. Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo halaęž‰ ne yankaluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 10 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ nenaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mea pekenaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiki homuluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ neke kinaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Pate Dieikopemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ amaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Isotaęž‰ itiki pelipa paęž‰laęž‰pate yaka loketaęž‰ homu paęž‰laęž‰me laa hone wilime.
\v 12 Maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ yaka apaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± watao IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki makeaasomaęž‰ laa IĚ± handaęž‰ wiaapaęž‰naęž‰e. Dupuaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo epeaasaęž‰eki minaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ paa yaka kone IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ esihou pi mea epenaęž‰ lapeke yeke loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Koto leeke ipikaęž‰ amaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Yaka wekio. Koto ipiliaęž‰ esihou pi manutaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰maęž‰ pa mo IĚ±maęž‰ aloeki pua pie. Mo nanikosi yaapo pua meawae leekeme.
\v 14 Koto leeke Dieikopemaęž‰ mo nanikosi yaapo mulu pua inkiki paęž‰taęž‰ mea epeekeme. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ atekemaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeeke nemaęž‰ handekeeki yankaeyekeme.
\v 15 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ oni da paęž‰taęž‰ Isonaęž‰ amu pea wiayeke dau manutaęž‰ mea Dieikopenaęž‰ pambawaeyekeme.
\v 16 Mo nanikosi yaaponaęž‰ yonkeleke manutaęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ kiki yaaponaęž‰ pambawaeyeke make kutupa ipikaęž‰ itiki na pelieke alenaęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ pambawaeyekeme.
\v 17 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo weki paęž‰taęž‰ mo tendepiki ne make mo yankeeke betedi make haleekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Kutupa Dieikope ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o leekeme. Atekemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Wae. Neketaęž‰ weki epi yakaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Dieikopemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ mupeke weki Isoe. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ hande peaęž‰pekee le hau pealome. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo epeaasaęž‰ ekimanu IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kuelenaęž‰maęž‰ pilisi tiao pitaęž‰ mo IĚ±maęž‰ mea aęž‰palo hoteke nae leekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Koto leeke Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka wekio. Ekipa aĚ±iĚ± handaęž‰ wia pelepe leekeme. Dieikopemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo Tekehali nakaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰ wiono IĚ± tambaęž‰ miaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pilisio. IĚ±maęž‰ neke wataalo polo tupaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ epoe. Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ Iso kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 22 Dieikopetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ pitiaęž‰ alenaęž‰ paa teke paęž‰taęž‰ pua pitiekeme. Kutu pieke atekemaęž‰ watao alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maketaęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰pate pa nakaęž‰ kikitaęž‰ Isonaęž‰ kiki wataake nono paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 23 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Dieikopee laa na handaęž‰ wieke ekitaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ kiki manutaęž‰ Isonaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handa itiki pelipa peeke ekimaęž‰ piekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ ekimanu teke paęž‰taęž‰ haluekemaęž‰ pitiekepate kone
\v 24 paa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ Iso kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme. Mo wekimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Aowe IĚ±e leekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Kotaęž‰ Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo mandane hoteke mea aęž‰pae. Naa pitaęž‰taęž‰ yaka epeaasaęž‰eki neke paęž‰taęž‰ kulueke leekeme. Koto leeke Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ ne mea aęž‰pao make nolo pieke waini ikali make mea aęž‰paeyekeme.
\v 26 Kutupa mo weki paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka wekio. IĚ± teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa IĚ± nunu pie leekeme.
\v 27 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ateke nunu pulueke alo hataęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ epeaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ mo yameeke akaęž‰manu totopo mu hao ipikaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ ekimanu haleekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Do yaka wekinaęž‰ totopo epeke pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo hande Tekehalimaęž‰ epealaęž‰ hamaęž‰naęž‰ totopomaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me.
\q1 
\v 28 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ oli ya nanemaęž‰ ekepipidaęž‰ kitolo nakaęž‰ hamaęž‰manu ne tieke winaęž‰e. Kutupa widi make waini ikali make wopu kinaęž‰e.
\q1 
\v 29 Tutu manutaęž‰ nakaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ tapake haenaęž‰e. Kutupa wandaęž‰hali neke paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniaenaęž‰e. Nakaęž‰ tapake paeyao handeteke halenaęž‰e. Nakaęž‰ amaęž‰naęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikimaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniaenaęž‰e.
\q1 Mo neke paęž‰taęž‰ esihou tunkilimi tapaketaęž‰ esihou paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰e. Kutupa neke epealimi wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ iki make epeaasaęž‰eki minaęž‰e laa leekeme.
\s1 Isomaęž‰ Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰eki honke leekeeki
\p 
\v 30 Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰eki halaa Dieikope pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke eiyaęž‰naęž‰ hao hondaęž‰ pambolo epeekeme.
\v 31 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make tendepiki ne yankao ateke paęž‰taęž‰ mea pua alotaęž‰ Pilisi apaęž‰o. Mo nakaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰eki IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kuelenaęž‰yeke IĚ±maęž‰ do mea aęž‰palo hoteke maęž‰ndaęž‰ noelenaęž‰ tiao pitie leekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ mupeke weki Isoe leekeme.
\p 
\v 33 Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ tolaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰ pututu liaaso alotaęž‰ Mo hoteke lia IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ mea epeaęž‰taęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Neke ambaęž‰ do hondaęž‰ pambolo ipuluekemaęž‰ halenaęž‰ kone noaęž‰me. Yaka paeyaaso epeaaso ekitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ haloaęž‰maęž‰ ametaęž‰ otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰eki homeke u halieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 34 Isomaęž‰ doeki opu haotaęž‰ kaęž‰paęž‰puki yoka anekemaęž‰ eĚ± wi tieke alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. IĚ± make nakaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰eki kie laa honke leekeme.
\p 
\v 35 Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kamemaęž‰ IĚ± aęž‰pa makeaaso nakaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰eki mea pu monealaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 36 Isomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoto yaapo peao IĚ± makealaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki Dieikopetaęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰piki tupaęž‰ laa pimikaęž‰taęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yaka mupeke wekinaęž‰ anke teke mulu poloeki make mea ametaęž‰ yaka epeaasaęž‰eki make mea pua pikaęž‰taęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ epeaasaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na pankaęž‰ wialepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 37 Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ neke ankulao you haenaęž‰ laa ipikaęž‰ tapakemanu maketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ tapake haenaęž‰ loaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ widi make waini ikali make haloaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ yaka wekio. Neke paęž‰taęž‰ pulu polo ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 38 Koto leekepate kone Isomaęž‰taęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ honke ombu alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. Mo epeaasaęž‰eki homeke siki make otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wilipe. Apaęž‰o. IĚ± make epeae alo hataęž‰ eĚ± leekeme.
\p 
\v 39 Kotaęž‰ Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Oli ya nanemaęž‰ ekepipidaęž‰ neke maęž‰ndaęž‰ na kinaęž‰e. Kenke epeke wiki hamaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me.
\v 40 Neketaęž‰ nakaęž‰ bainasi yaapo hao pelipikie. Pate neketaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kamenaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ hali halipikie.
\q1 Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate wetepenaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ liataęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ handeteke haliaęž‰eki pendulu bao pelipikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 41 Atekemaęž‰ mo hande epeaasaęž‰eki hameke paęž‰taęž‰ haleeke handaa Isomaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikope honditi piekeme. Ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka apaęž‰taęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ homolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homaęž‰ da pitulu polo ekitaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ Dieikope homenaęž‰ lulueke hone wiekeme.
\p 
\v 42 Pate Lepekamaęž‰ Isonaęž‰ pulueke leeke ekimanu ambaęž‰ opu hao Dieikope epoaęž‰ la alotaęž‰ Opie. Nakaęž‰ kame Isomaęž‰taęž‰ hombo peaaso hataęž‰ neke lu homalueke alaęž‰me.
\v 43 Koto alaęž‰maęž‰ yaka wekio. IĚ±maęž‰ pie aloeki piaęž‰peke. Mo yaka anaęž‰ Leibeni halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ Hatani nane ame do kone pue.
\v 44 Kutupa ipiki yaapo hosiki haotaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ kamenaęž‰ mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰eki uniao
\v 45 ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ peleeki hone yonkaęž‰laenaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Kutupa neke handaęž‰ mulu epenaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ tapaalueke. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ pa ekipeke yaka weki yaapo homeke natenaęž‰ alupaluaęž‰pe leekeme.
\s1 Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ Dieikope Leibeni paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 46 Lepekamaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do Isonaęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo handaęž‰peketaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ ki tieke pea sokaęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Dieikopemaęž‰ make do Hidi wandiki tonu maęž‰ndaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ homaęž‰peke make yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\c 28
\p 
\v 1 Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ Dieikope wi la taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa alotaęž‰ Keinani wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na miaęž‰peke.
\v 2 Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ mei Beduelonaęž‰ da kenke Mesopoteimia nane pua mo nakaęž‰ awaęž‰ Leibeninaęž‰ waneke tonu maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo meaęž‰peke.
\v 3 Kutupa neketaęž‰ tutu eleke elekenaęž‰ apaęž‰ halenaęž‰ yeke mo Aneke Wele Wopupiki Kodaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ milipi paęž‰taęž‰ neke epeaaso hataęž‰ wekiwandiki wopu kinaęž‰e.
\v 4 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ epeaaso piaęž‰ tupaęž‰ neke make nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paeyao epeaenaęž‰e. Kutupa make do neke hae kenketaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ haleaęž‰ kenke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ muelenaęž‰e.
\v 5 Kutupa Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ Dieikopetaęž‰ mo Iso pitaęž‰ Dieikope yaaponaęž‰ inkiki Lepekanaęž‰ beliki Aęž‰taęž‰mia hali Beduelomaęž‰ mondu wieke hali Leibeni hayeke alenaęž‰ mo Mesopoteimia nane penaęž‰ tapaeyekeme.
\s1 Isomaęž‰ wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ miekeeki
\p 
\v 6 Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikope epeao mo Mesopoteimia nane wandaęž‰ weilu penaęž‰ tapaeyekeeki Isomaęž‰ opiekeme. Kutupa make Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ mo weki epeaaso hataęž‰ Keinani wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na meaęž‰peke leekeeki opiekeme.
\v 7 Kutupa make Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ yaaponaęž‰ pi opua Mesopoteimia nane ambaęž‰ peekeeki opiekeme.
\v 8 Koto opiekeeki manumaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ atekemaęž‰ mo Keinani wandaęž‰weki otaęž‰ kiayekeeki hando hao
\v 9 Isomaęž‰taęž‰ mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke Isimaęž‰elonaęž‰ waneke Mahalaęž‰di mulu peekeme. Mahalaęž‰ditaęž‰ Nebeiotonaęž‰ beliki yekeme.
\s1 Dieikopemaęž‰ Bedele da upa piekeeki
\p 
\v 10 Dieikopetaęž‰ Biasiba minaęž‰paęž‰lao Hatani poluekemaęž‰ peekeme.
\v 11 Nate pambolo pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ ale maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ opolo aęž‰paataęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ peliekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ mo toopinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ lia polueke alo polu holepeekeme.
\v 12 Kutupa upa pitolotaęž‰ potaęž‰ lapaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ wia aęž‰pa yotuao oli ya nane pekeeki handeekeme. Mo potaęž‰ lapaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ enisolomanu olinaęž‰ puaęž‰tiki oninaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰tiki pimikieki handeekeme.
\v 13 Kutupa mo Tekehalitaęž‰ ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke yaaponaęž‰ Tekehali Kodaęž‰e. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do neke pelipaęž‰lia hale kenketaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ make kia nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ make halueke.
\v 14 Ikitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ na yataęž‰peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ dokolo paeyaomaęž‰ handilimikie. Ikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ da kenketaęž‰ do kenke nepoko paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ putupolo baalieke. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ make tutu paeyao epealueke.
\v 15 Niminalo pele ekitaęž‰ dupae. IĚ±taęž‰ neke yaapo mandakenaęž‰ hataęž‰ hane pekenaęž‰ make neke handeteke halueke. Kutupa neketaęž‰ do kenke paęž‰taęž‰ paa hatuku ipulueke. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo pi laęž‰ ulueki paeyaaluekemaęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lalueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Dieikopemaęž‰ u tiao alotaęž‰ Mo Tekehalitaęž‰ do hayaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ do pate haenaęž‰ kone hone na wia puaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me leekeme.
\v 17 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ palaęž‰ haaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ otaęž‰ paalaęž‰piki alenaęž‰e laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ da yalo paęž‰laęž‰me. Oli hepeni nane pulaęž‰ potaęž‰ kake lombaęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ yalo paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Kutupa otaęž‰ da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso siki Dieikope tiao mo ipikaęž‰ hande kaęž‰ndaęž‰ lia pelieke toopitaęž‰ hone u tialo piekeeki mea nokopeekeme. Kutupa mo toopi mandataęž‰ olipi oeta holaa alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ ekie leekeme.
\v 19 Kutupa koto patetaęž‰ Bedele leekeme. Koto patetaęž‰ ambaęž‰taęž‰ Lusu lemeke alenaęž‰e.
\v 20 Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ IĚ± yaapo haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo IĚ± pulu potaęž‰ kimisutaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ handeteke hao ne make akaęž‰ make kikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 21 kutupa IĚ± paa yaka apaęž‰naęž‰ da nane epeke tupaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la yapono lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ yaka Kodaęž‰ yelieke.
\v 22 Kutupa do paa hone uaęž‰tiki poluekemaęž‰ nokopolo toopitaęž‰ mo neke paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao yeiyaęž‰ lalo polo alenaęž‰e. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo IĚ± kilipi ale paeyaotaęž‰ putupa kiki homekenaęž‰ mandane tonkoputaęž‰ yaka minolo homeketaęž‰ neke kulueke leekeme.
\c 29
\s1 Dieikope Leibeninaęž‰ da opolo peekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Dieikope ipikaęž‰ potaęž‰ kini pea pua mo nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nanemaęž‰ kenke nane pulu ombu hayekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa paa peekepate nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pa mone wieke naku ikali maęž‰ndaęž‰ pua handaęž‰ wiekeme. Kutupa sipisipi tapake tepo mo naku ikali hopaęž‰liao pelia yapemekeeki handeekeme. Mo naku ikali kakenaęž‰taęž‰ toopi tiekemaęž‰ mea aęž‰mbaemekeme. Mo koto ikalitaęž‰ mo sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu ikali no halo haemekeekie.
\v 3 Kutupa mo tapake tapake paeyaonaęž‰ sipisipimanu paeyao koto homeke alenaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰tiki pimikitaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo sipisipi handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo toopi aneke mea petepete yao ikali no halaęž‰tiki pimikime. Kutupa paeyeketaęž‰ mo hande toopi paa mea wiaęž‰tiki pimikime.
\v 4 Dieikopemaęž‰ mo sipisipi handeteke haemeke haliweki lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Yaka yankeke tonuo. Ikitaęž‰ hane tapake yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Hatani nanee lemekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neihonaęž‰ eiyeke Leibenitaęž‰ handelemepe leeke mo tapakemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aowe. Handolomaęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Koto leeke alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ halaęž‰pe leekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ halaęž‰me. Handaęž‰taa. Ipikaęž‰ waneke Leisolotaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ sipisipimanu mea koto ipulaęž‰ handaęž‰e lemekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Koto lemeke Dieikopemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nate pa halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mo sipisipimanu mea aęž‰paęž‰peke nate aĚ±iĚ± diaęž‰maęž‰ ikali hala ambumanu nenaęž‰ paa na hatuku pulimipe leekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Mo tapakemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kotoeki aĚ±iĚ± na pikitaęž‰ mo sipisipi paeyao anaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰pa haenaęž‰ laa mo toopi petepete yaotaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikali no halumeke lemekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Dieikopetaęž‰ mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± pi pa alo haenaęž‰ Leisolotaęž‰ mo sipisipimanu ameĚ±leĚ± opolo epeekeme.
\v 10 Kutu pieke Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo aweke Leibeninaęž‰ sipisipimanu pitaęž‰ Leisolo epeaęž‰eki hataęž‰taęž‰ oni naku ikali paęž‰taęž‰ pua mo toopi mea petepete yao mo sipisipimanu ikali no hale hale piekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo wandiki nunu pitolo hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ pitolo kone eĚ± leekeme.
\v 12 Kutupa mo wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Lepekanaęž‰ eiyeke nakaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ tapakee leekeme. Koto leeke mo wandikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ lolueke alo aĚ±iĚ±ya peekeme.
\v 13 Kutupa atekemaęž‰ mo belikinaęž‰ eiyeke Dieikope epeekeeki opu haotaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya mandaęž‰hande pulu pua hopula nunu piekeme. Kutupa mo da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epeekeme. Kotaęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰ Leibeni paęž‰taęž‰ mo piekeeki paeyao la haleeke handa
\v 14 Leibenimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aowe. Otaęž‰e. Neketaęž‰ yaka loke homeke make we homekee leekeme. Kutupa Dieikopetaęž‰ sumbaęž‰ homeke koto paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme.
\s1 Dieikopemaęž‰ Leibeninaęž‰ e pokaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 15 Leibenimaęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ ya wandaęž‰maęž‰ mendiki yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yaka e pahameke pokaalueke hone na wikitaęž‰ yenki dupa mulueke laa lakie leekeme.
\v 16 Leibeninaęž‰ wandiki yaapo hayekeme. Mupeke wandikitaęž‰ Lia yekeme. Wetepe wandikitaęž‰ Leisolo yekeme.
\v 17 Lianaęž‰ leketaęž‰ u homeekepate Leisolotaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ lombeke wandiki seliapo yekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ Leisolo hone wopu pieke handa alotaęž‰ Yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± Leisolo miono lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ e bapi wataake hataęž‰naęž‰ pokaalueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Leibenimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halo polo tupaęž‰taęž‰ epeke ekitaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ homeke kuluekemaęž‰ IĚ± yaapo do pate hapanaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 20 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ Leisolo mulueke alo hataęž‰taęž‰ bapi wataake hataęž‰naęž‰ e pokeekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Leisolo pukimaęž‰ homeekeeki yalo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo bapi manutaęž‰ pa nate tepo aęž‰ndaęž‰ hone wiekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰ Leibeni paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande natetaęž‰ do maęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandiki miono lae leekeme.
\v 22 Koto ekinaęž‰ Leibenimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ natenaęž‰ ne pambolo hataęž‰ paeyaosiki wi leekeme.
\v 23 Pate koto timbataęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ Leisolo na hatuku peketaęž‰ Lia hatuku peekeme. Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandiki yaapo loke apaęž‰taeyekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa Leibenimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandiki Lianaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ wandiki ipikaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandiki Silipataęž‰ Lia paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme.
\v 25 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ timba ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo peliolome hone wiekepate da kaęž‰laęž‰paasotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ Lia yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa hande wiekeme. Kutupa ipiki Leibeni paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ do hautaęž‰ ekipeke pea pipe. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Leisolo muluekemaęž‰ e poka puaęž‰maęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ekipeke makeao pipee leekeme.
\p 
\v 26 Leibenimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo mupeke wandiki pa haenaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ wandiki ambaęž‰la halinaęž‰ da penaęž‰ alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do da hau diaęž‰me.
\v 27 Koto ekinaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ paa bapi wataake hataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ yaka e paa pokaalenaęž‰ kotaęž‰ do pula homeke mo ne pambaęž‰laęž‰eki paenaęž‰ laa Leisolo make neke kuluekemaęž‰ hando hae leekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Dieikopemaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ mo ne pambeeke pula homeke paeyeketaęž‰ Leibenimaęž‰ waneke Leisolo make Dieikopenaęž‰ wandaęž‰ haenaęž‰ haleekeme.
\v 29 Leibenimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandiki Bilihataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandiki Leisolonaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ wandiki haenaęž‰ haleekeme.
\v 30 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ Leisolo yaapo make loke apaęž‰taeyekeme. Kutupa telipunaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeekepate Leisolotaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ wopu homeekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ paa bapi wataake hataęž‰ Leibeninaęž‰ e paa pokaeyekeme.
\s1 Dieikopenaęž‰ mendiaeyeke wekiwandiki
\p 
\v 31 Dieikopemaęž‰ Liataęž‰ Leisolo pieke tupaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ wopu na homeeke handaa mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ Liataęž‰ wekiwandiki mendinaęž‰ leekepate Leisolotaęž‰ weki kenohali hayekeme.
\v 32 Liataęž‰ weki loke lomba hali weki mondu wiekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ yaka kaęž‰ndaęž‰ handa IĚ± tambaęž‰ maęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yaka halikimaęž‰taęž‰ ametaęž‰ IĚ± pukimaęž‰ homilieke leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Lubeni leekeme.
\v 33 Weki loke paa lomba hali weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ mondu wiekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya halikimaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ na homaęž‰laęž‰eki Tekehalimaęž‰ opu hao do weki kaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Simiono leekeme.
\v 34 Mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ weki loke paa lomba hali weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ ombu mondu wiekeme. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ yaka halikinaęž‰ weki tepo mondu wialo ekinaęž‰ yaka halikimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo IĚ± yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pilieke laa mo wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Lipai leekeme.
\v 35 Kutupa weki loke paa lomba hali weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ ombu mondu wiekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ biki mea minaęž‰lialueke laa mo wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Diuda leekeme. Kutupa weki mondu tunkuliekeme.
\c 30
\p 
\v 1 Pate Leisolomaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikope weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na mendiaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ hakepiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkulolo hataęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± homuluekemaęž‰ wekiwandiki kie leekeme.
\p 
\v 2 Koto leeke Dieikopetaęž‰ Leisolo yaapo mineke pankolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ topo peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa neke weki mendiaapaęž‰naęž‰ yeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ pitolo piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka weki mendialo paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ yaka pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandiki domaęž‰ peliaęž‰peke. Kutu piliaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ amaęž‰ au loluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliki paęž‰taęž‰ Biliha haleeke handa loke apaęž‰taepekeme.
\v 5 Kutupa Bilihataęž‰ weki loke lomba Dieikopenaęž‰ hali weki mendiaeyekeme.
\v 6 Leisolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ telipolo hataęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± maĚ±leke lilaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yaka puaęž‰ yeni opua weki kaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Daęž‰ni leekeme.
\v 7 Kutupa Bilihataęž‰ weki loke paa lomba ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ yaapo peao weki mondu wiayekeme.
\v 8 Kutu pieke handaa Leisolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ yaka asi yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke puaęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ bepolalo ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Naęž‰petali leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Kutupa Liamaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki weki mondulu piekeeki tunkuliekeeki hando haotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandiki Silipataęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰ weteke au laenaęž‰ haleekeme.
\v 10 Kutupa Silipamaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ hali weki mendiaeyekeme.
\v 11 Kotaęž‰ Liamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epekeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa mo wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Kaęž‰de leekeme.
\v 12 Kutupa Silipamaęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ hali weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ mendiaeyeke ekinaęž‰
\v 13 Liamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tieke wopu paęž‰laęž‰me. Ametaęž‰ wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰e lelimikie laa ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Aęž‰sia leekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Mo hande widi kinaęž‰taęž‰ Lubenitaęž‰ oni e paęž‰taęž‰manu pua mo maęž‰ndaęž‰teiki leke ti kiliki handaęž‰ wia ipikaęž‰ inkiki Lia paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa haleekeme. Kutu pieke Leisolomaęž‰ Lia paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pilisi nakaęž‰ wekinaęž‰ ti kiliki IĚ± maęž‰ndaęž‰ kie leekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Koto leeke Liamaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka haliki pake nele ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰pe. Ametaęž‰ pa yaka wekinaęž‰ ti kiliki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ alepe leekeme. Kotaęž‰ Leisolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ wekinaęž‰ ti kiliki IĚ± maęž‰ndaęž‰ kikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ame timbataęž‰ Dieikope yaapo poluelenaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Kutupa welealo nane Dieikopetaęž‰ oni e paęž‰taęž‰manu hao epeeke handaa Lia hama opolu bao mandaęž‰hande pulu pua alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ yaka wekinaęž‰ ti kilikimaęž‰ nekenaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hamboaęž‰maęž‰ ame timbataęž‰ IĚ± yaapo pelipikie leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ koto timbataęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ yaapo peliekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Lianaęž‰ pieke yeni hombo peaasotaęž‰ weki loke lomba ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ yunki pao weki mendiaeyekeme.
\v 18 Liamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaka haliki paęž‰taęž‰ haloeke handaa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ yaka yenki kaęž‰laęž‰mee laa mo wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Isaka leekeme.
\v 19 Kutupa Lia weki loke paa lomba ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ yunki mindiki hataęž‰ peao weki mendiaeyekeme.
\v 20 Kutupa Liamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke pa kitaęž‰laęž‰ ale kaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ yaka halikinaęž‰ yunki mindiki hataęž‰ weki mendiaaso ekinaęž‰ IĚ± pukimaęž‰ homa handaęž‰ milieke laa mo wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Sebuloni leekeme.
\v 21 Wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ Liamaęž‰ wandiki mondu wia bikitaęž‰ Daena leekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Leisolo hone u haotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pieke yeni opua weki mendinaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 23 Mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ weki loke lomba hali weki mondu wiekeme. Kutupa alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ yaka yalaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ weki kitolo hataęž‰ mea baalaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 24 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ IĚ± weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ paa kinaęž‰e alo hataęž‰ koto wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Diosepe leekeme.
\s1 Dieikopemaęž‰ Leibeni yaapo pi lo tonkaepekeeki
\p 
\v 25 Mo Diosepe mendia hoki nanetaęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰ Leibeni paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± yaka da ponomaęž‰ IĚ± tapae laa alotaęž‰
\v 26 Mo IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ e pokao molo wekiwandaęž‰ mea hatuku minaęž‰paęž‰lao pono lae. Pa ekipeke IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ e epeke tupaęž‰ pokalo ekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone wilimee leekeme.
\p 
\v 27 Koto leeke Leibenimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ doeki lono lae. Mo ale paeyao molo ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ handeau opao handaęž‰ witolo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± epealaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me laa hone ulume.
\v 28 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke hambuluekemaęž‰ nakaęž‰ yenki dupae laa lae leekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Dieikopemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ e pokaaloeki make yaka kiki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu saęž‰mbaęž‰lalaęž‰eki make nakaęž‰ handeleme.
\v 30 Mo IĚ± aĚ±iĚ± na epeke hano hosiki siki wia hae ekitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ tieke kiake saęž‰mbaęž‰laęž‰pa ulaęž‰me. Kutupa mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±naęž‰ yeke neke epeaalaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ yaka ekimanu handeteke halo polo natee leekeme.
\p 
\v 31 Koto leeke Leibenimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ ekipumaęž‰ hambonope leekeme. Dieikopemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ yenki kipaęž‰laęž‰me. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do alo ekinaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu paa handeteke hawalueke.
\v 32 Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ nakaęž‰ sipisipi polu paęž‰taęž‰ puataęž‰ mo punu paęž‰laęž‰ sipisipi ikikimanu make wape wape piki o au au laęž‰laęž‰ nanikosi ikikimanu make yataęž‰pa meono lae. Kotoeki homeketaęž‰ mo yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰ yenkie.
\v 33 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ wetepe ninaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke na makealomee laa anaęž‰naęž‰ handilipikie. Pa ekipeke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka molo yenki handulueke alo epekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo IĚ±maęž‰ au au na laęž‰laęž‰ o wape wape na piki nanikosi o punu na piki sipisipi maęž‰ndaęž‰ wia haowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pake naęž‰laęž‰me laa handaęž‰ wilipikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 34 Leibenimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Mo nakanaęž‰maęž‰ aleeki otaęž‰ pupanaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 35 Pate koto natenaęž‰ kone Leibenimaęž‰taęž‰ mo wape daęž‰pedaęž‰pe piki o au au leke nanikosi hali ekimanu make mo au au leke wandaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ paeyao siki make kutupa mo punu piki sipisipi paeyao make yataęž‰po miekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ weki tonu paeyaomaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ laataęž‰
\v 36 Dieikope minaęž‰paęž‰lao koto au au leke maęž‰naęž‰manu mea nate teponaęž‰ polo pieke tupaęž‰ papate mea pemekeme. Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande minaęž‰paęž‰laeyeke au au na leke maęž‰naęž‰manu handeteke hayekeme.
\p 
\v 37 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki ti palekemanu mea hake pu lopa lopa pinaęž‰taęž‰ mandane yonkelekemanu lokaęž‰laęž‰ mepi piekeme.
\v 38 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do ti paleke manutaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ manunaęž‰ ikali no haemeke kawaso wieke alenaęž‰ pua nokopeekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto pate wieke ekitaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ manumaęž‰taęž‰ ikali nolo aęž‰pa koto pate tiaęž‰tiki pieke piekeme.
\v 39 Kutupa mo nanikosi manumaęž‰ mo ti palekemanu nokopeeke alenaęž‰ tiaęž‰tiki pimikitaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo panake mendiaęž‰tiki pimiki ikiki sunutaęž‰ au au la make wape wape piki ekimanu mondu wiaęž‰tiki pimikime.
\p 
\v 40 Koto ekinaęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo sipisipitaęž‰ nanikosi yaapo na apaęž‰take taęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo koto sipisipi paeyaotaęž‰ mo Leibeninaęž‰ au au leke make punu piki sipisipimanu hayaęž‰ nanemaęž‰ leke popeleke yao haenaęž‰ leekeme. Dupieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu aneke hapu saęž‰mbaęž‰laęž‰pa witolo hataęž‰ mo Leibeninaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu taęž‰taęž‰ putupa haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 41 Kutupa mo hande panka wiki wandaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ manunaęž‰ puteke pambiekeeki handolotaęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ manumaęž‰ ikali no haemeke kawaso wieke alenaęž‰ tiaęž‰tiki pinaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ mo ti paleke manutaęž‰ koto pate nokaęž‰paęž‰tiki piekeme.
\v 42 Pate mo honkopu na hake maęž‰naęž‰manu haemeke alenaęž‰taęž‰ mo ti palekemanu na wiaęž‰tiki piekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ Leibenitaęž‰ mo honkopu na hake maęž‰naęž‰manu minolo hataęž‰ Dieikopetaęž‰ mo panka wiki maęž‰naęž‰manu wia hayekeme.
\v 43 Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikopetaęž‰ hamoko tieke hayekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ sipisipi pitaęž‰ nanikosimanu make pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ tapake make kemelomanu make donkimanu make otaęž‰ wopu wia hayekeme.
\c 31
\s1 Dieikope pindipa peekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Leibeninaęž‰ eiyeke tonumaęž‰ lemekeeki opieke ekitaęž‰ dupae. Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ apaęž‰maęž‰ wia hayaęž‰ ale paeyao maęž‰laęž‰me laa Ipikaęž‰ hamoko halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰eki maęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰mee lemekeeki opiekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Leibenitaęž‰ ambaęž‰taęž‰ homu piekepate ametaęž‰ leke tankemaęž‰ handeekeeki handeekeme.
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo nakaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ kenke nane make nakaęž‰ tapake paęž‰taęž‰ make paa pue. Kutupa IĚ±taęž‰ neke yaapo halueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Koto leeke Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ Leisolo pitaęž‰ Lia yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu hayeke alenaęž‰ ipiki aęž‰pa mandaęž‰hande piaęž‰paęž‰peke laa pi tapaeyekeme
\v 5 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipilikaęž‰ apaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ piaęž‰ tupaęž‰ homu na piki pa leke tankemaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰eki IĚ±maęž‰ handolome. Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate yaka apaęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± yaapo halaęž‰me.
\v 6 Yaka welemaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ e pokalo ekitaęž‰ hone wilipime.
\v 7 Kutu puaęž‰pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± makeao make yaka yenki manutaęž‰ hoto kiki yaapo natenaęž‰ honditi paęž‰laęž‰mee. Koto pinaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± na hoeyaenaęž‰ leaęž‰me.
\v 8 Pa mo ipilikaęž‰ apaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo au au lelie nanikosi manutaęž‰ nakaęž‰ yenkie laa laęž‰tiki pieketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ au au lekeeki mondu pambaęž‰tiki piekeme. Kutupa paa alotaęž‰ mo wape wape piliaęž‰ nanikositaęž‰ nakaęž‰ yenkie pa laęž‰tiki piaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ wape wape pikieki homeke mondu pambaęž‰tiki piaęž‰me.
\v 9 Kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ manutaęž‰ pao mea IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 10 Mo maęž‰naęž‰manu titaęž‰laęž‰ kinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ dupiki upa puaęž‰me. Mo tiaęž‰tiki pimi nanikosi halieki manutaęž‰ au au laa make wape wape pikieki homeke handoaęž‰me.
\v 11 Kutupa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ upamaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dieikopeo leeke IĚ±maęž‰ Wae loaęž‰me.
\v 12 Koto loeke alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰e. Mo titaęž‰laęž‰ nanikosi halieki manutaęž‰ mo au au leke make wape wape piki ekimanu homekee. Dupitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo Leibenimaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki handolo hataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ dupiki hau pinaęž‰ alome.
\v 13 IĚ±taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande toopitaęž‰ hone u tiaasaęž‰ ale winaęž‰ la olipi oeta hola keke pi laęž‰ wi ale Bedele hama paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao epoaęž‰ Kodaęž‰e. Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ mo neke mendiaęž‰ kenke nane polenaęž‰ tikitiki yae laa leaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Koto leeke Leisolo pitaęž‰ Lia yaapomaęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo dikanaęž‰maęž‰ dikaęž‰ apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ meaęž‰peke ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me.
\v 15 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ dikitaęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ wandaęž‰maęž‰ handaalaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ diki tapao miaęž‰ manitaęž‰ naęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 16 Mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ dikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ alemanu paeyao maęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dikaęž‰eki make diki wekiwandikinaęž‰eki konee. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke la kaęž‰laęž‰eki kone pie lepekeme.
\p 
\v 17-18 Koto ekinaęž‰ Dieikopetaęž‰ mo ateke hayeke alenaęž‰ Keinani nane poluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yaeyekeme. Ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki make weteke tonu make mo kemelomanu manda pitaeyekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu paeyao make mo ipikaęž‰ Mesopoteimia hataęž‰ mieke alemanu paeyao mea pulu haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 19 Leibenitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ sipisipi manunaęž‰ itiki tunkulu pu moneayeke hoki nane haenaęž‰ Leisolomaęž‰taęž‰ atekenaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pa wepia wieke kodaęž‰manu pake miekeme.
\v 20 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki minaęž‰paęž‰laasome laa Leibeni na opuaeyeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Leibeni makeaeyekeme.
\v 21 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ alemanu paeyao mea ipupulo minaęž‰paęž‰laeyekeme. Kutupa mo Yupoteitisi ikali yuma pua mo yu elimanu wiki Kiliaęž‰de kenke nane polueke alo pemekeme.
\s1 Leibenimaęž‰ Dieikope telimea peekeeki
\p 
\v 22 Nate tepo paeyeketaęž‰ Dieikopetaęž‰ pindipa paęž‰laęž‰me laa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Leibeni la haleekeme.
\v 23 Kutu pieke handaa ipikaęž‰ haliweki hatuku hoto wataake hataęž‰ natenaęž‰ Dieikope teliaęž‰ mea pua mo yu eli hapeleke Kiliaęž‰de kenke paęž‰taęž‰ pua teliminimikime.
\v 24 Koto timbataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Leibeni paęž‰taęž‰ upamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ mulueke alo hataęž‰ paalaęž‰ tiaapeke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na peaęž‰peke laa leekeme.
\v 25 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ palai da manutaęž‰ mo pote paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰eyekeme. Kutupa make Leibeni ipikaęž‰ palai dataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mo pote eli wiki Kiliaęž‰de kenke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰eyekeme.
\p 
\v 26 Leibenimaęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ekipeke makeao mo yaka wandiki yaapotaęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ dipula minaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ handeke tupaęž‰ hatuku mea aęž‰pa pelepe.
\v 27 IĚ±taęž‰ ekipeke makeao IĚ± na opuake yopusiki dodaęž‰pikimaęž‰ aęž‰pa pelepe. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± lekenaęž‰ yolutaęž‰ mo neke tapaaso hataęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo kida make tapekemaęž‰ handeke ale make litolo hataęž‰ emelimanu lo tapaalo puaęž‰me.
\v 28 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yaka wandiki yaaponaęž‰ wekiwandiki make yaka wandiki yaapo make aęž‰taloe pi alo hataęž‰ nunu na piono lemee. Koto hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ ti na piki hau peleme.
\v 29 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke hoeyalo polo honkoputaęž‰ ulaęž‰pate nakaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ambaneke timba IĚ± kinki pitolo alotaęž‰ Neke paalaęž‰ tiaapeke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na peaęž‰peke leaęž‰me.
\v 30 IĚ±maęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ da aĚ±iĚ± aęž‰pawemaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ pelepate ekipeke ya da paęž‰taęž‰ uaęž‰ kodaęž‰ alemanu pake naa aęž‰pa pelepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 31 Koto leeke Dieikopemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandiki yaapo pao milipipatemaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homoaęž‰me.
\v 32 Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ nakaęž‰ wepia wiki kodaęž‰manu wia haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ lu homaenaęž‰e. Do dikaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ wekitisi haaso haenaęž‰taęž‰ pa nakaęž‰ alemanu weiya nakaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ miaęž‰peke laa leekeme. Koto leekeeki Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Leisolomaęž‰ Leibeninaęž‰ wepia wieke kodaęž‰manu pake neekeeki na handeekeme.
\p 
\v 33 Koto leeke Leibenimaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ palai da paęž‰taęž‰ pua weiya kutupa Lianaęž‰ palai da paęž‰taęž‰ make mo pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaaponaęž‰ palai da paęž‰taęž‰ make pua weiyekepate ipikaęž‰ wepia wieke kodaęž‰manu na handaęž‰ wiekeme. Kutupa Leisolonaęž‰ palai da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme.
\v 34 Leisolomaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande da paęž‰taęž‰ wieke wepia wieke kodaęž‰ manutaęž‰ mo kemelo maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ hoki manda yama pitaęž‰laęž‰ seamaęž‰ handeke alenaęž‰ u hayeke nu paęž‰taęž‰ mendia ipikitaęž‰ manda pua pitiekeme. Leibenimaęž‰taęž‰ mo palai da paęž‰taęž‰ weiyekepate na handaęž‰ wiekeme.
\v 35 Leisolomaęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. IĚ± yaapo mineke na pankaęž‰peke. Mo nakaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ IĚ± na tiao halo ekitaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ kaisepo da handolome laa leekeme. Kotaęž‰ Leibenimaęž‰taęž‰ weiyekepate ipikaęž‰ wepia wieke kodaęž‰manu otaęž‰ na handaęž‰ wiekeme.
\p 
\v 36 Kutu pieke handaa Dieikopetaęž‰ mineke tunkulu mea nalo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ekipiki ataęž‰kaęž‰ peaasaęž‰eki polope laa mineke pankolo hataęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Mo IĚ± teliaęž‰ mea epele ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hando tombo ulaęž‰ pi yambololo ekimaęž‰ pie leeke pelepe.
\v 37 Ametaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao koto talo pelemaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ hando ekimanu handaęž‰ wilipe. Nakaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ make yaka haliwekimaęž‰ make handolotaęž‰ epimaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hau paęž‰laęž‰mee lenaęž‰maęž‰ do hamekenaęž‰ mea wie.
\v 38 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ 20 bapinaęž‰ neke yaapo haowaęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ sipisipi manumaęž‰ make nanikosi manumaęž‰ make ikiki pa epeke ombu mendiolo haememe. Kutupa make IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ sipisipi hali ekimanu homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na lu noaęž‰me.
\v 39 Mo tikene maęž‰naęž‰ yeti sayalemaęž‰ nakaęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰ndaęž‰ lu neeketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ yaka kone epeatiki puaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ yaka pu hoeyaasoeki diaęž‰me laa loluekemaęž‰taęž‰ neke na aęž‰pa walaęž‰tiki puaęž‰me. Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo timba o natenaęž‰ pake naęž‰tiki piaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± koto kone epeae laa laęž‰tiki pime.
\v 40 Hoto anekemaęž‰ mo natenaęž‰taęž‰ nate titipumaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki meaęž‰tiki pea timbataęž‰ kosaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰tiki pitolo u peliaęž‰peke na yaęž‰tiki piaęž‰me.
\v 41 Koto hautaęž‰ mo hande neke yaapo hatia pu haowaęž‰ 20 bapi tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ piaęž‰ekie. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ 14 bapitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandiki yaapo muluekemaęž‰ nakaęž‰ e pokaokaęž‰naęž‰ mo yunki mindiki hataęž‰ bapinaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu maęž‰ndaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ handeteke haowaęž‰me. Kutu piono kone nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yaka yenkitaęž‰ hoto kiki yaaponaęž‰ topo pime.
\v 42 Mo yaka apaęž‰tonu Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke yaaponaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ IĚ± yaapo na hataęž‰ yolutaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone kiki hameke pono tapaalo pime. Pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yaka kaęž‰ndaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ pokoaęž‰ e make hando haotaęž‰ ambaneke timbataęž‰ ipiki paeyaaso hataęž‰ IĚ± maĚ±leke lia piaęž‰me leekeme
\s1 Dieikope pitaęž‰ Leibeni yaaponaęž‰ pi lo tonkaepekeeki
\p 
\v 43 Leibenimaęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do wandiki yaapotaęž‰ yaka wandiki yaapoe. Ipilikaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ yaka ekie. Kutupa do maęž‰naęž‰manu paeyaotaęž‰ yaka ekie. Handaęž‰taa. Do ale paeyaotaęž‰ yakaeki yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pate IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do yaka wandiki yaapo make ipilikaęž‰ wekiwandiki make pao muluekemaęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰
\v 44 kotaęž‰ neke yaapo aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa pi tonkaluekemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ tikitiki yao halome. Ametaęž‰ mo dikaęž‰ pi tonkao witolopaęž‰eki niminao haluekemaęž‰taęž‰ toopimanu mu mombaęž‰la hombutaęž‰ hapanaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 45 Koto leeke Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ niminao halo pieke toopi mea haenaęž‰ laataęž‰
\v 46 ipikaęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mandane toopimanu mu hombutaęž‰ hape leekeme. Kutupa koto toopimanu mea hombutaęž‰ hayeke ale teaęž‰ nanetaęž‰ iki paeyao pitaęž‰ ne nemekeme.
\v 47 Koto patetaęž‰ Leibenimaęž‰taęž‰ Dieka Sahaduda leekeme. Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ Kaęž‰lidi leekeme.
\v 48 Leibenimaęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do mu mombololopaęž‰ toopi manumaęž‰taęž‰ diki telipunaęž‰ hone u tialieke leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ yeke koto patetaęž‰ Kaęž‰lidi leekeme.
\v 49 Leibenimaęž‰ ombu alotaęž‰ Diki taęž‰taęž‰ pualu pupaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ maketaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ diki handeteke haenaęž‰e laa mo alenaęž‰taęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Misipa make leekeme.
\v 50 Leibenimaęž‰ pi paa alo alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka wandiki yaapo epeke tupaęž‰ na handeteke hake o wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ mu pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ na opulu polopate Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ diki handaęž‰laęž‰me laa hone wiaęž‰peke.
\v 51 Dotaęž‰ neke diki tukikinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mu mombololo toopi manue. Kutupa do toopitaęž‰ niminapeke toopie.
\v 52 Do mombololopaęž‰ toopimanu make do niminapeke ekinaęž‰ toopi maketaęž‰ diki hone u tialo paęž‰laęž‰ekie. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke hoeyaluekemaęž‰taęž‰ do mombololopaęž‰ toopimanu ankulao na ipulueke. Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± hoeyaluekemaęž‰taęž‰ do toopimanu o do niminapeke toopi ulaęž‰eki ankulao na aęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 53 Mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰ Neiho yaaponaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ dikaęž‰ haumanu telipaenaęž‰e leekeme. Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ lao yeni pu hayeke Kodaęž‰naęž‰ bikinaęž‰ mo pi laęž‰ wipikieki opulueke laa keke pi laęž‰ wiekeme.
\v 54 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ liataęž‰ mo potenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni hau pea ipikaęž‰ haliweki wi laęž‰ meataęž‰ ne nemekeme. Ne no paeyaotaęž‰ koto timbataęž‰ mo pote paęž‰taęž‰ pelimikime.
\v 55 Da kelepeeketaęž‰ Leibenimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandiki yaaponaęž‰ wekiwandiki make waneke yaapo make nunu peataęž‰ paa da poluekemaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la peekeme.
\c 32
\s1 Dieikopemaęž‰ Iso mandaęž‰hande puluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yaeyeke ekie.
\p 
\v 1 Dieikope potaęž‰naęž‰ pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ mandane enisolomanu mandaęž‰hande piekeme.
\v 2 Kutaa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo enisolomanu hando hao alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ taęž‰kaęž‰li dae laa Koto patetaęž‰ Mahaneimi leekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Idomo kenke nane hameke Iso paęž‰taęž‰ pi mea polo pieke haliweki ambaęž‰la pulu haenaęž‰ tapaeyekeme.
\v 4 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa pua lapaęž‰peke laa la halolo alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ pi opua e pokaasaęž‰ some Dieikopemaęž‰ yaka you hali Iso neke paęž‰taęž‰ do pi lo tapaasome. IĚ±taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na epoaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Leibeni yaapo hao ametaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipulume.
\v 5 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ kaomanu make donkimanu make sipisipimanu make nanikosimanu make pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make miniki ipulume. Ya tiekeo. IĚ±taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa handaęž‰ minaęž‰lepe laa do pi tapaasome laa lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Kutupa mo pi mea pemeke haliweki Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipulu alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kame Iso paęž‰taęž‰ pua lomeke handaa ipikitaęž‰ neke mandaęž‰hande pulueke alo hataęž‰ ambaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ ipulaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ 400 haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± ipulaęž‰me laa lemekeme.
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰ Dieikopetaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ hone ti yokeekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke wandaęž‰hali make ipikaęž‰ sipisipimanu make nanikosimanu make kaomanu make kemelomanu make tapake yaapo putupaęž‰ alu piekeme.
\v 8 Ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Isomaęž‰ mo titinaęž‰ tapake aęž‰pa hoeyaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo wetepenaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pindipinaęž‰e hone wiekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰ yeni pitolo alotaęž‰ Yaka mei Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰ yaka apaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke yaaponaęž‰ Kodaęž‰o. Yaka pi opie. Tekehalio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo yaka kenke paęž‰taęž‰ make yaka tapake paęž‰taęž‰ make paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pue laataęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao epealueke laa IĚ± la kimee.
\v 10 IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ e pokaaso hali hataęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make kimaęž‰ na homaęž‰laęž‰eki make ki ekitaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mone yopulutaęž‰ mo hande Diodani ikalitaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na miniki pa tumapu piti homeke yumuaęž‰pate pa ame ipulutaęž‰ do tapake yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± ipulume.
\v 11 Koto ekinaęž‰ ya Tekehalio IĚ±taęž‰ yaka kame Isomaęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰e. Ipikitaęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea niki paeyao make mo wekiwandaęž‰ make hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰mee.
\v 12 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao epeao make kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ puluaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na yataęž‰polo paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ mo dawala teaęž‰naęž‰ ulaęž‰ ikali houmaęž‰ handekeeki kulueke laa laęž‰ wi pitaęž‰ hone wie laa Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni piekeme.
\p 
\v 13-15 Koto timbataęž‰ koto pate peliolo hataęž‰taęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ hameke Iso pa halo pieke maęž‰naęž‰manu dupa yataęž‰po miekeme. Nanikositaęž‰ 200 wandaęž‰eki pitaęž‰ 20 halieki make sipisipitaęž‰ 200 wandaęž‰eki pitaęž‰ 20 halieki make kemelotaęž‰ 30 ikiki andu haleekeeki pitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikiki tonu make 40 kaomanu make kiki yaapo kao halieki make donkitaęž‰ 20 wandaęž‰ ekimanu pitaęž‰ kiki yaapo donki halieki make paeyao yataęž‰po miekeme
\v 16 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ homeke tapake tapake sununaęž‰ haenaęž‰ lomaęž‰ lomaęž‰ peataęž‰ homeke homekenaęž‰taęž‰ hali homekemaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ lomaęž‰ lomaęž‰ pinaęž‰ leekeme. Kutupa mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki ambaęž‰la pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ mo homeke homeke maęž‰naęž‰ tapakenaęž‰ tukikinaęž‰taęž‰ waleke umaęž‰ umaęž‰ pinaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke laa manaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 17 Kutupa mo titinaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ mea peeke some paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo yaka kame Isomaęž‰ neke mandaęž‰hande pea neke lotaęž‰ pitolo Nakaęž‰ you sometaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe o Hane pulipe o Do ipulimi maęž‰naęž‰ manutaęž‰ epinaęž‰ ekipe laa lotaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 18 kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ dupa hombo peaapeke. Ikitaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali Dieikopenaęž‰ ekie. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ you some Iso paęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰eki tapaalaęž‰me. Kutupa Dieikope ipikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoki nane ipulaęž‰me laa lapeke leekeme.
\v 19 Kutupa mo hoki paęž‰taęž‰ hali make tepo peao hali paęž‰taęž‰ make mo paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make homeke pi kone lomaęž‰ lomaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iso mandaęž‰hande pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ dupa lapaęž‰peke laa la halolotaęž‰
\v 20 dupa make lapaęž‰peke. Aowe. Nakaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali Dieikopetaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoki nane kone ipulaęž‰me lapaęž‰peke leekeme. Dieikopenaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ ale manumaęž‰ hamekenaęž‰ puki epeao kutupa ipiki pua mandaęž‰hande puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ puaęž‰ hautaęž‰ pa paeyawalieke laa honemaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 21 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo pa halaęž‰laęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ titinaęž‰ pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ koto timba ipikitaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ palai da paęž‰taęž‰ peliekeme.
\s1 Dieikopemaęž‰ Penielo kenke paęž‰taęž‰ tonkaęž‰neli piekeeki
\p 
\v 22 Koto homeke timba konetaęž‰ Dieikope tiao ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo make mo e pokaepeke wandaęž‰ yaapo make ipikaęž‰ kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ homeke wekiwandiki make mo Diaęž‰boko ikali yumaęž‰ pa penaęž‰ tapaeyekeme.
\v 23 Kutupa mo tapake tapaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao siki make tapaeyekeme.
\v 24 Pate ipikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ siki pao hayekeme. Kutupa koto timbataęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰pa ipiki yaapo tonkaęž‰neli pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ da kelepeekeeki teke paęž‰taęž‰ mieke minaęž‰paęž‰laluekemaęž‰
\v 25 mo somemaęž‰ mo tonkaęž‰neli pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ na bepolapeke yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa handolo hataęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Dieikopenaęž‰ pelimokonaęž‰ lieke handaataęž‰ pelimoko yokaęž‰ endiaeyekeme.
\v 26 Kutupa mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Da kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ± pono lae leeke handaa Dieikopemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Neke aĚ±iĚ± na tapake. IĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ epeaekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neke tapaalueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 27 Koto leeke mo halimaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ epipe leekeme. IĚ±taęž‰ Dieikopee leekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Kotaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ nakaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Dieikope diaęž‰yaęž‰lieke. Pa ekipeke nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo make hali yaapo make tonkaęž‰neli pea bepolae ekinaęž‰ nakaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Isulaie leekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Koto leeke Dieikopemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ biki la kie leekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ekipeke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka biki opuluekemaęž‰ alepe laa leekeme. Koto laataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Dieikope epeayekeme.
\p 
\v 30 Kotaęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ leke popeleke paęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰ alu puaęž‰pate IĚ±taęž‰ na homeke pa halomee leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ koto alenaęž‰taęž‰ Penielo leekeme.
\v 31 Dieikopetaęž‰ Penielo minaęž‰paęž‰laaso haenaęž‰taęž‰ nate opeekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pelimokomaęž‰ yokaęž‰ endiatiki peekeme.
\v 32 Ame do maketaęž‰ mo Isulainaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikimaęž‰ maketaęž‰ mo pelimoko tunalaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ honkoputaęž‰ na no halememe. Pa ekipeke Dieikopetaęž‰ mo koto honkopunaęž‰ lieke ekinaęž‰ pitelememe.
\c 33
\s1 Dieikopemaęž‰ Iso mandaęž‰hande piekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ Iso ipikaęž‰ 400 haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± epemeeki hando haotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ mo Lia make Leisolo make mo e pokaepeke wandaęž‰ yaapo make teli pea haomaęž‰ haomaęž‰ pinaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 2 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo e pokaeyeke wandaęž‰ yaapo ipilikaęž‰ wekiwandiki ameĚ±leĚ± titinaęž‰ haenaęž‰ laa koto hoki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Lia ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki ameĚ±leĚ± haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo Leisolo pitaęž‰ Diosepe yaapotaęž‰ sale nane haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 3 Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki ambaęž‰la titinaęž‰ pua mo ipikaęž‰ hameke handaęž‰tia pulu hataęž‰ hoto wataake hataęž‰naęž‰ oni kenkenaęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniaeyekeme.
\v 4 Pate Isomaęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya ipiki mandaęž‰hande pulu pulu hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki yaapo bao hameke hopulolo hataęž‰ nunu piekeme. Ipiliki telipunaęž‰ eĚ± lepekeme.
\v 5 Kutupa Isomaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰weki make wekiwandiki make handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do neke ameĚ±leĚ± halaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ epi ameda yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme. Dieikopemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Kameo. Dotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ apetolo hataęž‰ IĚ± kaęž‰laęž‰ wekiwandikie leekeme.
\v 6 Kutupa mo e pokaepeke wandaęž‰ yaapo ipilikaęž‰ wekiwandiki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰pa pandaęž‰ puniaemekeme.
\v 7 Kutupa Lia pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰pa pandaęž‰ puniaemekeme. Kuta otaęž‰ wetepe nanetaęž‰ Diosepe pitaęž‰ Leisolo yaapomaęž‰ aęž‰pa pandaęž‰ puniaepekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Isomaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Pa mo titinaęž‰ mandaęž‰hande puaęž‰ tapaketaęž‰ kototaęž‰ eki laa pipe leekeme. Dieikopemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Kototaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homoelenaęž‰ yeke tapao puaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Pate Isomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kameo. IĚ±taęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ wia halomaęž‰ nakaęž‰ wia hale ekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kone wia hae laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Dieikopemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pilisi otaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka pa hameke kitolo alemanu mie. Ametaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ homu wopu pitele ekitaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ leke popeleke handolo ekitaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popeleke handeke nono pitaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 11 Koto ekinaęž‰ pilisio. Do IĚ±maęž‰ mea aęž‰palo pa hameke kitolo ale manutaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa mie laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ mo IĚ±maęž‰ weiyuaęž‰ alemanu paeyao anaęž‰naęž‰ kiaęž‰me leekeme. Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ hameke honke laęž‰tia puoopu haotaęž‰ Isomaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ miekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Isomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ kotaęž‰ panaęž‰ tikitiki yae. IĚ± ambaęž‰la polueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Koto leeke Dieikopemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Yaka hosiki wekiwandikitaęž‰ sokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ handeleme. Kutupa mo sipisipi pitaęž‰ kao kemboko ankulaęž‰ ankulaęž‰ make hone wiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ikitaęž‰ pa mo nate homeke sikinaęž‰ kone mo maęž‰naęž‰manu lu yombutia pomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ paeyao siki homilimikie.
\v 14 Koto ekinaęž‰ pilisi neke ambaęž‰la pue. IĚ±taęž‰ neke teliaęž‰ mea yopusiki mo yaka maęž‰naęž‰manu make mo wekiwandiki ameĚ±leĚ± honkopu hao kone aęž‰pa mo Idomo da aęž‰pa tolu minuluekee leekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Koto leeke Isomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ neke tambaęž‰ minaęž‰ mo yaka mandane haliweki minaęž‰paęž‰lanoe leekepate Dieikopemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ kotoeki hone pieke na loaęž‰pate pa mo nakaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki homekenaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 16 Koto ekinaęž‰ koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ Isotaęž‰ Idomo poluekemaęž‰ peekepate
\v 17 Dieikopetaęž‰ Sakodo nane peekeme. Koto patetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da aęž‰eya make ipikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ manunaęž‰ kalale da sunu make aęž‰eyaeyekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ koto patetaęž‰ Sakodo leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Dieikope mo Mesopoteimia haotaęž‰ mo Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ Sekeme daoni paęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ opolo epeekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ palai da manutaęž‰ mo daoninaęž‰ hamaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰eyekeme.
\v 19 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto hamaęž‰taęž‰ Sekemenaęž‰ ateke Hamonaęž‰ tapakenaęž‰eki 100 silipa manimaęž‰ hambeekeme.
\v 20 Koto patetaęž‰ oloda maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰eya bikitaęž‰ mo Isulainaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Elo winaęž‰ leekeme.
\c 34
\s1 Daena lumea peekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Lia Dieikope yaaponaęž‰ waneke Daenataęž‰ mo Keinani wandaęž‰weki handolo peekeme.
\v 2 Kutu piekepate mo da kenke paęž‰taęž‰ you hali hayeke Hipi hali Hamonaęž‰ eiyeke Sekememaęž‰ hando haotaęž‰ Daenaęž‰ pake lumea peekeme.
\v 3 Pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ wandiki seliapo yeke handaa mo wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandikinaęž‰ puki epealuekemaęž‰ taapeekeme.
\v 4 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. Koto wandikitaęž‰ yaka wandaęž‰ haenaęž‰ yeke mealenaęž‰ hone witolome leekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ waneke paęž‰taęž‰ yaalaęž‰piki hau piekeeki handeekepate ipikaęž‰ weki tonutaęž‰ oni hamaęž‰manu paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu handeteke halo pemeke ekiyalo pa hando hayekeme.
\v 6-7 Kutupa mo Dieikopenaęž‰ eiyeke tonutaęž‰ oni hamaęž‰manu paęž‰taęž‰ hao hondaęž‰ pambolo ipulu haenaęž‰ kone mo Sekemenaęž‰ ateke Hamotaęž‰ Dieikope yaapo pi lolueke alo hataęž‰ opolo peekeme. Kutu piekepate mo weki tonumaęž‰taęž‰ Sekememaęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ waneke lumea paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ dupiki hau paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo Isulai wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ yalaęž‰ peake hau paęž‰laęž‰me laa tolaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰ tetomaęž‰ homemekeme.
\v 8 Hamomaęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka weki Sekememaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandikinaęž‰ da otaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 9 Pilisio. Minaęž‰ lae. Kutupa nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make yaka wandaęž‰hali make mu alu alu pu halaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ dikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi lo tonkao u panaęž‰e.
\v 10 Kutupa neketaęž‰ do yaka kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ hataęž‰ mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ pa topo topo pea nakaęž‰ kenkemanu hamba wia halenaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Kutupa Sekememaęž‰ Daenanaęž‰ ateke make beliki tonu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa yaka honke aloeki peaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ alemanu kulueke.
\v 12 Ikaęž‰ anaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ pa kitolo alemanu muemenaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo wandikinaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ make pa minaęž‰liaemekaęž‰naęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa pinaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandiki homeke otaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone witolome leekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Pate Sekememaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ anaęž‰ Daena yalaęž‰ peake hau pieke handaa mo Dieikopenaęž‰ eiyeke tonumaęž‰ mo Sekeme pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ateke Hamo yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ yayapiki tupaęž‰ hombo peaemekeme.
\v 14 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ anaęž‰taęž‰ mo sekemesaisi hau na paęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ miaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kototaęž‰ niki yalaęž‰ tieke piki haue.
\v 15 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ niki polomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ nakaęž‰ haliweki paeyao sekemesaisi hau pimikaęž‰naęž‰ homeke aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lolumeke.
\v 16 Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ mu alu alu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lolumeke. Kutupa nikitaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± homeke wandaęž‰hali hao polumeke.
\v 17 Pate do nikanaęž‰maęž‰ alomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ sekemesaisi hau na pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo wandiki pao mea minaęž‰paęž‰lao polumeke lemekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Dupiki pimaęž‰taęž‰ Hamo pitaęž‰ eiyeke Sekeme yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me hone wipikime.
\v 19 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo paęž‰paęž‰naęž‰ wekimaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ waneke pukimaęž‰ homeekeeki yalo mo piaęž‰peke lemeke ekitaęž‰ nateleke maęž‰ndaęž‰ na paeyaeyekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ tapake tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ you some hayekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Kotaęž‰ Hamo pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eiyeke Sekeme yaapotaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke alenaęž‰ mo daoni potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ pua mo ipilikaęž‰ daoni haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pimanu lepekeme.
\v 21 Do haliwekitaęž‰ homu pelememe. Do niki halomaęž‰ kenke paęž‰taęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ pa pominaęž‰ lomanaęž‰e. Do nikaęž‰ kenketaęž‰ iki make anaęž‰naęž‰ halimikie. Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ wandiki tonu hapua meataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ wandiki tonu make hapua meaęž‰tiki pinaęž‰e.
\v 22 Kutu pulu polomaęž‰pate do haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ homeke wandaęž‰hali hamanaęž‰e alemepate ekiaęž‰ndaęž‰ homeketaęž‰ iki peleme tupaęž‰ nikaęž‰ haliweki paeyao make sekemesaisi hau pumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ homeke aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me alememe.
\v 23 Kutu pumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu paeyao make ikaęž‰ wia haleme alemanu paeyao make nikaęž‰eki diaęž‰yaęž‰liepe. Koto ekinaęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± haenaęž‰ lomanaęž‰e lepekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Hamo pitaęž‰ Sekeme yaapomaęž‰ lepeke ekitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa iki paeyao siki sekemesaisi hau pimikime.
\p 
\v 25 Hoto tepo hao mo haliweki koto sekemesaisi hau pimiki ekimaęž‰ tanda pa pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ eiyeke yaapo mo Daenanaęž‰ beliki Simiono pitaęž‰ Lipai yaapomaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ bainasi yaapo mina oni daoni paęž‰taęž‰ pepekeme. Mo weki yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ piki hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ wiaamaęž‰naęž‰ yeke pa otaęž‰ hone wia peke nono pea pua mo haliweki paeyao lia
\v 26 make mo Hamo pitaęž‰ Sekeme yaapo make lipikime. Kutupa Daena mo Sekemenaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pitieke alenaęž‰ pao hatuku pepekeme.
\v 27 Mo haliweki lu paeyaepeke hoki nanetaęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ eiyeke titi mandane weki tonumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ yalaęž‰ mieke ekinaęž‰ hombo peaaso hataęž‰ mo daoni teke puleke laemekeme.
\v 28 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰manu make kaomanu make donkimanu make oni daoni paęž‰taęž‰ wieke alemanu paeyao make oni hamaęž‰ ninaęž‰ hayeke alemanu paeyao mea pemekeme.
\v 29 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo yenki tieke peke alemanu paeyao mea wandaęž‰weki make mina kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰manu wieke alemanu paeyaosiki make mea pemekeme.
\p 
\v 30 Dieikopemaęž‰ Simiono pitaęž‰ Lipai yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mea kelepeme. Ametaęž‰ mo Keinani wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make Petese wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make do kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyao sikimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ honditi pilimikie. Koto wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ apaęž‰tao IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hali wopu diaęž‰yalo hataęž‰ do yaka tapake paeyaotaęž‰ hoeyaalimikie.
\v 31 Pate mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Dikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ dikaęž‰ anaęž‰taęž‰ pa koto hali yolaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰ tupaęž‰ haenaęž‰ lenaęž‰ lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me lepekeme.
\c 35
\s1 Bedele haenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Dieikope epeayekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto kone Bedele nane pua hapeke. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ neke mo hande nakaęž‰ kame Iso paalaęž‰ hao pindipa yapeke handa neke paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yaowaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ oloda aęž‰eyaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 2 Koto leeke Dieikopemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tapake make mo ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao haemeke tapake paęž‰taęž‰ make alotaęž‰ Mo ikaęž‰ wia haleme da maęž‰ndaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ kodaęž‰manu mea baapee. Kutupa make ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki tikitiki yao mo haĚ±iĚ± na taĚ±leke akaęž‰manu yamaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 3 Nikitaęž‰ do pate minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Bedele nane pulumaęž‰me. Koto patetaęž‰ mo IĚ±maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tuaęž‰ natenaęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ mea make mo IĚ± pomuaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰manu IĚ± yaapo hao hayaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ oloda aęž‰eluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 4 Koto leeke mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ wia haemeke da maęž‰ndaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ kodaęž‰manu paeyao make mo ikaęž‰ pankemeke haleke halimanu make paeyao Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ halemekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto alemanu paeyao mo Sekeme hayeke pei teke paęž‰taęž‰ hoiyekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Mo Dieikope ipikaęž‰ weki tonu ameĚ±leĚ± minaęž‰paęž‰laaso haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo teke paęž‰taęž‰manu hao yapeeke daonimanu paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ pa paalaęž‰ tieke pieke handaa mo tapake na teliaęž‰ mea pemekeme.
\v 6 Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± Lusu opolo epemekeme. Ametaęž‰ oni Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ Bedele leleme alenaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 7 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto pate oloda aęž‰eyaataęž‰ mo koto patetaęž‰ Bedelenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki tapu wiao leekeme. Pa ekipeke koto patetaęž‰ mo hande ipiki ipikaęž‰ hameke paalaęž‰ hao pindipa peeke handa Kodaęž‰ ipiki kone peneme yaeyeke alenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 8 Ambaęž‰ koto patetaęž‰ mo hande hosiki yaęž‰naęž‰ kone mo Lepekanaęž‰ pa hameke e pokao hayeke wandaęž‰ Debota homeeke handaa mo Bedele kaęž‰waęž‰ nanemaęž‰ tilao mo pei teke maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hoimiki yeke handa bikitaęž‰ EĚ± Alaęž‰ Peie lemekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Kutupa Dieikope mo Mesopoteimia minaęž‰paęž‰lao epeeketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ paa peneme yao pua ipiki epeayekeme.
\v 10 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Dieikope yaęž‰laęž‰pate ame do kini peataęž‰ Isulai lenaęž‰e leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Isulai leekeme.
\v 11 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Aneke Wele Wopupiki Kodaęž‰e. Wekiwandiki wopu mendiaęž‰peke. Tutu manutaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilieke. Kutupa neketaęž‰ kini hali manunaęž‰ apaęž‰mei halipikie.
\v 12 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ haloaęž‰ kenketaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ kulueke. Kutupa make nakaęž‰ hoki nane mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilimi wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ make halueke leekeme.
\v 13 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki minaęž‰paęž‰laeyekeme.
\v 14 Koto pate mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi la haleeke alenaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰ niminapeke toopi nokaęž‰pa olipi oeta make waini ikali make hola dotaęž‰ yakopiki alenaęž‰e laa pi wiekeme.
\v 15 Koto patetaęž‰ biki Bedele leekeme
\s1 Leisolonaęž‰ homeekeeki
\p 
\v 16 Dieikope ipikaęž‰ tapake ameĚ±leĚ± Bedele minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Epaęž‰taęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ pa hosiki papate leke winaęž‰taęž‰ Leisolo ipikaęž‰ weki mulu pieke nate minolo hataęž‰taęž‰ weki hoki nalo hataęž‰ make kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke miekeme.
\v 17 Mo weki hoki otaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ neeke dinaęž‰ mo weki meao hayeke wandaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Leisoloo. Hali weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰pee leekepate
\v 18 mo Leisolotaęž‰ homolo pulu hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paeyaaso pomo minolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Benomi leekeme. Pate pa atekemaęž‰taęž‰ biki Benisamini leekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Leisolo homeaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Epaęž‰taęž‰ nane pulaęž‰ potaęž‰ teaęž‰naęž‰ hoimikime. Ametaęž‰ Betelehaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰leme alenaęž‰e.
\v 20 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ niminaasaęž‰ toopi maęž‰ndaęž‰ koto alenaęž‰ nokopeekeme. Kutupa ame do make Leisolonaęž‰ lapaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰e laa walo halaęž‰me.
\v 21 Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Edanaęž‰ oli ya paęž‰taęž‰ haliao peke hokulupeke da teaęž‰ nane ipikaęž‰ palai damanu aęž‰elo peekeme
\s1 Dieikopenaęž‰ eiyeke tonu
\p 
\v 22 Dieikope koto kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ Lubenimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaeyeke wandaęž‰ Biliha yaapo loke apaęž‰taeyekeme. Koto ekitaęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰ opuataęž‰ mineke tieke wopu pankeekeme.
\p Dieikopetaęž‰ weki kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ yaapo pea mondu wiekeme.
\q1 
\v 23 Lianaęž‰ weki tonutaęž‰ Lubeni hande Dieikopenaęž‰ mupeke weki make Simiono make Lipai make Diuda make Isaka make Sebuloni make yekeme.
\q1 
\v 24 Leisolonaęž‰ eiyeke yaapotaęž‰ Diosepe pitaęž‰ Benisamini yaapoe.
\q1 
\v 25 Mo Leisolonaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaeyeke wandaęž‰ Bilihanaęž‰ eiyeke yaapotaęž‰ Daęž‰ni pitaęž‰ Naęž‰petali yaapoe.
\q1 
\v 26 Mo Lianaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke yaapotaęž‰ Kaęž‰de pitaęž‰ Aęž‰sia yaapo yekeme.
\p Do wekitonu paeyaotaęž‰ mo Mesopoteimia nane hataęž‰ mendieke weki tonue.
\s1 Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ homeekeeki
\p 
\v 27 Dieikopetaęž‰ ateke Aisaęž‰ke hayaęž‰ nane peekeme. Kototaęž‰ mo Maęž‰mote da Hebotoni nanemaęž‰ ateke Aisaęž‰ke pitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ yaapo hao hayeke alenaęž‰e.
\v 28 Aisaęž‰ketaęž‰ 180 bapi hao
\v 29 otaęž‰ koke yaa homeekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ weki Iso pitaęž‰ Dieikope yaapomaęž‰ hoipikime.
\c 36
\s1 Isonaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke wekiwandiki
\p 
\v 1 Dotaęž‰ mo hande Iso o biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Idomo laęž‰laęž‰ somenaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ bikie.
\v 2 Isomaęž‰taęž‰ Keinani wandaęž‰weki miekeme. Maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Hidi hali Ilononaęž‰ waneke Ada miekeme. Kutupa mo Hipi hali Sibiononaęž‰ eiyeke Ananaęž‰ waneke Oholibama make
\v 3 Nebeiotonaęž‰ beliki Baęž‰semaęž‰detaęž‰ Isimaęž‰elonaęž‰ waneke make miekeme.
\v 4 Titinaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Adamaęž‰taęž‰ Elipaęž‰se mendiaeyekeme. Baęž‰semaęž‰demaęž‰taęž‰ Leuelo mendiaeyekeme.
\v 5 Kutupa Oholibamamaęž‰taęž‰ Dieusi make Dialamo make Kota make mendiaeyekeme. Do weki paeyaotaęž‰ mo Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ Isonaęž‰ mendiaemeke weki tonue.
\p 
\v 6 Kutupa Isomaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰weki make eiyeke tonu make waneke tonu make ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyao make ipikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu make mo Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ mieke alemanu paeyao tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mea hameke Dieikope minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme.
\v 7 Ipiki minaęž‰paęž‰laeyeke ekitaęž‰ mo Dieikope ipiliki haepeke kenketaęž‰ ne dokaęž‰tiki yeke piekeme. Ipilikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ manutaęž‰ wotu taĚ±laĚ±oĚ± handolo hataęž‰ homeke paęž‰taęž‰ hapeke na yekeme.
\v 8 Koto ekinaęž‰ Isotaęž‰ mo Idomonaęž‰ pote eli paęž‰taęž‰ pu hayekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Dotaęž‰ mo hande Idomo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ apaęž‰mei Isonaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikie.
\q1 
\v 10 Isonaęž‰ weteke Adamaęž‰taęž‰ weki homeke Elipaęž‰se mendiaeyekeme.
\q1 Kutupa weteke maęž‰ndaęž‰ Baęž‰semaęž‰demaęž‰taęž‰ weki homeke Leuelo mendiaeyekeme.
\b
\q1 
\v 11 Isonaęž‰ eiyeke Elipaęž‰semaęž‰taęž‰ weki yunki hataęž‰ mendiekeme. Ikaęž‰ biki manutaęž‰ Temani make Oma make Sepo make Kaęž‰tamo make Kenaęž‰se makee.
\q1 
\v 12 Kutupa Elipaęž‰senaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaeyeke wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ Timinamaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ weki homeke Aęž‰maęž‰leke mendiaeyekeme.
\b
\q1 
\v 13 Kutupa Isonaęž‰ eiyeke Leuelomaęž‰taęž‰ weki tonkopu mendiekeme. Ikaęž‰ biki manutaęž‰ Nahati make Sita make Siama make Misa makee. Ikitaęž‰ mo Baęž‰semaęž‰denaęž‰ wekinaęž‰ eiyeke tonue.
\b
\q1 
\v 14 Isonaęž‰ weteke maęž‰ndaęž‰ Oholibamamaęž‰taęž‰ weki tepo mendiaeyekeme.
\q1 Ikaęž‰ biki manutaęž‰ Dieusi make Dialamo make Kota makee.
\q1 Oholibamamaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Sibiononaęž‰ eiyeke Ananaęž‰ wanekee.
\b
\p 
\v 15 Dotaęž‰ mo Iso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ epemeke tapake you hali manue.
\q1 Mo Isonaęž‰ mupeke weki Elipaęž‰setaęž‰ do tapake manunaęž‰ apaęž‰meie.
\q1 Temani make Oma make Sepo make Kenaęž‰se make
\v 16 Kota make Kaęž‰tamo make Aęž‰maęž‰leke makee.
\q1 Do tapake manutaęž‰ mo Isonaęž‰ weteke Ada paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ epemeke tapake manue.
\b
\q1 
\v 17 Isonaęž‰ eiyeke Leuelo paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ epeeke tapaketaęž‰ Nahati make Sita make Siama make Misa makee. Do tapake manutaęž‰ Isonaęž‰ weteke Baęž‰semaęž‰de mendiaeyeke ekie.
\b
\q1 
\v 18 Dotaęž‰ mo hande Ananaęž‰ waneke Oholibamamaęž‰ Isonaęž‰ mendiaeyeke weki tonunaęž‰ tapakemanue. Dieusi make Dialamo make Kota make mendiaeyekeme
\q1 
\v 19 Koto tapake paeyaotaęž‰ Iso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ epemeke tapakemanue
\s1 Seiyanaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke tapakemanu
\p 
\v 20 Mo Idomo kenke kini pea haemeke tapakemanu ikaęž‰ apaęž‰meitaęž‰ mo Ho hali Seiyanaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikie. Koto tapake manunaęž‰ apaęž‰meinaęž‰ biki manutaęž‰ doe.
\q1 Loutani make Soubalo make Sibiono make Ana make
\v 21 Disiono make Esa make Disianaęž‰ makee.
\b
\q1 
\v 22 Loutanitaęž‰ mo Hoti pitaęž‰ Hemane yaaponaęž‰ apaęž‰meie. Kutupa Loutaninaęž‰ belikitaęž‰ Timinae.
\b
\q1 
\v 23 Soubalotaęž‰ mo Elipani make Manahati make Ebalo make Siepo make Onamo make paeyaonaęž‰ apaęž‰meie.
\b
\q1 
\v 24 Sibionotaęž‰ weki yaapo Aiyali pitaęž‰ Ana yaapo mendiekeme. Anataęž‰ mo hande atekenaęž‰ donkimanu mo hande hapu hayeke alemaęž‰ handeteke hataęž‰ mo titipu piki ikali opeekeeki handaęž‰ wieke somee.
\v 25 Anataęž‰ mo Disiononaęž‰ atekee. Anamaęž‰taęž‰ wandiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Oholibama make mondu wiekeme.
\b
\q1 
\v 26 Disionotaęž‰ do tapake manunaęž‰ apaęž‰meie. Hemedani make Esibani make Itidani make Dietani makee.
\b
\q1 
\v 27 Esataęž‰ mo Bilihane make Sapani make Akane make koto tapake manunaęž‰ apaęž‰meie.
\b
\q1 
\v 28 Disianaęž‰taęž‰ mo Usu pitaęž‰ Atani tapake yaaponaęž‰ apaęž‰meie.
\b
\q1 
\v 29-30 Koto mo hande Idomo kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke Ho tapake manunaęž‰ bikie. Loutani make Soubalo make Sibiono make Ana make Disiono make Esa make Disianaęž‰ makee.
\s1 Idomonaęž‰ Kinimanu
\p 
\v 31 Ambaęž‰taęž‰ mo Isulai wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ kinimanu maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na handeteke haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Idomo kenke paęž‰taęž‰ kini pieke kini manunaęž‰ bikimanu doe.
\q1 
\v 32 Beonaęž‰ eiyeke Belataęž‰ mo Idomonaęž‰ kini hali hayekeme. Ipikaęž‰ daoninaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Dinihabae.
\q1 
\v 33 Bela homeeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ Sitanaęž‰ eiyeke Diobabemaęž‰ anketeke mea kini hali hayekeme. Ipikaęž‰ daonitaęž‰ Bositae.
\q1 
\v 34 Diobabe homeeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ Husamimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ anketeke mea kini hali hayekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ mo Temani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ epeeke somee.
\q1 
\v 35 Husami homeeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ Bedadenaęž‰ eiyeke Hadademaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ anketeke mea kini hali hayekeme. Ipikaęž‰ daoninaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Apitie. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Moaęž‰be kenke paęž‰taęž‰ mo Midiani tapake ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea bepolayeke somee.
\q1 
\v 36 Hadade homeeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Maseteka hali Samelamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ anketeke mea kini hali hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 37 Kutupa Samela homeeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ hayeke Teihobodi daoni paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke some Siaulumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ anketeke mea kini hali hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 38 Siaulu homeeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ Akebonaęž‰ eiyeke Baele Hananemaęž‰ anketeke mea kini hali hayekeme.
\q1 
\v 39 Akebonaęž‰ eiyeke Baele Hanane homeeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ Hadademaęž‰ anketeke miekeme. Ipikaęž‰ daoninaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Paue. Ipikaęž‰ weteketaęž‰ mo Mesahabenaęž‰ waneke Matededenaęž‰ waneke Mehetabelee.
\p 
\v 40 Dotaęž‰ mo hande Iso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ epeeke tapake manunaęž‰ you haliwekinaęž‰ biki manue.
\q1 Timina make Alapa make Dietede make
\v 41 Oholibama make Ela make Pinono make
\v 42 Kenaęž‰se make Temani make Mibisa make
\v 43 Makediele make Itame makee.
\p Koto you haliwekimanu haemeke kenke manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ bikimanu yalao haemeke tapake manue.
\c 37
\s1 Diosepe pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameketonu
\p 
\v 1 Dieikopetaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ ateke hayeke Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ paa hayekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa dotaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ tapakenaęž‰ tamenie.
\p Diosepetaęž‰ 17 bapinaęž‰ paęž‰paęž‰naęž‰ weki hataęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ e pokaeyeke wandaęž‰ yaapo Biliha pitaęž‰ Silipa yaaponaęž‰ eiyeke tonu ameĚ±leĚ± mo sipisipimanu make nanikosimanu make handeteke haemekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ hameke tonumaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ piaęž‰tiki pimiki ekinaęž‰ pi mea aęž‰paęž‰tiki piekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo wekitonu ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ homeke puki tieke wopumaęž‰ homeekeme. Pa ekipe mo wekitaęž‰ ipiki koke nanemaęž‰ mendiaeyeke weki yeke handa piekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ piki au leke kosaęž‰ dau hokulupeke wepia haleekeme.
\v 4 Kutupa mo ipikaęž‰ hameke tonumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ atekemaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ homeke puki tiekemaęž‰ wopu homeekeeki hando haotaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kame paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ honditi pitolo hataęž‰ homu piki pi manumaęž‰ na la halemekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Timba maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ upa pea mo ipikaęž‰ hameke tonu laa haleeketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ mineke leke ale panka aęž‰ndaęž‰ lia haemekeme.
\v 6 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo IĚ±maęž‰ puaęž‰ upa kelepono opuaęž‰pe.
\v 7 Niki paeyaotaęž‰ oni e paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ widimanu tonkaaso haomaęž‰me. Kutupa yaka widi tonkaaketaęž‰ tikitikinaęž‰ tialiao hayaęž‰me. Kutupa ikaęž‰eki manumaęž‰taęž‰ yakaeki popei yao hataęž‰ yaka widi tonkaake paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniaememe laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Koto leeke mo hameke tonumaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ kini hali hataęž‰ niki handeteke halipikie hone witelepe lemekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ upamanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mo ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰pa laęž‰tiki pieke pimanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ opiaęž‰tiki pitolo hataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke mineke pankaęž‰tiki pimikime.
\p 
\v 9 Kutupa Diosepemaęž‰ upa maęž‰ndaęž‰ pea ipikaęž‰ hameke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ upa maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa puaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nate make kaisepo make kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ homeke hombulankaęž‰manu make handoaęž‰me Kutupa moeki manumaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniaememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo koto upataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ make la haleeke handaataęž‰ atekemaęž‰ ipiki hando alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kototaęž‰ ekipiki upa pea pelepe. Nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ amaęž‰maęž‰ make nakaęž‰ kame tonumaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ make neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa pandaęž‰ punialumekee laa alepe leekeme.
\v 11 Diosepenaęž‰ hameke tonumaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ wamili pimikipate atekemaęž‰taęž‰ mo ekinaęž‰ hone pa wiaęž‰tiki pu hayekeme.
\s1 Diosepetaęž‰ tapao Idiepi mea pemekeeki
\p 
\v 12 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ hameke tonutaęž‰ mo atekenaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu handeteke halo oni Sekeme nane pua haenaęž‰taęž‰
\v 13 Dieikopemaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka taęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ neketaęž‰ oni nakaęž‰ kame tonumaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰manu handeteke haleme alenaęž‰ Sekeme nane poelenaęž‰e leekeme. Koto leeke Diosepemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yalome leekeme.
\v 14 Ipikaęž‰ atekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo nakaęž‰ kame tonutaęž‰ epeke halemepe laa handolo puataęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰manu epeke tupaęž‰ haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la IĚ± lolo aęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ atekemaęž‰ mo wekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ haemeke Hebotoni hadipi minaęž‰paęž‰lao peneyeke tapaalo peekeme.
\p Diosepetaęž‰ mo Sekeme opolo pua
\v 15 mo pate pomu lopolo haenaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰ u hao lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ aleke weitolo pipe laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Mo wekimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo yaka kame tonu ikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu handeteke haleme paęž‰taęž‰ weitolome. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo iki haleme paęž‰taęž‰ handekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± la kie leekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ pelememe. Ikitaęž‰ mo Dodani nane pulumaęž‰me lemeeki opuaęž‰me leekeme. Koto leeke Diosepetaęž‰ hameke tonu telimea pua Dodani pua handaęž‰ wiekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Diosepe papate leke epeekeeki hando haotaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na opolo epeke haenaęž‰ kone pi lo tonkaasotaęž‰ lu homaamanaęž‰e laa lemekeme.
\v 19 Ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone la alu alu pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hande upa pu halaęž‰ some ipulaęž‰mee.
\v 20 Ametaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± lu homao ipikaęž‰ loketaęž‰ oni naku ikali hapupapeke ekimanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lu baamanaęž‰e. Ipikitaęž‰ tikene maęž‰naęž‰yeti sayale maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ lia paęž‰laęž‰me lomanaęž‰e. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ upamaęž‰ waleaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ piliaęž‰eki handomanaęž‰ loaęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Lubenimaęž‰ mo lemekeeki opu hao Diosepe tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ yeke alotaęž‰ Na lumanaęž‰ pipe.
\v 22 Tanda maęž‰ndaęž‰ na haleketaęž‰ pa do hapekenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ naku paęž‰taęž‰manu lopamanaęž‰ pipe leekeme. Lubenimaęž‰ koto leeke ekitaęž‰ mo weki paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ mea ateke halaęž‰ nane paa tapaalueke hone witolo hataęž‰ leekeme.
\v 23 Diosepe mo hameke tonu haemeke alenaęž‰ opolo epeeketaęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ piki au leke kosaęž‰ dau hokulupeke titipulaęž‰ mea baemekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa mo weki meataęž‰ mo ikali na pitieke naku paęž‰taęž‰ mea baemekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Koto hoki nane ikitaęž‰ ne nalo pitinaęž‰taęž‰ koto kone mo Isimaęž‰elo tapake haliweki Kiliaęž‰de hao Idiepi nane yapemeeki handemekeme. Ikaęž‰ kemelo manutaęž‰ mo ne tende peaasaęž‰ alemanu make totopo piki ti pankekemanu make mu wia yapemekeme.
\v 26 Diudamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo nikaęž‰ kame lia aęž‰mbaomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ aleke otaęž‰ handaęž‰ ulumaęž‰pe.
\v 27 Pao. Do Isimaęž‰elo tapakemaęž‰ hambenaęž‰ tapaamanaęž‰e. Kutu pumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiki na hoeyaalumeke. Pa ekipeke ipikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ kame make homeke loke we konee leekeme. Koto leeke ipikaęž‰ hameke tonumaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 28 Kutupa mo Midianinaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ tapao halaęž‰ haliweki epemeketaęž‰ mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maęž‰ Diosepe oni naku paęž‰taęž‰ yolaęž‰ mea mo Isimaęž‰elo tapake paęž‰taęž‰ 20 silipa manimaęž‰ mea tapaemeke handaa mo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ hatuku Idiepi nane pemekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Kutupa Lubenitaęž‰ oni naku paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa handeeke pate Diosepe na pitiekeeki hando haotaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ akaęž‰manu sinki piekeme.
\v 30 Ipikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Mo wekitaęž‰ hande naku paęž‰taęž‰ na pilaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ eki puluaęž‰pe leekeme.
\p 
\v 31 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hameke tonumaęž‰ nanikosi maęž‰ndaęž‰ lia Diosepenaęž‰ hokulupeke kosaęž‰ dautaęž‰ oni maęž‰naęž‰ we kita kita pimikime.
\v 32 Kutupa mo dautaęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ mea pua alotaęž‰ Do dautaęž‰ handaęž‰ umaęž‰mee. Nakaęž‰ wekinaęž‰ eki yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\p 
\v 33 Mo atekemaęž‰ eiyekenaęž‰ eki yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa handaęž‰ u hao alotaęž‰ Aowe. Ipikaęž‰ ekie. Mandane tikene maęž‰naęž‰yeti sayalemaęž‰ lia piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me. Yaka weki Diosepetaęž‰ sinki sinki pea wia piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me leekeme.
\v 34 Koto ekinaęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ akaęž‰manu sinkipa busaęž‰ pitikimanu yameekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nate hokulunaęž‰ eiyeke homaęž‰ wia pitu hayekeme.
\v 35 Kutu pieke ipikaęž‰ eiyeke tonumaęž‰ make waneke tonumaęž‰ make atekenaęž‰ puki epealo epemekepate pa mo ipiki epeaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kiaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Oni homo halaęž‰ kenke paęž‰taęž‰ pulu maketaęž‰ yaka wekinaęž‰ homaęž‰ pa upaleke polueke leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ eiyeke Diosepenaęž‰ homaęž‰ pa utia peekeme.
\p 
\v 36 Kutu pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Midiani tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ oni Idiepi pua Diosepetaęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ da handeteke haenaęž‰ leeke you some maęž‰ndaęž‰ Podipamaęž‰ hambenaęž‰ tapaemekeme.
\c 38
\s1 Diuda pitaęž‰ Teima yaapo
\p 
\v 1 Koto nate ninaęž‰taęž‰ Diudataęž‰ hameke tonu minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Adalamo daoni hali Hita yaapo halo pu moneayekeme.
\v 2 Koto patetaęž‰ Diudamaęž‰taęž‰ Keinani hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Suanaęž‰ waneke handeekeme. Kutupa mo wandiki meataęž‰
\v 3 hali weki mondu wiaotaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Ea leekeme.
\v 4 Weki loke paa lombaataęž‰ hali weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ mondu wiataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Onane leekeme.
\v 5 Kutupa weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ mendiataęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Sela leekeme. Diudataęž‰ Kesibi haenaęž‰ do weki Sela mondu wiekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Diudamaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mupeke weki Eanaęž‰taęž‰ biki Teima leke wandaęž‰ meayekeme.
\v 7 Eanaęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoeyeke ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ na homolo hataęž‰ lu homaeyekeme.
\v 8 Koto ekinaęž‰ Diudamaęž‰ Eanaęž‰ hameke Onane paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kamenaęž‰ weteke kineke yaapo polu pue la alotaęž‰ Mo hande nikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ ulumaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ halikinaęž‰ hameke hataęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ kamenaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ piliaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki haenaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 9 Pate Onanemaęž‰taęž‰ mo wekiwandikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰eki diaęž‰yaęž‰lieke hone witolo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hamekenaęž‰ wandaęž‰ kineke yaapo polu pulutaęž‰ hamekenaęž‰ wekiwandiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na mendiaenaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hali hapeketaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ pao yapenaęž‰ laęž‰tiki piekeme.
\v 10 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kutupiki hau pieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ na homaeyeke handa Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki make lu homaeyekeme.
\v 11 Koto ekinaęž‰ Diudamaęž‰ meiyeke wandaęž‰ Teima paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo yaka weki Sela daenaęž‰ hombotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pa laęž‰kaęž‰la puataęž‰ kineke wandaęž‰ hapeke leekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ doeki leeke ekitaęž‰ mo hande hameke yaapo piaęž‰ tupaęž‰ Sela make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ liliekee laa paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Teimataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ da paa laęž‰kaęž‰la peekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Natemanu hosiki haotaęž‰ Diudanaęž‰ weteke homeekeme. Kutupa mo homaęž‰ wia pita paeyeketaęž‰ ipiki pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yankeke some mo Adalamo hali Hita yaapo Timina nane mo ipikaęž‰ sipisipimanu itiki pondaęž‰laeyeke nane pepekeme.
\v 13 Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Teima paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ meitaęž‰ mo Timina nane ipikaęž‰ sipisipi manunaęž‰ itiki pondololo yopulaęž‰me laa leekeeki opiekeme.
\v 14 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ yamo hayeke kineke wandaęž‰naęž‰ akaęž‰manu topo pea ipikaęž‰ leke popeleketaęž‰ dau sinkipikimaęž‰ aęž‰mbaotaęž‰ mo Timina pulaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ hayeke daoni Eneiminaęž‰ potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ pua pitiekeme. Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Diudanaęž‰ wetepe weki Selataęž‰ ambaęž‰ daelaęž‰pate kone IĚ± na minaęž‰ alaęž‰me hone wiekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Kutupa Diudamaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ hando haotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popeleke aęž‰mbaeyeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ pa yolaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ hone wiekeme.
\v 16 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo potaęž‰ teaęž‰naęž‰ pua mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ ekipa kuluaęž‰pe leekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ meiwandaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me hone na wiekeme.
\p Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ aleke kilipikipe leekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Mo halimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo yaka panake nanikosi maęž‰ndaęž‰ tapanealueke laa leekeme.
\p Koto leeke mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na kiki halenaęž‰taęž‰ aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ ambaęž‰laęž‰ taęž‰kaęž‰li wia hawano kilipikipe leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ mo taęž‰kaęž‰li wia hawalo pele aletaęž‰ aleke kionope leekeme.
\p Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo taęž‰kaęž‰li wia hawalo polo aletaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ pi lo tonkaaso hataęž‰ taĚ±laĚ±oĚ± hale tombotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ endu lopalaęž‰ pu make mo nakaęž‰ miniki hale tumapu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ make kie leekeme. Koto leeke mo ale manutaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme. Kutupa loke apaęž‰tao mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ weki loke lombeekeme.
\v 19 Kutupa Teimataęž‰ da pua mo dau sinkipiki mea bao mo kineke wandaęž‰naęž‰ akaęž‰manu paa pua mu pambaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Diudamaęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ yankeke Hita paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande IĚ±maęž‰ diminaowaęž‰ nanikosi mea pua mo hande wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halolo hataęž‰ ya ambaęž‰ hande taęž‰kaęž‰li wia hawaloaęž‰ alemanu mea aęž‰papeke laa leekeme. Hitataęž‰ koto leeke peekepate mo hande wandaęž‰ na handaęž‰ wiekeme.
\v 21 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Eneimi haemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hande potaęž‰naęž‰ pitiaęž‰ yolaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰taęž‰ handokaęž‰taęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme.
\p Mo haliwekimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do patetaęž‰ yolaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na halaęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Mo hande halitaęž‰ Diuda paęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pua alotaęž‰ Mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰ wiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰me. Kutupa make mo koto da haliwekimaęž‰ make alotaęž‰ Do patetaęž‰ yolaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na halaęž‰me laa lememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Koto leeke Diudamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ mo ale manutaęž‰ pa wia haenaęž‰e. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ diki kitaamaęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ yenki haluekemaęž‰ puaęž‰pate mo wandaęž‰ taa na handaęž‰ wikaęž‰taęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Kutupa kaisepo tepomanu paenaęž‰taęž‰ Diuda paęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ mei wandaęž‰ Teimamaęž‰taęž‰ hali yolaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰maęž‰ handaakaęž‰naęž‰ ametaęž‰ weki loke lombaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p Koto leeke Diudamaęž‰ pi takaęž‰lakemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto wandaęž‰ mea pua timaęž‰ yankaa homenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Kotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ timaęž‰ yanka homaluekemaęž‰ hama mea pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ meiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ do ale manunaęž‰ teke somemaęž‰ weki mendiao paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ do pi lo tonkaaso hataęž‰ taĚ±laĚ±oĚ± halaęž‰ tombotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ endu lopalaęž‰ pu make do tumapu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ epinaęž‰ ekipe laa handaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 26 Diudamaęž‰ mo hande alemanu handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ tikitikinaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo yaka weki Selamaęž‰ minaęž‰ lapeke ale kone pa IĚ±maęž‰ pi laęž‰ uaęž‰eki ataęž‰kaęž‰ pealome leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Diudamaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ yaapo loke paa na apaęž‰taeyekeme.
\p 
\v 27 Mo wandaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki mulu pieke nate opolo epeeketaęž‰ hone yaapo wiki weki mendilieke laa handaęž‰ wimikime.
\v 28 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰ weki hoki nalo pitinaęž‰taęž‰ mo weki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kiki epenaęž‰ leeke handa mo weki meao hayeke wandaęž‰maęž‰ kiki yolaęž‰ mea wepiki pu tunkilikimaęž‰ tonkao alotaęž‰ Doeki ambaęž‰la titinaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰laęž‰me leekepate
\v 29 pa mo wekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki paa yolaęž‰ mea mo hameke maęž‰ndaęž‰ ambaęž‰la mendiekeme. Kotaęž‰ mo weki meao hayeke wandaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dupiki haumaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ potaęž‰ pondaęž‰pa ipulu pikaęž‰taęž‰me leekeme. Kotaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Petese leekeme.
\v 30 Kutupa mo ipikaęž‰ hameke mo wepiki pu kikinaęž‰ tonkaeyeke wekitaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ mendia ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Sita lemekeme.
\c 39
\s1 Diosepe pitaęž‰ Podipanaęž‰ weteke yaapo
\p 
\v 1 Mo hande Isimaęž‰elo tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ Idiepi nane Diosepe hatuku pua mo kininaęž‰ da handeteke haenaęž‰ leeke aminaęž‰ you some maęž‰ndaęž‰ Podipa paęž‰taęž‰ tapaemekeme.
\v 2 Mo Tekehalitaęž‰ Diosepe yaapo hayeke ekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pieke hau paeyao epeayekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ pahameke e pokao hayeke Idiepi halinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pelia hayekeme.
\v 3 Kutupa koto somemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Tekehalitaęž‰ Diosepe yaapo hayekeeki yalo ipikaęž‰ pieke hau paeya tapaomaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ piekeeki handeekeme.
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰ Podipamaęž‰taęž‰ mo wekimaęž‰ pieke hau manunaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki pi e pokaasaęž‰ some haenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da make ipikaęž‰ wia hayeke alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaonaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ you hali haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 5 Koto natenaęž‰ kini peaataęž‰ mo Diosepe hayeke ekinaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Idiepi halinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ wieke alemanu paeyao make oni e ninaęž‰ haemeke alemanu make paeyao epeayekeme.
\v 6 Podipamaęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ wia hayeke alemanu paeyao sikitaęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ kiki paęž‰taęž‰ u moneaaso hataęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ hone na wikitaęž‰ pa nolo pieke nenaęž‰ homeke hone wiekeme.
\p Diosepetaęž‰ loke panka hali seliapo hayekeme.
\v 7 Kutupa hao hao peaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you somenaęž‰ wetekemaęž‰taęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ da tunkulolo hataęž‰ da pandaęž‰ nane polupanaęž‰ panaęž‰e laa honke leekeme.
\v 8 Koto leeke mo wekimaęž‰ kiaaso hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰e. Yaka you halimaęž‰taęž‰ do IĚ± halo ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ hone bao halaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao IĚ±maęž‰ handeteke hano laęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 9 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ honkopu kone IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ make alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao handeteke hano laęž‰laęž‰pate neke homeke diaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ pa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau pitolo hataęž‰ do nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ale hoke hautaęž‰ ekipa peonope laa leekeme.
\v 10 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hoto paeyao Diosepe honke laęž‰tia pulu hayekepate mo wandaęž‰ yaapo otaęž‰ na polu peekeme.
\v 11 Kutu piekepate nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Diosepetaęž‰ oni da paęž‰taęž‰ e pokulueke alo peekepate mo da paęž‰taęž‰ e pokao haemeke tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰ make otaęž‰ na haemekeme.
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ dau hokulupeke mineke hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Oni da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ dikaęž‰ polupanaęž‰ panaęž‰ epoma leekepate mo wekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dautaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ kiki paęž‰taęž‰ holaęž‰mea wia haenaęž‰ hama pindipa opolu baeyekeme.
\v 13 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo wekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau minaęž‰paęž‰lao hama opolu baeyaęž‰ eki hando haotaęž‰
\v 14 kotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ e pokaemeke mandane wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ eĚ± wi alo alotaęž‰ Do ale handaęž‰pee. Do hande yaka halikimaęž‰ hatuku epeaęž‰ Hibulu wekimaęž‰taęž‰ niki yalaęž‰ peake hau paęž‰laęž‰mee. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yaka da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa IĚ± minuluekemaęž‰ piaęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ eĚ± wi tieke loaęž‰me.
\v 15 Mo ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ eĚ± wi loaęž‰eki opu haotaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau winaęž‰ winaęž‰ pea hama opolu bao paęž‰laęž‰mee leekeme.
\v 16 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ dautaęž‰ pa wia pita mo wekinaęž‰ you some epeeke handaa waleekeme.
\v 17 Kutupa mo hande ambaęž‰ leekeeki kone paa laa halolo alotaęž‰ Mo nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hande hatuku epe pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ Hibulu wekimaęž‰taęž‰ yalaęž‰ peake hau puluekemaęž‰ yaka da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ epeaęž‰me.
\v 18 Kutu piekepate pa mo IĚ±maęž‰ eĚ± wi loaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ do ipikaęž‰ dau winaęž‰ winaęž‰ pu hama opolu baeyaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Kotaęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ you somemaęž‰ kotoeki opu haotaęž‰ tetomaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰
\v 20 Diosepe mininaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ dipula haliweki pitaeyeke ale paęž‰taęž‰ dipula pitinaęž‰ leekeme. Kutupa Diosepetaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ hao hayekeme.
\v 21 Pate mo Tekehalitaęž‰ Diosepe yaapo hataęž‰ ipiki epeayekeeki yalo mo dipula handeteke hayeke halimaęž‰ make Diosepe yaapo taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 22 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo somemaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepetaęž‰ mo mandane dipula haliweki paeyao handeteke haenaęž‰ laa make mo dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ pieke haumanu paeyaotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 23 Mo Tekehalitaęž‰ Diosepe yaapo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pieke haumanu paeyaotaęž‰ pu epeayeke handaa mo dipula handeteke hayeke somemaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ leeke ale manutaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa na handeteke hayekeme.
\c 40
\s1 Diosepemaęž‰ dipula hali yaaponaęž‰ upanaęž‰ teke la haleekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Hao hao pea nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Idiepi kininaęž‰ waini ikali handeteke hayeke some pitaęž‰ betedi yanko hayeke some yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kini somenaęž‰ puki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ peaepekeme.
\v 2 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo kinitaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ e pokaepeke you hali yaapo ameĚ±leĚ± mineke pankolo hataęž‰
\v 3 mo hande Diosepe pitieke ale paęž‰taęž‰ oni dipula handeteke hayeke somenaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ dipula mea pitaeyekeme.
\v 4 Hali yaapotaęž‰ nate wotunaęž‰ dipula pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo dipula handeteke hayeke somemaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepetaęž‰ mo hali yaaponaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ hali haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Timba maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ waini ikali handeteke hayeke somemaęž‰ make mo betedi yanko hayeke somemaęž‰ make telipunaęž‰maęž‰ upa teketaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pikieki pu alu pipikime.
\v 6 Diosepetaęž‰ da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso mo hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ epeekepate ipilikitaęž‰ wenoko homaęž‰niao pitipipikieki handeekeme.
\v 7 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali yaapo lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ ipilikitaęž‰ ekipeke wenoko homaęž‰niao pitipipipe leekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Koto leeke mo hali yaapomaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diki telipunaęž‰maęž‰ upa polopaęž‰pate mo upa tekemanu la kulu paęž‰laęž‰ some do pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ na halaęž‰me lepekeme.
\p Koto lepeke Diosepemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo upa laęž‰kaęž‰la halaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ honkoputaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kone kitolo pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipilikaęž‰ upa yaapo la kipee leekeme.
\p 
\v 9-10 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ waini ikali handeteke hayeke somemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya upamaęž‰taęž‰ mo yaka puki nanemaęž‰taęž‰ hopiki tepo hake waini pu hayekeme. Mo katakemanu dutaęž‰pa lopaęž‰ lopaęž‰ piaęž‰ dinaęž‰ konetaęž‰ mo momamanu liaataęž‰ mo waini kilikimanu make koto kone poteaęž‰me.
\v 11 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ kapo miniki hataęž‰ pueke ale mo waini kilikimanu mea oni kapo paęž‰taęž‰ dekepo pamba mo kini paęž‰taęž‰ haloaęž‰me laa la haleekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Diosepemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo upanaęž‰ teketaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰ peleme. Mo hopiki tepotaęž‰ nate tepoe.
\v 13 Mo tepo natenaęž‰taęž‰ kinimaęž‰ neketaęž‰ dipula minaęž‰paęž‰lalenaęž‰ laa nakaęž‰ hande poko hae e paa pokoelenaęž‰ laęž‰lieke. Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ waini ikali handeteke hae tupaęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ kapo paa halo halipikie.
\v 14 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate mo neke epeke tupaęž‰ pua hao pelikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± hone wiaęž‰peke. Kutupa make pilisi IĚ± do dipula minaęž‰paęž‰lano aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minolo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo kini paęž‰taęž‰ pua opuapeke leekeme.
\v 15 Pa ekipeke IĚ±taęž‰ mo Hibulu tapakenaęž‰ kenke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pake mea aęž‰pa ame do Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ maketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ dipula pulaęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na puaęž‰pate kone pelememe laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Kotaęž‰ mo hande betedi yanko hayeke you somemaęž‰taęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ waini ikali handeteke hayeke you halinaęž‰ upa tekemanu la haleeke ekitaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ la haleeke handa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make upa dupa puaęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ betedi wiki kawaso paeyao tepo yaka younaęž‰ tuekeme.
\v 17 Kutupa mo otaęž‰ manda tepo peao tueke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ anemone taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki palaowa kitikimanu yekeme. Kutupa mo ba manumaęž‰ mu nememe.
\p 
\v 18 Diosepemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Teketaęž‰ dupae. Mo kawaso tepotaęž‰ nate tepo la paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 19 Nate teponaęž‰taęž‰ kinimaęž‰ neketaęž‰ dipula minaęž‰paęž‰lalenaęž‰ laataęž‰ nakaęž‰ make tunkilieke. Kutupa nakaęž‰ loketaęž‰ ti hokulunaęž‰ endialimi alenaęž‰ mo ba titimaęž‰ nakaęž‰ loke nelimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Kotaęž‰ nate tepo paeyeketaęž‰ mo kinimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mendieke nate mieke handa ipikaęž‰ you haliweki manunaęž‰ ne pambaaso hataęž‰ mo hande ipikaęž‰ waini ikali handeteke hatiki pieke you some make mo betedi yanko hatiki pieke you some make telipunaęž‰ dipula da minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo ipikaęž‰ you haliweki pitimiki alenaęž‰ hatuku epeekeme.
\v 21 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo waini ikali handeteke hayeke you sometaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande enaęž‰ paa haenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰taęž‰
\v 22 mo palaowa yanko hatiki pieke you sometaęž‰ lia endiayekeme. Do hau paeyaotaęž‰ mo hande Diosepemaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ siki kone piekeme.
\v 23 Pate mo kininaęž‰ waini ikali handeteke hawayeke somemaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepe otaęž‰ hone na wiki hone yonkaęž‰la kilipayekeme.
\c 41
\s1 Diosepemaęž‰ mo kini halinaęž‰ upa manunaęž‰ teke la haleekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Koto hao pea bapi yaapo paeyeketaęž‰ mo Idiepi kini ipikaęž‰ upamaęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo Naili ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ hayekeeki handeekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa mo ikali paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ loke panka wiki yonkeleke homu piki wataake hataęž‰ kaomanu opaęž‰liaotaęž‰ mo ambumanu nalo haemekeme.
\v 3 Kutupataęž‰ pa mandane wataake hataęž‰ kaomanu make opaęž‰liaememe. Koto kao manutaęž‰ loke diaęž‰ya make paęž‰taęž‰liki holiki yapeekeme. Ikitaęž‰ mo titinaęž‰ kaomanu haemeke alenaęž‰ mo ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ pua haemekeme.
\v 4 Kutupa mo loke diaęž‰yeke kao manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo loke panka wiki kaomanu naęž‰taęž‰ paemekeme. Kotoeki handolo hataęž‰ mo kinitaęž‰ paa tiaeyekeme.
\v 5 Kutupa ipiki paa polu holaęž‰pa upa maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa piekeme. Kunimaęž‰ handeke ale widi opeekeeki liki homekenaęž‰taęž‰ napeke paeyao wataake hataęž‰ wiekeme. Mo napeke manutaęž‰ panka wia napea wiekeme.
\v 6 Kutupa pa wataake hataęž‰ widi napekemanu homeke ekinaęž‰ ombu opaęž‰liaeyekepate mo napeketaęž‰ na pankeekeme. Kotaęž‰ mo hapupa paęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ yamaęž‰ epeeke titipu piki pomaęž‰taęž‰ mo napeke pou taeyekeme.
\v 7 Kutupa mo na pankeke widi napeke manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo panka wiki napekemanu mea naęž‰taęž‰ paemekeme. Kotaęž‰ mo kini tiaotaęž‰ upamaęž‰ puaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa handaęž‰ wiekeme.
\v 8 Da kaęž‰laęž‰paasotaęž‰ mo kinimaęž‰taęž‰ hone kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ mo Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke tiĚ±oĚ± haliweki make mo hone u lenkene pimiki tapake make wi laęž‰ mipi piekeme. Kutupa koto haliweki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ upa yaapo kelepeekepate homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ teke otaęž‰ la halaęž‰peke na yekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo waini ikali handeteke hayeke you somemaęž‰ mo kini paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau polomaęž‰ ame neke paęž‰taęž‰ keleponoe.
\v 10 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ palaowa yanko hayaęž‰ some diki paęž‰taęž‰ mineke pankolo hataęž‰ mo dipula handeteke halaęž‰ somenaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ dipula mea lopaeme.
\v 11 Kotaęž‰ timba maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ diki telipunaęž‰maęž‰ teke taęž‰taęž‰ wiki upa pu alu pupaęž‰me.
\v 12 Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ diki ameĚ±leĚ± mo Hibulu weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ da handeteke haenaęž‰ lele aminaęž‰ you somenaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ weki yekeme. Dikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ dikaęž‰ upa kelepopeke handaataęž‰ mo upa yaaponaęž‰ teketaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ diki la kiaęž‰me.
\v 13 Koto mo somemaęž‰ leaęž‰ tupaęž‰ konetaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ yaka e paa kipate mo betedi yanko hayaęž‰ you sometaęž‰ lu endiaeme laa la haleekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Koto leeke ekinaęž‰ mo kinimaęž‰ Diosepe handaęž‰ mealo pupaęž‰ leeke handaa koto kone mo dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰ mea epeekeme. Mo weki ipikaęž‰ yankake itiki mea akaęž‰ topo pea paeyeketaęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ epeekeme.
\v 15 Kutupa mo kinimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ upa puaęž‰pate maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ koto upanaęž‰ teke la kiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo upa tekemanu lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa leaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Koto leeke Diosepemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Aneke halio. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ homeke epeke tupaęž‰ teke la kilieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Mo kinimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka upamaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo Naili ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ hataęž‰ puekeme.
\v 18 Kutupa mo ikali paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ loke panka wiki yonkeleke homu piki wataake hataęž‰ kaomanu opaęž‰liaotaęž‰ mo ambumanu nalo haememe.
\v 19 Kutupataęž‰ pa wataake hataęž‰ kaomanu opaęž‰liaememe. Mo koto kao manutaęž‰ loke diaęž‰ya paęž‰taęž‰liki holiki yapeekeme. Koto kao manutaęž‰ do Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰manu IĚ± otaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na hando alo otaęž‰ hoke kaomanu yekeme.
\v 20 Mo loke na pankeke kao manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo loke panka wiki kaomanu naęž‰taęž‰ paememe.
\v 21 Kutu pimipate mo kaomanu nemekeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰ wiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo kao manutaęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ haeme tupaęž‰ kone paa haemekeme. Kutupataęž‰ IĚ± tiaowaęž‰me.
\v 22 Koto timba kone pa upa maęž‰ndaęž‰ puaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo kunimaęž‰ handeke ale widi opeekeeki homeke likinaęž‰taęž‰ napeke paeyao wataake hataęž‰ wiekeme. Mo napeke manutaęž‰ panka wia napea wiekeme.
\v 23 Kutupa pa wataake hataęž‰ widi napekemanu homeke ekinaęž‰ ombu opaęž‰liaeyekepate mo napeketaęž‰ na pankeekeme. Kotaęž‰ mo hapupa paęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ yamaęž‰ epeeke titipu piki pomaęž‰taęž‰ mo napekemanu pou taeyekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa mo na pankeke widi napeke manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo panka wiki napekemanu naęž‰taęž‰ paememe. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do upa yaapotaęž‰ mo tiĚ±oĚ± haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ kelepoaęž‰pate pa homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ teke otaęž‰ la kiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰me laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Diosepemaęž‰ mo kini paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo upa yaaponaęž‰ teketaęž‰ homeke konee. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki neke paęž‰taęž‰ la kaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 26 Mo panka wiki wataake hataęž‰ kao manutaęž‰ wataake hataęž‰ bapi manue. Kutupa mo panka ulaęž‰ wataake hataęž‰ kunimaęž‰ handeke widi napeke make homeke tupaęž‰ wataake hataęž‰ bapi manue. Mo upa yaaponaęž‰ teketaęž‰ homeke konee.
\v 27 Kutupa mo wetepenaęž‰ opaęž‰liaeyeke loke na pankeke wataake hataęž‰ kaomanu pitaęž‰ mo na pankeke kunimaęž‰ handeke widi napeke mo hapupa paęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ yamaęž‰ epeeke titipu piki pomaęž‰ pou taeyaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ bapi wataake hataęž‰naęž‰ teaęž‰ ki tieke epolo paęž‰laęž‰ekie.
\v 28 Kototaęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ hande la kuaęž‰ tupaęž‰e. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki neke paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 29 Kotaęž‰ mo bapi wataake hataęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ do Idiepi kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ne wotu tande pilieke.
\v 30 Kotoeki hoki nanetaęž‰ bapi wataake hataęž‰naęž‰ teaęž‰ ki ipilieke. Koto hoke teaęž‰ ki ipulu do kenke hoeyaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande epeke bapi manutaęž‰ hone yonkaęž‰lalimikie.
\v 31 Mo ne tande peaęž‰ bapi manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ hone yonkaęž‰lalimikie. Pa ekipeke mo ipiliaęž‰ teaęž‰ kitaęž‰ otaęž‰ teto pikieki ipilieke.
\v 32 Mo hoto yaapo peao pele upanaęž‰ teketaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ pulueke laa wia kutupa teke paęž‰taęž‰ kone pinaęž‰ lelieke.
\p 
\v 33 Koto ekinaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hone u lenkene paęž‰laęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ do kenke handeteke haenaęž‰ maĚ±leke luelenaęž‰e.
\v 34 Kutupa make mandane handeteke halo pimiki you halimanu meataęž‰ mo ne wopu witaęž‰laęž‰ bapi wataake hataęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ amu pimi ne manutaęž‰ yunki hataęž‰ lo winaęž‰ laataęž‰ homeke lo meataęž‰ mu mombelenaęž‰ lapeke.
\v 35 Mo tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ mo ipulaęž‰ epeke bapimanu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ koto ne paeyaomanu mu mombelenaęž‰ laataęž‰ Kutupa oni daoni paęž‰taęž‰manu koto kunimaęž‰ handeke widi kilikimanu wiaęž‰peke damanu aęž‰enaęž‰ biki halaataęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ lenaęž‰ lapekee.
\v 36 Mo koto Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ teaęž‰ kitaęž‰ mo amu pea wilimi nemaęž‰ do Idiepi wandaęž‰hali paeyao epealieke. Do hau pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao teaęž‰maęž‰ na homilimikie leekeme.
\s1 Diosepetaęž‰ Idiepinaęž‰ you hali haenaęž‰ leekeeki
\p 
\v 37 Mo kini hali pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you haliwekimaęž‰ make do Diosepemaęž‰ leeke pinaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa
\v 38 mo kini halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Diosepe ankulake Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidi pilaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na handaęž‰ ulumeke leekeme.
\v 39 Kutupa mo kinimaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do hau paeyao neke paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ mo nakanaęž‰maęž‰ aneke tupaęž‰ hone u lenkene pitele ekitaęž‰ paeyao otaęž‰ ankulaleeki handolomaęž‰me.
\v 40 IĚ±maęž‰ neketaęž‰ yaka kenke paeyao handeteke halenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo yaka wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pipaęž‰ lelipieki opua pinaęž‰ lolueke. Nakaęž‰ handeteke hale ekitaęž‰ ya handeteke halo ekinaęž‰ yaapo peao winaęž‰e.
\v 41 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neketaęž‰ do Idiepi kenke paeyaonaęž‰ kapomaninaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ you hali pituelenaęž‰ ame maĚ±leke litolome leekeme.
\v 42 Mo kinimaęž‰taęž‰ mo kapomaninaęž‰ handeteke pilaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi tonkao u halaęž‰ linitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kikinaęž‰ holaęž‰ mea Diosepenaęž‰ kikinaęž‰ pitaeyekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ mo epeke dau seliapo maęž‰ndaęž‰ pambawaotaęž‰ kolomaęž‰ wepiki senipu ipikaęž‰ make paęž‰taęž‰ mokaeyekeme.
\v 43 Kutupa pomu lopenaęž‰taęž‰ mo kinimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yaapo peao hosimaęž‰ yola pulaęž‰ ale mo Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ halaataęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ handeteke haemeke haliwekitaęž‰ Diosepe titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la pulu hataęž‰ eĚ± wi laęž‰ moneaaso alotaęž‰ Potaęž‰ pilae. Potaęž‰ pilae laa lenaęž‰ leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepetaęž‰ Idiepi kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ kapomaninaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ hali pitiekeme.
\v 44 Mo kinimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ kini yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ do Idiepi kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ some homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ sikimaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ aleeki na miki hataęž‰taęž‰ kiki anke kone na mea minaęž‰liaenaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 45-46 Kutupa Diosepetaęž‰ mo Idiepi biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Saęž‰penaęž‰de Pania halaataęž‰ mo Heliopolisi daoni paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke yeni peao hayeke hali Podipitanaęž‰ waneke Aęž‰senaęž‰de minaęž‰ haleekeme.
\p Diosepetaęž‰ 30 bapinaęž‰ mo Idiepinaęž‰ kininaęž‰ e kini pea pokaeyekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ da minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Idiepi kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pomu lopeekeme.
\v 47 Mo ne tandepeeke bapi wataake hataęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ ne tieke opeeketaęž‰
\v 48 Diosepemaęž‰ meataęž‰ mo daoni paęž‰taęž‰manu da aęž‰eya mu mombeleekeme. Daoni homeke homeke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ koto daoni teaęž‰naęž‰ hao yapeeke e paęž‰taęž‰manu ne meataęž‰ da aęž‰eya mu mombaęž‰la wiaęž‰tiki piekeme.
\v 49 Kunimaęž‰ handeke widitaęž‰ otaęž‰ tieke wieke ekiyalo Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ tombo mieke ekitaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰laeyekeme. Mo widitaęž‰ dawalanaęž‰ houmaęž‰ handeekeme.
\p 
\v 50 Mo teaęž‰ ki epolo piaęž‰ bapimanu aĚ±iĚ± na epeke haenaęž‰taęž‰ Aęž‰senaęž‰demaęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ weki yaapo mendiaeyekeme.
\v 51 Diosepemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ mo IĚ±maęž‰ muaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu make yaka tapake make hone yonkaęž‰lano laęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ Mo mupeke wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Maęž‰naęž‰saęž‰ leekeme.
\v 52 Kutupa make alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo yaka kaęž‰ndaęž‰ molo kenke paęž‰taęž‰ wekiwandiki kaęž‰laęž‰me laa mo yaapo peao mendieke wekinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Ipoteimi leekeme.
\p 
\v 53 Kutupa mo hande Idiepi tapakenaęž‰ ne tande peeke taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homemeke wataake hataęž‰ bapitaęž‰ paelo epeekeme.
\v 54 Kutupa mo hande Diosepemaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ kone mo teaęž‰ kinaęž‰ wataake hataęž‰ bapi kini piekeme. Kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ teaęž‰ ki tieke epeekepate Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ homeketaęž‰ ne pa wiekeme.
\v 55 Mo Idiepi wandaęž‰ hali teaęž‰maęž‰ homolotaęž‰ mo kini paęž‰taęž‰ nenaęž‰ honke loloendi pimikime. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo kinimaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ penaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pipe leliaęž‰eki piaęž‰paęž‰peke laa leekeme.
\v 56 Mo teaęž‰ kitaęž‰ mo Idiepi kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ putupolo hataęž‰ otaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰tia peeke handa Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ mo ne damanu lumba mo Idiepi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ widimanu tapatiki piekeme.
\v 57 Mo teaęž‰ kitaęž‰ kenke taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ putupieke handaa mo kenke taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ oni Idiepi da paęž‰taęž‰ widi hambuluekemaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ epemekeme.
\c 42
\s1 Diosepenaęž‰ hameke tonu widi hambolo Idiepi pemekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Idiepi nane widi ulaęž‰me leekeeki opu hao ipikaęž‰ eiyeke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ekipeke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na pitelemepe.
\v 2 Oni Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ widi ulaęž‰maęž‰ aleke opitolo loaęž‰maęž‰ do niki teaęž‰maęž‰ homaamaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ koto nane pua hambaęž‰pee leekeme.
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ hameke tonu paeyao kiki yaapo weki tonutaęž‰ Idiepi nane widi hambolo pemekeme.
\v 4 Pate Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diosepenaęž‰ hameke wetepe nane weki Benisaminitaęž‰ mo hameke tonu ameĚ±leĚ± na tapaeyekeme. Pa ekipeke ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo weki paęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ peaamaęž‰naęž‰e hone wiekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Mo Keinani kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ teaęž‰ ki tieke pambeke handaataęž‰ mo Dieikopenaęž‰ eiyeke tonu ameĚ±leĚ± mandane wandaęž‰hali make apaęž‰tao widi hambolo pemekeme.
\v 6 Mo Idiepi kenkenaęž‰ kapomani handeteke hayeke some Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke honiki wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ widi tapatiki piekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ hameke tonumaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ leke popeleke oni kenkenaęž‰ wataaso haenaęž‰ aęž‰pa pandaęž‰ puniaemekeme.
\v 7 Diosepemaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ hameke tonutaęž‰ handeekepate kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa na handeke nono pea hayekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo tapake paęž‰taęž‰ pi takaęž‰lakemaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ hanemaęž‰ epelemepe leekeme. Koto leeke mo tapakemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ mo Keinani hao ne hambuluekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa pumaęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Mo Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke tonue laa handaęž‰ wiekepate mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kamee laa na handaęž‰ wimikime.
\v 9 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ handaęž‰ ikinaęž‰ pieke upamanu niminaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ kika ikiki haliwekie. Ikitaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ kenke hando paęž‰taęž‰ damako paęž‰laęž‰pe laa handolo aęž‰pa pelememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Koto leeke mo tapakemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tiekeo. Diaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ e pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ tapake au laa ne hambolo epomaęž‰me.
\v 11 Tiekeo. Nikitaęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰e. Nikitaęž‰ kika ikiki haliweki diaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pu halomaęž‰ haliwekie lemekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Pate Diosepemaęž‰ mo tapake paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diaęž‰me. Ikitaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ kenke hando paęž‰taęž‰ damako paęž‰laęž‰pe laa handolo epelememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Mo tapakemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tiekeo. Nikitaęž‰ paeyao kiki yaapo paeya ankenaęž‰ yaapo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ yaęž‰me. Mo Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ some homekenaęž‰ wekitonue. Pate weki homeketaęž‰ homeaęž‰me. Kutupa mo wetepe nane wekitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ apaęž‰ yaapo halaęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Diosepemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Pa mo hande IĚ±maęž‰ loaęž‰ handaęž‰e. Ikitaęž‰ kika ikiki haliwekie.
\v 15 Ametaęž‰ dotaęž‰ iki yokaalo polo tupaęž‰e. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ keke pi alo alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na peke pa haotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wetepe nane weki epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pelimikie.
\v 16 Iki homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo weki handaęž‰ mulu puaęž‰paęž‰peke. Paeyaotaęž‰ dipula pitaotaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ aleme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰pe laa ambaęž‰laęž‰ yokaalumeke. Diaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ kini otaęž‰ halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ kika ikiki haliwekie laa peneme yaęž‰lieke leekeme.
\v 17 Kutupataęž‰ mo tapaketaęž‰ hoto tepo dipula pitaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Mo tepo natenaęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ mo tapake paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paalaęž‰ haso hali yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hau homeke homeketaęž‰ iki homaamaęž‰naęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ tambaęž‰ mulueke.
\v 19 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi lelemepe laa handaęž‰ uluekemaęž‰taęž‰ iki homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ dipula pa pitinaęž‰e. Kutupa iki paeyaotaęž‰ pa laęž‰kaęž‰la pua mo hande hambeme widi manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ tapake paęž‰taęž‰ mea poemenaęž‰e.
\v 20 Kutupa ikaęž‰ kame wetepe wekitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku aęž‰paęž‰paęž‰peke. Koto hau pilimi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ pi lelememe laa iki na lu homalueke leekeme.
\p Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do pinaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laa
\v 21 ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Aowe. Ametaęž‰ mo hande nikaęž‰ kame paęž‰taęž‰ pumaęž‰ haunaęž‰ kiliki kone talolomaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ipiki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke minolo hataęž‰ ipiki tambaęž‰ mipee laa honke leaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ kone na opumaęž‰me. Kutu pumaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ame nikitaęž‰ do kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halomaęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Lubenimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo weki na liaęž‰paęž‰pee loaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yaka pi na opimime. Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 23 Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ mo tapakemaęž‰ lemeke ekitaęž‰ opiekepate mo tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ kotoeki hone na wimikime. Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo pi laęž‰kaęž‰laeyaęž‰ some paęž‰taęž‰ laa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ mea halaęž‰tiki piaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 24 Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ mo tapake minaęž‰paęž‰lao pua eĚ± leekeme. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ pi anaęž‰naęž‰ lapeke yeketaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰pa mo ikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ Simiono maĚ±leke lia mina mea tonkaenaęž‰ leekeme.
\s1 Diosepenaęž‰ hameketonu Keinani laęž‰kaęž‰la pemekeeki
\p 
\v 25 Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ mo e pokaemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ hameke tonunaęž‰ nu manutaęž‰ mo widi napeke manumaęž‰ tumbao mo homeke homekenaęž‰ widi hambemeke manitaęž‰ mo nu kakenaęž‰ paa mendiamaęž‰ mendiamaęž‰ peaataęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ nolo pimiki ne make halaęž‰paęž‰peke leeke handa otaęž‰ kutu pimikime.
\v 26 Kutupa mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo widi nu manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ donki manunaęž‰ hokinaęž‰ atula atula pea mea wia pemekeme.
\v 27 Mo potaęž‰naęž‰ timbaęž‰ leeke pua pelimiki alenaęž‰ mo hameke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ donkinaęž‰ ne halueke alo hataęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ nu maęž‰ndaęž‰ tokiekepate mo nu kakenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mani paa mendipelia hayekeeki handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 28 Aęž‰paęž‰e. Yaka manitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰pa piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa penkilipaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameketonu paęž‰taęž‰ wi alo alotaęž‰ Do handaęž‰pe. Yaka nu paęž‰taęž‰ mendaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme. Kutupa mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰naęž‰ puki keapa olinaęž‰ oninaęž‰ pitolo pututumaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone lotaęž‰ pu alualu pitolo alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ eki hau pea paęž‰laęž‰pe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Iki mo Keinani nane paa opolo aęž‰paataęž‰ ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande iki paęž‰taęž‰ piekeeki paeyaosiki aęž‰pa la halolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 30 Mo Idiepinaęž‰ kapomaninaęž‰ you somemaęž‰taęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ pi takaęž‰lake alo hataęž‰ nikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kenke handuluekemaęž‰ kika ikiki haliweki pomaęž‰me leaęž‰me.
\v 31 Koto leeke nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ kika ikiki haliweki diaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pitolomaęž‰ tapakee laa
\v 32 Nikitaęž‰ hali homekenaęž‰ wekitonu paeyao kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ yaapo yaęž‰mee. Weki homeketaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa wetepe nane wekitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ apaęž‰ yaapo oni Keinani pa halaęž‰me lomaęž‰me.
\v 33 Kutupa mo you halimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi lo haleme haliwekie laa handuluekemaęž‰taęž‰ dupulueke. Iki maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondotaęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± pa hapelia hataęž‰taęž‰ mo iki paeyaotaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ tapakenaęž‰ widi napekemanu mea pupee laataęž‰
\v 34 Ikaęž‰ wetepe nane wekitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku aęž‰paęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ kika ikiki haliweki diaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ pi aleme haliwekie hone ulueke. Kutupa do ikaęž‰ kame iki paęž‰taęž‰ paa kiakaęž‰naęž‰ ikitaęž‰ dopate hataęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ pa tapamenaęž‰e laa leaęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 35 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ numanu tokimi dinaęž‰taęž‰ homeke homekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ mani nu handaęž‰ wimikime. Kutupa mo mani hando haotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰ make paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme.
\v 36 Ikaęž‰ apaęž‰maęž‰ mo wekitonu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ yaka wekiwandiki paeyao alu pano pitelemepe. Diosepe paęž‰laęž‰me. Simiono make paęž‰laęž‰me. Ametaęž‰ Benisamini mea polukumaęž‰ alemepe. IĚ±taęž‰ mo teto minolo somee leekeme.
\p 
\v 37 Koto leeke Lubenimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ Benisamini aęž‰ndaęž‰ paa na hatuku epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaka weki yaapo luelenaęž‰e. Mo wekitaęž‰ yaka kiki paęž‰taęž‰ wie. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ paa hatuku ipulueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 38 Pate Dieikopemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka wekitaęž‰ neke yaapo na penaęž‰ lolueke. Ipikaęž‰ hameketaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipiki homeke hapelia halaęž‰me. Mo potaęž‰naęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ peaapaęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ koke hali yaalo hataęž‰ mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mea ipilimi puki tandamaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± lu homaliekee leekeme.
\c 43
\s1 Mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maęž‰ Benisamini hatuku Idiepi pemekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Oni Keinani nanetaęž‰ mo teaęž‰ kitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoeyekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa mo Dieikopenaęž‰ tapakemaęž‰ mo hande Idiepi nane hambolo pua mea epemeke widitaęž‰ naęž‰taęž‰ paotaęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰ eiyeketonu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Paa pua nikaęž‰ ne tepo aęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ pua hambaęž‰pee leekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Diudamaęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande you halimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ pi takaęž‰lakemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ kame na hatuku epemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke popeleke na handulueke laa leaęž‰me.
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ kame niki ameĚ±leĚ± tapaalueke hone wikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ ne hambalo polumeke.
\v 5 Pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ na tapaalueke lekenaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ kame niki ameĚ±leĚ± ipikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ pomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ homeketaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me leaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ na polumeke leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Dieikopemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ do kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke epenaęž‰yeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ekipeke ikaęž‰ kame maęž‰ndaęž‰ halaęž‰me laa la halaa pelemepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo halimaęž‰taęž‰ niki make nikaęž‰ tapake make lotaęž‰ lotaęž‰ ombu piaęž‰me. Ikaęž‰ apaęž‰taęž‰ pa halaęž‰pe o Ikaęž‰ kame maęž‰ndaęž‰ halaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ ombu piaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peapeke yeke lomaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ kame hatuku aęž‰paęž‰paęž‰peke laa lolo piaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa ekipa hone wiomono alepe.
\p 
\v 8 Diudamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki koto kone polumekemaęž‰ mo weki IĚ± yaapo tapae. Kutu pumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ niki maęž‰ndaęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ na homulumeke.
\v 9 Mo weki paęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ maketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ winaęž‰e. IĚ±maęž‰ mo weki hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ peao epeke tupaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ na hatuku epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pu hoeyaluaęž‰ haunaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ winaęž‰ loelenaęž‰e.
\v 10 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nateleke hokulunaęž‰ na yuwia haomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ ametaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hoto yaapo pua epolo pumaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Ikaęž‰ apaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ kutu pulu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ opaęž‰laęž‰ epeke nemanu ikaęž‰ nu paęž‰taęž‰manu mendiao mo kapomani handeteke halaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ ale mea puapee. Mo ale manutaęž‰ pa totopo piki ti yonkeleke sikimaęž‰ make hosiki boi hapeke make mo ne totopo peaasaęž‰ alemanu make mo (pei kilikimaęž‰ handeke) pisidasio kiliki make (mo saęž‰tikimaęž‰ handeke) amono kiliki make mea puapee.
\v 12 Kutupa make mo hande ikaęž‰ nu kake ninaęž‰ mendiaeyeke manitaęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ peaopate pimimaęž‰ pao mea puaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ moeki hakaęž‰taęž‰pao yaapo peao mea puaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 13 Kutupa ikaęž‰ kame make hatuku puaataęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± koto kone paa laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰paęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 14 Mo you halimaęž‰taęž‰ Benisamini make mo ikaęž‰ kame maęž‰ndaęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo kinaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ mo Aneke Wele wopupiki Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo some paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki halenaęž‰e. Kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ yaka wekiwandiki alupawaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ alupaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu make mo mani hakaęž‰taęž‰pao yaapo peao mea Benisamini ameĚ±leĚ± Idiepi nane pemekeme. Koto pate ikitaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ pua walemekeme.
\v 16 Kutupa Diosepemaęž‰ mo tapake ameĚ±leĚ± Benisamini hayekeeki hando haotaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ da handeteke hawayeke e pokaeyeke some paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do haliweki yaka da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pue. Ikitaęž‰ natepa nane IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± ne nelimikimaęž‰ mo koa maęž‰naęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ lia amu peapeke leekeme.
\v 17 Mo e pokaeyeke halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo piaęž‰peke leeke tupaęž‰ mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hatuku Diosepenaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ mo da paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epeeketaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ dupiki hone wimikime. Niki do paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku ipulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo hande titinaęž‰ hande nikaęž‰ nu paęž‰taęž‰manu mendieke maninaęž‰ pate pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Ametaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki hoeyao make nikaęž‰ donkimanu make mea nikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasomaęž‰ tapake hamono lelimikie laa hone wimikime.
\v 19 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo da potaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua hataęž‰ mo e pokao hayaęž‰ handeteke hayeke some paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 20 Tiekeo. Pilisi nakanaęž‰maęž‰ opie. Nikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hoto homeke do paęž‰taęž‰ ne hambolo epomaęž‰me.
\v 21 Kutupa paa pua timbaęž‰ leeke palai da pua aęž‰eyaataęž‰ nikaęž‰ numanu pua tokua handomaęž‰pate hali homeke homekemaęž‰ nikaęž‰ mani otaęž‰ anaęž‰ sikinaęž‰ mendieke handaa pao mea epolomaęž‰me.
\v 22 Kutupa make ne maęž‰ndaęž‰ hambulumekemaęž‰ yeke mandane mani make mea epolomaęž‰me. Mo nikaęž‰ nu paęž‰taęž‰manu mo mani paa mendiaeyeke sometaęž‰ epimaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ o niki mataęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Mo e pokaeyeke somemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hone ti yokolo hataęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ numanu paęž‰taęž‰ mo mani paa mendiao paęž‰laęž‰mee. Ikaęž‰ yenki manutaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ muaęž‰me leekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Simiono iki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epeekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Mo e pokaeyeke somemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku mea epeekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ ankemanu tandepolo pimiki tupaęž‰ ikali halaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ donkimanu make ne haleekeme.
\v 25 Mo tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ natepa nane Diosepe ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ ne nelimikie laa la haleeke handa mo hande pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu tikitiki yao pitimikime.
\v 26 Kutupa Diosepe da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo epeeketaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu oni da paęž‰taęž‰ mea pua ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua pandaęž‰ puniaemekeme.
\v 27 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ halemepe laa alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ kokenaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ IĚ± la kimimaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ eki paęž‰laęž‰pe. Ipikitaęž‰ pa halaęž‰pe o epeke halaęž‰pe laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ epeke homupiki e pokaasaęž‰ hali mo nikaęž‰ apaęž‰taęž‰ pa epeke tupaęž‰ halaęž‰mee lemekeme. Koto laataęž‰ tumiki yotuao ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniaemekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Kutupa Diosepemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke Benisamini hando hao alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ hande IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ la kimi ikaęž‰ wetepe nane weki yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me. Yaka wekio. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke epeaenaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 30 Koto laataęž‰ Diosepe ipikaęž‰ kamenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ tanda tieke pieke handaa koto kone iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao peekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ eĚ± podelaęž‰ miaęž‰peke nono pieke handa ipikaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua eĚ± leekeme.
\v 31 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ leke popeleke tandaęž‰pataęž‰ hama opolu bao aęž‰pa ipikaęž‰ kone lu minaęž‰niao pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo ne panaęž‰ pie leekeme.
\v 32 Diosepetaęž‰ teipolo maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ panaęž‰ peao ipikaęž‰ hameke tonutaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ panaęž‰ peayekeme. Kutupa koto paęž‰taęž‰ ne nemeke Idiepi tapake manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo Hibulu tapake ameĚ±leĚ± mandake paęž‰taęž‰ pita ne napeke anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ teipolo maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰ ne nemekeme.
\v 33 Mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰taęž‰ Diosepe handaęž‰ moneao pitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ mendieke tupaęž‰ mupeke hali ambaęž‰la pita pua mo wetepe wekinaęž‰ pua pitu naenaęž‰ leekeme. Mo tapakemaęž‰ iki pitaeyeke tupaęž‰ hando haotaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone handaęž‰ alu alu pimikime.
\v 34 Mo netaęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ teipolonaęž‰ panaęž‰ piekeme. Kutupa Benisaminitaęž‰ mo hameke tonunaęž‰eki make ankulao hakaęž‰taęž‰pao mo ipikaęž‰ ne yunki peao mulu pieke tupaęž‰ haleekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo tapaketaęž‰ Diosepe ameĚ±leĚ± ne ikali no opu hao keaemekeme.
\c 44
\s1 Diosepenaęž‰ kapo alupiekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Diosepemaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ da handeteke hayeke e pokaeyeke some paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo haliwekinaęž‰ numanu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo ne ikaęž‰ mondulu peleme tupaęž‰ kone mendiaotaęž‰ pa mo homeke homekenaęž‰ manitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ nu kakenaęž‰ mendia mendia peaęž‰peke.
\v 2 Kutupa mo yaka silipamaęž‰ wepieke kapotaęž‰ mo wetepe wekinaęž‰ nu paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ widi hambeaęž‰ mani pitaęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ mendiapeke leekeme. Koto leeke mo halimaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ siki kone piekeme.
\v 3 Da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso sikitaęž‰ mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ donkimanu pitaęž‰ penaęž‰ tapaeyekeme.
\v 4 Mo tapaketaęž‰ mo daoni minaęž‰paęž‰lao pa hosiki siki papate leke pulu haenaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da handeteke hayaęž‰ some paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo haliweki teliaęž‰ mea aĚ±iĚ± pue. Kuta teliminikinaęž‰taęž‰ dupa lotaęž‰ piaęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo epeke haunaęž‰ pa hoke ekimaęž‰ yenki kia pelemepe.
\v 5 Pa ekipeke yaka you somenaęž‰ silipa kapo pake naa pelemepe. Koto ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ikali no halaęž‰eki homeke make ipikaęž‰ handehau pulukumaęž‰ meaęž‰tiki pu halaęž‰ kapoe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke hau pelememe laa lapeke leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Mo e pokaeyeke somemaęž‰ mo tapake pua teliminataęž‰ homeke pi kone pua leekeme.
\v 7 Mo tapakemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Tiekeo. Dupiki pi ale ekitaęž‰ eki la alepe. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kutupiki hau na polomaęž‰me laa keke alomaęž‰me.
\v 8 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hao ipulu hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hande nikaęž‰ nu kakenaęž‰ mendiaęž‰ mani manutaęž‰ paa mea epomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone wilime. Koto ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ mo silipa o kolotaęž‰ pa ekipeke pake nolumaęž‰pe.
\v 9 Tiekeo. Niki maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ mo ale mulumaęž‰eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ handaęž‰ wikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ lu homaenaęž‰ laataęž‰ niki paeyaotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasomaęž‰ tapake halumeke laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Mo halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo kapo maęž‰laęž‰ some homeketaęž‰ yaka pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ hali haenaęž‰ iki paeyaotaęž‰ pao pomenaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 11 Koto ekinaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ koto kone ikaęž‰ numanu oni kenkenaęž‰ mea wia homeke homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ nu toku wia pitimikime.
\v 12 Kutupa Diosepenaęž‰ e pokaeyeke somemaęž‰taęž‰ sembepelasiki mo mupeke halinaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kini pea weiyaęž‰tia pua mo wetepe halinaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pua paeyaeyekepate mo kapotaęž‰ Benisamininaęž‰ nu paęž‰taęž‰ mendieke handaęž‰ wiekeme.
\v 13 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ akaęž‰manu sinkipa ikaęž‰ numanu mo donki hokinaęž‰ paa mu wia mo daoni nane paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pemekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Mo Diuda hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ mo Diosepenaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ epemeketaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ pa pitiekeme. Kutupa ikitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniaemeke handaa
\v 15 Diosepemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ekipiki hau pea pelemepe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ dupiki e pokolo hali IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ peleme hautaęž‰ mo handehau pea na handaęž‰ ulueke hone wimipe leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Koto leeke Diudamaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Tiekeo. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ eki lomonope. Ekipa pi yokaalu piomonope. Ekipa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ diaęž‰me lomonope. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ polomaęž‰ hoke hau peneme yalaęž‰me. Mo hande kapo miaęž‰ some homeke diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate ametaęž‰ niki paeyaotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasomaęž‰ haliweki halomaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Diosepemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ O diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ kutupiki hau otaęž‰ na pulueke. Mo yaka kapo maęž‰laęž‰ some homeketaęž‰ yaka pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ some halieke. Iki paeyaotaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ siki hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na piki ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pelimikie leekeme.
\s1 Diudamaęž‰ Benisamininaęž‰ honke leekeeki.
\p 
\v 18 Diudamaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Pilisi Tiekeo. Neketaęž‰ pa mo kinimaęž‰ handele ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ pi la kiono mineke na pankaęž‰pekee.
\v 19 Tiekeo. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ apaęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰pe o ikaęž‰ kame maęž‰ndaęž‰ halaęž‰pe laa lemee.
\v 20 Koto leke nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaasotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ apaęž‰taęž‰ koke halisiki halaęž‰ make nikaęž‰ wetepe wekitaęž‰ mo koke nane maęž‰ndaęž‰laęž‰ weki make halaęž‰me. Mo wekinaęž‰ hameketaęž‰ homa inkikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ ipiki homeke pa halaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰maęž‰ mo wekitaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ wopu homaęž‰laęž‰me lomaęž‰me.
\v 21 Tiekeo. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ handuluekemaęž‰ hatuku aęž‰paęž‰pekee leke handa
\v 22 nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaasotaęž‰ mo wekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lalieke lomaęž‰me. Minaęž‰paęž‰laeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ateketaęž‰ homilieke laa lomaęž‰me.
\v 23 Koto lomeke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ wetepe weki iki ameĚ±leĚ± epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ homeke nakaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ niki handulumeke lemee.
\p 
\v 24 Kutupa niki nikaęž‰ apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ puataęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ le pimanu paeyao pua la halomaęž‰me.
\v 25 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ Paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pua ne hosikimaęž‰ pua hambaęž‰pee leaęž‰me.
\v 26 Koto leeke nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo nikaęž‰ kame wetepe nane wekitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± pomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ homeke mo halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ pua hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo nikaęž‰ kame Benisamini niki ameĚ±leĚ± peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ homeke puaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me lomaęž‰me.
\v 27 Koto lomeke nikaęž‰ apaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo yaka wandaęž‰ Leisolomaęž‰taęž‰ yaka weki yaapo homeke mendiaeyaęž‰me.
\v 28 Homeketaęž‰ IĚ± ambaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lalaęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ hoki peaęž‰ nane make otaęž‰ na handolo ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo tikene maęž‰naęž‰yeti sayale manumaęž‰ sinki sinki pea witolo paęž‰laęž‰mee.
\v 29 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ame do weki hatuku pua hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ peaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ koke yalo hataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mea ipilimi aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± lu homaalieke laa leaęž‰me laa la haleekeme.
\p 
\v 30-31 Diudamaęž‰ ombu pa alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tiekeo. Pa ametaęž‰ IĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ mo weki yaapo yaka apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na poaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo weki IĚ± yaapo na handolo kone ipiki homilieke. Ipikaęž‰ hone puki paeyaotaęž‰ koto weki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ koke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ pulumaęž‰ haumaęž‰ kone ipiki lu homaalumeke.
\v 32 Hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ make dupae. IĚ±maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo weki paęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ maketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ winaęž‰e laa yaka apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo weki aęž‰ndaęž‰ pa na hatuku epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pu hoeyaluaęž‰ haunaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ winaęž‰ loelenaęž‰e loaęž‰me.
\v 33 Koto ekinaęž‰ tiekeo. Ametaęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ anketeke minolo hataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaaso hali haluekemaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke tonu ameĚ±leĚ± paa penaęž‰ lae.
\v 34 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ eki ekipa mo wekitaęž‰ IĚ± yaapo na peke haenaęž‰ yaka apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ poluaęž‰pe. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ yaka apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki ke tieke ipulaęž‰eki handaęž‰peketaęž‰ IĚ± anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\c 45
\s1 Diosepemaęž‰ ipikie laa peneme yaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wieke hone manunaęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ e pokaemeke tapakenaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ lu minaęž‰niapeke na yalo hataęž‰ paeyaosiki mo da pandaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao pupe laa leekeme. Kotaęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± maęž‰ndaęž‰ siki otaęž‰ na haenaęž‰ mo hameke tonu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± lataa laa la haleekeme.
\v 2 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ eĚ± alo hataęž‰ anekemaęž‰ kaęž‰paęž‰puki yokeke handa mo Idiepi tapakemaęž‰ make opuaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ekinaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ make mea pemekeme.
\v 3 Diosepemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameketonu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Diosepee. Yaka apaęž‰taęž‰ pa halaęž‰pe leekeme. Koto leekepate mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ doeki opu hao paalaęž‰maęž‰ hone mamatalo hataęž‰ hombo peapeke na yekeme.
\v 4 Kotaęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pilisi IĚ± teke paęž‰taęž‰ ipupe leekeme. Kotaęž‰ mo tapake teke paęž‰taęž‰ epemeke handa alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Idiepi nane mani mea tapaeme some ikaęž‰ kame Diosepee.
\v 5 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± tapaaleme ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na homa make nikanaęž‰maęž‰ pu hoeyalomaęž‰me pi na lapaęž‰peke. Otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kone mo wandaęž‰hali homaapaęž‰naęž‰yeke. IĚ±maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰lono IĚ± ambaęž‰la tapao paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 6 Do kenke paęž‰taęž‰ mo teaęž‰ ki aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ bapi yaapo homeke do handaęž‰e. Mo yu litaęž‰laęž‰eki kone o ne napeke minaęž‰laęž‰eki kone otaęž‰ na pulu paęž‰laęž‰ bapi yunki hataęž‰taęž‰ pa ulaęž‰me.
\v 7 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± ambaęž‰la tapaalaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupiki taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ piki haumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰lono laa kutupa mo ikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilimi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki anaęž‰naęž‰ hao pelinaęž‰yeke paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 8 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± do Idiepi kenke nane na tapaemepate pa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kone paęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ kapomani manda you hali pitono laęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ do kenke paeyao handeteke halome. IĚ±taęž‰ do Idiepi wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ you hali halome.
\p 
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰ yaka apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± laęž‰kaęž‰la puataęž‰ dotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ weki Diosepemaęž‰ alaęž‰ pie laa pua lapaęž‰peke. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Idiepinaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ hali hano laęž‰laęž‰me. Nate leke hokulu na peake IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± epoe.
\v 10 Neke make nakaęž‰ wekiwandiki make nakaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki make nakaęž‰ sipisipimanu make nakaęž‰ nanikosimanu make nakaęž‰ kaomanu make mo nakaęž‰ wia hale alemanu paeyao make IĚ± teke paęž‰taęž‰ wia halo pele tupaęž‰ mo Kosene kenke paęž‰taęž‰ halenaęž‰e laataęž‰
\v 11 Neke mo Kosene kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke handeteke halo polo tupaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Mo teaęž‰ kitaęž‰ bapi yunki hataęž‰ pa ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ neke make nakaęž‰ tapake make nakaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu make teaęž‰maęž‰ homilimikiyeke loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Diosepemaęž‰ ombu alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ iki paeyaomaęž‰ make Benisamini nakanaęž‰maęž‰ make IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ Diosepee laa handelememe.
\v 13 Kutaa IĚ± do Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ honkopu tieke ulaęž‰eki make mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handeleme alemanu paeyao make yaka apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua lapaęž‰peke. Kutupa aĚ±iĚ± aĚ±iĚ± pu kone ipiki do pate hatuku aęž‰paęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Koto laataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke Benisaminitaęž‰ hopulaęž‰ mea eĚ± leekeme. Benisaminimaęž‰ make eĚ± alo hataęž‰ hameke hopulaęž‰ miekeme.
\v 15 EĚ± pa alo alo hataęž‰taęž‰ hameke titi homeke homeke lo hopulolo hataęž‰ nunu piekeme. Kotaęž‰ kutu pieke hoki nanetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke tonumaęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± pi kini pea lemekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Mo hande Diosepenaęž‰ hameke tonutaęž‰ epelememe le ekitaęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke tapakemaęž‰ opitolo hataęž‰ mo kinimaęž‰ make mo ipikaęž‰ e pokaeyeke you haliwekimaęž‰ make taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme.
\v 17 Mo kinimaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kametonu ikaęž‰ nemanu mo donki manunaęž‰ hokinaęž‰ atula atula pea wia mo Keinani nane laęž‰kaęž‰la pupaęž‰e lae laataęž‰
\v 18 Ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ tapake make hatuku do ane laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰paęž‰paęž‰peke lae. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke paeyao ankulake otaęž‰ epeke kenke halaataęž‰ otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pake tupaęž‰ ne no hao pelinaęž‰ loaęž‰me lae.
\v 19 Kutupa make mo ikaęž‰ weteke tonu make ikaęž‰ hosiki wekiwandiki sunu make ikaęž‰ ateke make hatuku epolo peleme mo Idiepinaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ yolaęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰ alemanu mea penaęž‰ lae.
\v 20 Kuta ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ wia haleme alemanu minaęž‰paęž‰laasomaęž‰me laa hone kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke do Idiepi kenke paeyao siki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ epeke ale manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰eki yaęž‰lieke loaęž‰me lae leekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Koto leeke mo Dieikopenaęž‰ eiyeke tonumaęž‰taęž‰ mo leeke tupaęž‰ siki kone pimikime. Kutupa Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ mo kinimaęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰ kone mo maęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ yolaęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰ alemanu halaataęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ nolo pimiki ne make haleekeme.
\v 22 Kutupa Diosepemaęž‰ hameke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ mo topo akaęž‰manu make haleekepate pa Benisaminitaęž‰ 300 silipa mani make topo akaęž‰ paeyao yunki hataęž‰ haleekeme.
\v 23 Kuta ipikaęž‰ atekenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Idiepinaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke nemanu mo kiki yaapo donkinaęž‰ mu wia kutupa pa kiki yaapo donkimanu maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo potaęž‰naęž‰ nolo pieke widimanu make betedimanu make mandane nemanu make mu wiao tapaeyekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa mo ipikaęž‰ hameketonu penaęž‰ tapaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo potaęž‰naęž‰ hankiliki na yolaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Kotaęž‰ mo tapaketaęž‰ Idiepi minaęž‰paęž‰lao ikaęž‰ da nane ateke hayeke alenaęž‰ Keinani nane pemekeme.
\v 26 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Diosepetaęž‰ pa halaęž‰mee. Ipikitaęž‰ mo Idiepi kenke paeyaonaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ hali halaęž‰me lemekeme. Koto lemeke handa Dieikopetaęž‰ hone mataęž‰pa pulu no laęž‰mea pitaęž‰ mo weki tonumaęž‰ lemeke ekinaęž‰ hone na tulaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 27 Pate mo eiyeke tonumaęž‰ hande Diosepemaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ leekeeki paeyao ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ la halemekeme. Dieikopemaęž‰ koto lemekeeki opuolo pitaęž‰ pa mo Diosepemaęž‰ ipiki mulu epenaęž‰ tapaeyeke maęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ yolaęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰ alemanu hando haotaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ paa epeke hone wia pitiekeme.
\v 28 Kutu pitolo hataęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Keiyae. Doeki homeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yaka weki Diosepetaęž‰ paa hayaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ IĚ± aĚ±iĚ± na homeke hataęž‰ kone ipiki handolo polueke leekeme.
\c 46
\s1 Dieikope tapake Idiepi pemekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wia hayeke alemanu paeyao talo peaataęž‰ Biasiba nane peekeme. Koto patetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ateke Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni hau piekeme.
\v 2 Koto timbataęž‰ upamaęž‰ leke ale Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi alo alotaęž‰ Dieikopeo Dieikopeo leeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Wao. IĚ± do handaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Tekehalimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ nakaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰e. Idiepi poluekemaęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰peke. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ koto pate tapake tieke haenaęž‰ lolueke.
\v 4 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke yaapo oni Idiepi nane mandakenaęž‰ puaataęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ do kenke nane paa hatuku ipulueke. Koto patetaęž‰ mo Diosepe neke yaapo mandakenaęž‰ haenaęž‰ neke homilipikie laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Kotaęž‰ Dieikopetaęž‰ Biasiba minaęž‰paęž‰laeyekeme. Ipikaęž‰ weki tonumaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Idiepi kinimaęž‰ tapaeyeke maęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ yolaęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰ ale manunaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ ateke make ikaęž‰ hosiki wekiwandiki sunu make ikaęž‰ weteke tonu make pitaemekeme.
\v 6 Ikaęž‰ mo Keinani hataęž‰ mimiki alemanu paeyao make maęž‰naęž‰manu make mea Idiepi nane pemekeme. Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paeyao hatuku peekeme.
\v 7 Ipikaęž‰ wekitonu make ipikaęž‰ weki tonunaęž‰ wekitonu make ipikaęž‰ wandikitonu make ipikaęž‰ waneke tonunaęž‰ wandikitonu make paeyao hatuku peekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Mo Dieikope ameĚ±leĚ± oni Idiepi nane pemeke ipikaęž‰ tapaketaęž‰ mupeke weki Lubeni
\v 9 make Lubeninaęž‰ eiyeke tonu Haęž‰noko make Palu make Hesetoni make Kami makee.
\v 10 Kutupa Simiono make ipikaęž‰ wekitonu Diemuelo make Diamini make Ohadi make Diakini make Soha make Siolo makee. Do weki Siolotaęž‰ mo Keinani wandaęž‰naęž‰ wekie.
\v 11 Lipai make ipikaęž‰ weki tonutaęž‰ Kiesoni make Kohaęž‰di make Metati makee.
\v 12 Diuda make ipikaęž‰ weki tonutaęž‰ Sela make Petese make Sita makee. Diudanaęž‰ eiyeke yaapo Ea pitaęž‰ Onane yaapotaęž‰ Keinani haemeke tomaęž‰naęž‰ kone ambaęž‰ homepekeme.
\v 13 Isaka make ipikaęž‰ weki tonutaęž‰ Tola make Pua make Yope make Simitoni makee.
\v 14 Sebuloni make ipikaęž‰ weki tonutaęž‰ Setede make Elono make Dialieli makee.
\v 15 Do weki tonutaęž‰ oni Mesopoteimia hataęž‰ Liamaęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ mendiaeyeke weki tonue. Liamaęž‰ wandiki Daena make mendiaeyekeme. Koto paeyao siki yataęž‰polotaęž‰ Lia paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Dieikope ipikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke wekiwandiki paeyaotaęž‰ 33 yekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Kaęž‰de make ipikaęž‰ wekitonu Sepedoni make Haki make Siuni make Eseboni make Eti make Atodi make Ateli makee.
\v 17 Aęž‰sia make ipikaęž‰ weki tonutaęž‰ Imina make Isipa make Isipi make Betia make ikaęž‰ anaęž‰ Seta makee. Betianaęž‰ eiyeke yaapotaęž‰ Heba pitaęž‰ Malakiele yaapoe.
\v 18 Do 16 wekiwandikitaęž‰ mo hande Leibenimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ waneke Lia paęž‰taęž‰ haleeke pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandiki Silipamaęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ mendiaeyeke wekiwandikie.
\p 
\v 19 Dieikopenaęž‰ weteke Leisolomaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikope ipikaęž‰ weki Diosepe pitaęž‰ Benisamini yaapo mendiaeyekeme.
\v 20 Oni Idiepi kenketaęž‰ mo Heliopolisi da paęž‰taęž‰ yeni peao hayeke hali Podipitanaęž‰ waneke Aęž‰senaęž‰demaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ weki Maęž‰naęž‰saęž‰ pitaęž‰ Ipoteimi yaapo mondu wiayekeme.
\v 21 Benisamininaęž‰ eiyeke tonutaęž‰ Bela make Bekea make Aęž‰saęž‰bele make Keta make Naamani make Ehi make Otosi make Mupimi make Hupimi make Ada makee.
\v 22 Koto 14 weki tonutaęž‰ mo Leisolomaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ mendiaeyeke wekiwandikie.
\p 
\v 23 Daęž‰ni make ipikaęž‰ weki Husimi makee.
\v 24 Naęž‰petali make ipikaęž‰ wekitonu Diasiele make Kuni make Diesa make Silemo makee.
\v 25 Do watake hataęž‰ tapaketaęž‰ mo hande Leibenimaęž‰ waneke Leisolo haleeke pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandiki Bilihamaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke wekiwandikie.
\v 26 Kotaęž‰ mo Dieikopenaęž‰ eiyeke tonunaęž‰ weteke tonu na yataęž‰peke pa mo otaęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pieke wekitonu homeketaęž‰ paeyao 66 oni Idiepi nane pemekeme.
\v 27 Kutupa Diosepenaęž‰ oni Idiepi mendiaeyeke weki yaapo apaęž‰taasotaęž‰ mo Dieikopenaęž‰ oni Idiepi nane pu haemeke tapake paeyaotaęž‰ 70 yekeme.
\s1 Oni Idiepi nane Dieikope pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tapake haemekeeki
\p 
\v 28 Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ mo Kosene kenke paęž‰taęž‰ iki aęž‰pa mandaęž‰hande pinaęž‰ honke lenaęž‰yeke Diuda ambaęž‰la tapaeyekeme. Kutupa mo tapake opolo pemeketaęž‰
\v 29 Diosepemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hosimaęž‰ yolaęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰ ale pitulu pua Kosene kenke paęž‰taęž‰ ateke mandaęž‰hande pulu peekeme. Kutupa mo pate pua ateke mandaęž‰hande pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki bao mo atekenaęž‰ make yolaęž‰ mea hopulolo hataęž‰ eĚ± tieke lo hokulu peayekeme.
\v 30 Dieikopemaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paa haekaęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ laa handolo hataęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ametaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ homuluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yao halome leekeme.
\p 
\v 31 Kutupa Diosepemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ make mo atekenaęž‰ tapake paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo kini paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ oli Keinani haeme yaka kametonu make yaka apaęž‰naęž‰ tapake paeyao IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epelememe laa ambaęž‰la lolo polueke.
\v 32 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lolueke. Ikitaęž‰ sipisipimanu handeteke hao haleme haliweki make maęž‰naęž‰manu punu haleme haliweki make yalo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu make e wae alemanu make ikaęž‰ wia haleme alemanu paeyao make mea epelememe laa pua lolueke.
\v 33 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo kinimaęž‰ iki wi laęž‰ mea ikaęž‰ pu haleme ekitaęž‰ aleke kaęž‰taęž‰paęž‰ laa lotaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰
\v 34 mo hande ikaęž‰ apaęž‰meimaęž‰ pu haemeke tupaęž‰ koto ikaęž‰ haleme andusaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu handeteke hao halomaęž‰me laa lapaęž‰peke. Dupa lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Kosene kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hape laa laęž‰lieke leekeme. Diosepemaęž‰ dupiki pi leeke ekitaęž‰ mo Idiepi tapake paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ mo sipisipi handeteke haleme wandaęž‰hali iki ameĚ±leĚ± hamaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ kiaemeke ekinaęž‰ leekeme.
\c 47
\p 
\v 1 Kutupa Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ hameketonu paeyao yunki hataęž‰ hatuku mo kini paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Pua mo kini paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka apaęž‰ make yaka kametonu make mo Keinani hao ikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu make e wae alemanu make ikaęž‰ wia haleme alemanu paeyaosiki make mea epelememe. Ikitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ mo Kosene kenke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa halememe.
\v 2 Kutupa Diosepe ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hatuku epeeke hameke tonutaęž‰ mo kini hali paęž‰taęž‰ waleekeme.
\v 3 Mo kinimaęž‰ iki lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ eki e poko halemepe leekeme.
\p Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ apaęž‰meimaęž‰ piaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone sipisipi handeteke hao halomaęž‰ haliwekie.
\v 4 Kutupa mo Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ do teaęž‰ kitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoelaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ nikaęž‰ sipisipi manunaęž‰ ambu maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ do kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haluekemaęž‰yeke epolomaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ pilisio. Niki mo Kosene kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hamono waleke kie laa lemekeme.
\v 5 Koto lemeke mo kinimaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ nakaęž‰ apaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ kametonu make opolo epeleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰
\v 6 do Idiepi kenketaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ekie. Ikitaęž‰ mo Kosene kenke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ handa pitinaęž‰e. Kutupa mo iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ handa wiki haliweki maęž‰ndaęž‰ haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka maęž‰naęž‰manu make handeteke hawaenaęž‰ lapeke leekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Kutupa Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ Dieikope hatuku mo kini paęž‰taęž‰ pua waleeketaęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰ mo kinitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ bikinaęž‰ epeayekeme.
\v 8 Kutupa mo kinimaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ bapi ekipa kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Dieikopemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ± pa pomu lopolo hanotaęž‰ bapi paeyao 130 paelaęž‰me. Koto bapi manutaęž‰ mo yaka apaęž‰meimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ bapi eleke eleke pomu lopemeke tupaęž‰ make na handeke pa taęž‰taęž‰ dokaęž‰tikipiki takaęž‰lake bapimanu yaęž‰mee leekeme.
\v 10 Koto laa Dieikopemaęž‰ mo kini hali paęž‰taęž‰ paeyaaso epeaasaęž‰eki halaa minaęž‰paęž‰laeyekeme.
\v 11 Kutupa Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ mo kinimaęž‰ piaęž‰peke leeke tupaęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ ateke make hameketonu make mo Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ pitinaęž‰ laa mo Lamesese daoni nepoko nanemaęž‰ mo Idiepi kenkemanu paeyao lombeipiki otaęž‰ epeke kenkemanu haleekeme.
\v 12 Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ hameke tonu make mo ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ tapake paeyaosiki mo hosiki wekiwandikisunu make apaęž‰tao paeyaosiki ne anaęž‰naęž‰ haleekeme.
\s1 Mo teaęž‰ ki tieke
\p 
\v 13 Mo hande teaęž‰ kitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰pa wieke yalo hataęž‰ da paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ ne diaęž‰yekeme. Kutupa mo Idiepi wandaęž‰hali make Keinani wandaęž‰hali make paeyaosiki teaęž‰maęž‰ honkopu diaęž‰ yekeme.
\v 14 Kuta mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ widi hambaęž‰tiki pimikitaęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ mani paeyao meataęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ mea puaęž‰tiki piekeme.
\v 15 Kutupa mo Idiepi pitaęž‰ Keinani kenke yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ wieke mani paeyaosiki paeyeketaęž‰ mo Idiepi haliwekimaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Niki ne kie. Niki na homaamaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ make aĚ±iĚ± pie. Nikaęž‰ mani paeyaotaęž‰ otaęž‰ paelaęž‰me laa lemekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Koto lemeke Diosepemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu mea ipupee. Ikaęž‰ mani paeyao paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto ale topo pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki ne kuluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 17 Koto leeke mo tapakemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰manu mea Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ epemekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hosi maęž‰naęž‰manu make sipisipimanu make nanikosimanu make kaomanu make donkimanu make mea epemeke topo peataęž‰ ne haleekeme. Koto bapinaęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ manunaęž‰ topo pea ne halaęž‰tiki piekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Mo panake bapi maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Tiekeo. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ na aęž‰mbalumeke. Mo nikaęž‰ mani paeyaotaęž‰ paelaęž‰ make mo nikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ manutaęž‰ ambaęž‰ nakaęž‰ mime. Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ mo neke kiaęž‰peke alemanu maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ na ulaęž‰pate pa mo nikaęž‰ loke pitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ kenkemanu homeke neke paęž‰taęž‰ kiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 19 Niki homaamaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ make aĚ±iĚ± pie. Nikaęž‰ e manutaęž‰ na mopu yamono lae. Niki make nikaęž‰ kenke make nemaęž‰ topo pitolo hataęž‰ hambaęž‰e. Nikitaęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ tapake homono nikaęž‰ kenke make ipiki milieke. Niki paa daęž‰ta halo polomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone widimanu kie. Kutupa make nikaęž‰ e paęž‰taęž‰manu nokopomono wae alemanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ kie laa honke lemekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Kotaęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Idiepi kenke paeyaotaęž‰ kininaęž‰ eki winaęž‰ hambaeyekeme. Mo teaęž‰ kitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰pa wieke handa mo Idiepi tapake paeyaonaęž‰ kenketaęž‰ otaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ tapaenaęž‰ leeke ekimaęž‰ mo kenketaęž‰ kininaęž‰ eki homeke wiekeme.
\v 21 Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Idiepi kenke mandane nepokonaęž‰ kini pea pua mandane nepokonaęž‰ puataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 22 Kuta mo na hambeeke kenke homeketaęž‰ mo hande yeni peao hayeke tapakenaęž‰ eki yekeme. Pa ekipeke ikaęž‰ eki na tapaemeke ekitaęž‰ kinimaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ nolo pimiki nemanu anaęž‰naęž‰ halaęž‰tiki pieke pimikime.
\v 23 Diosepemaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki make ikaęž‰ kenke make mo kininaęž‰ hambalo ekitaęž‰ handelememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ e ninaęž‰ nokopolo peleme wae alemanu do handaęž‰pe.
\v 24 Kutu pulu pelemepate mo ne napeke mendiolotaęž‰ yunki hataęž‰naęž‰ homeke homeke lo hondo mo kini paęž‰taęž‰ halimikie. Mo paa wiliaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ wae wia make ikaęž‰ tapake ikaęž‰ nolo peleme eki miaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 25 Koto leeke mo tapakemaęž‰ hombo peaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki nakanaęž‰maęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ homolo pumaęž‰pate niki tambaęž‰ meleme. Tiekeo. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke hau pime. Koto ekinaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ tapakee.
\v 26 Koto ekinaęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ mo Idiepi kenkenaęž‰ lo pi witolotaęž‰ mo ne napeke mendiolo yunki hataęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo meataęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ eki yaęž‰naęž‰e laa lo pi wiekeme. Ame do make koto pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pa paęž‰laęž‰me. Pate mo yeni peao haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ kenkemanu homeketaęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ eki na wiekeme.
\s1 Dieikopenaęž‰ paeyaaso honke leekeeki
\p 
\v 27 Mo Isulai tapaketaęž‰ oni Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ mo Kosene da yu paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ hamoko haotaęž‰ wekiwandiki wopu mondu wimikime.
\v 28 Dieikopetaęž‰ mo Idiepi haenaęž‰taęž‰ bapi 17 paeyekeme. Kutupa otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ bapitaęž‰ 147 miekeme.
\v 29 Mo ipikaęž‰ homolo pieke nate teke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo epeeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eiyeke Diosepe wi laęž‰ mea alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kiki yaka paleke ankolopunaęž‰ wia hataęž‰ IĚ± do Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ na hoilueke laa keke pi laęž‰ wie.
\v 30 Pa ekipeke yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo yaka apaęž‰ ameda hoilaęž‰ alenaęž‰ hoilu poelenaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ± do Idiepi minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo tapake hoilaęž‰ alenaęž‰ tia pua hoiyaęž‰peke leekeme. Diosepemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ale tupaęž‰ otaęž‰ pulueke laa laęž‰ wiekeme.
\p 
\v 31 Dieikopemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pulueke laa keke pi laęž‰ wie leeketaęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ keke pi laęž‰ wieke handa Dieikopemaęž‰ koto pate ipikaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitolo hataęž‰ keiyae leekeme.
\c 48
\s1 Dieikopemaęž‰ Ipoteimi pitaęž‰ Maęž‰naęž‰saęž‰ yaapo epeayekeeki
\p 
\v 1 Hao hao pa nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ateke yeni hapa ulaęž‰me laa lemekeeki opu haotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki yaapo Maęž‰naęž‰saęž‰ pitaęž‰ Ipoteimi yaapo hatuku Dieikope handolo peekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa Dieikope paęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ weki Diosepetaęž‰ neke handolo aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me lemeke opu haotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ honkopu hao tia liao pitiekeme.
\v 3 Dieikopemaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Aneke Wele wopupiki Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ oli Keinani ulaęž‰ Lusu kenke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo aęž‰pa IĚ± epeaeyaęž‰me.
\v 4 IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ dupa leaęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ tutu paeyao siki haenaęž‰ yeke handa wekiwandiki wopu kulueke leaęž‰me. Kutupa do kenketaęž‰ ikaęž‰eki u tia pu haenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ pilipi wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki halueke leaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Dieikopemaęž‰ ombu alotaęž‰ Diosepeo. Mo IĚ± aĚ±iĚ± na epeke hano do Idiepi mendialaęž‰ nakaęž‰ weki yaapotaęž‰ yaka ekie. Ipoteimi pitaęž‰ Maęž‰naęž‰saęž‰ yaapotaęž‰ pa mo yaka weki Lubeni pitaęž‰ Simiono yaapo konemaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 6 Pate mo nakaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ mendilipi weki tonutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka weki diaęž‰ yaęž‰lieke. Koto weki tonumaęž‰taęž‰ mo Ipoteimi pitaęž‰ Maęž‰naęž‰saęž‰ yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipiliaęž‰ alemanu milimikie.
\v 7 IĚ±maęž‰ dupitolo ekitaęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ amaęž‰ Leisolonaęž‰ yeke pitolome. IĚ± mo Mesopoteimia hao epoaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ Epaęž‰taęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± aęž‰taęž‰ tieke peao homeaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ Epaęž‰taęž‰ pulaęž‰ potaęž‰ teaęž‰naęž‰ hoiyuaęž‰me leekeme. Koto Epaęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ametaęž‰ Betelehaęž‰maęž‰ lelememe.
\p 
\v 8 Dieikopemaęž‰ mo Diosepenaęž‰ weki yaapo hando hao alotaęž‰ Do weki yaapotaęž‰ epi yaapo yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Diosepemaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Do weki yaapotaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hano kaęž‰laęž‰ weki yaapoe leekeme.
\p Koto leeke Dieikopemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipiliki epealuekemaęž‰ dopate hatuku epoe leekeme.
\v 10 Dieikopetaęž‰ bapi tieke lieke ekiyalo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke anku pieke ekimaęž‰ wopu handaęž‰peke na yekeme. Kutupa Diosepemaęž‰ mo weki yaapo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku aęž‰pa haenaęž‰ laa mo weki yaapo hopula nunu piekeme.
\v 11 Dieikopemaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke paa handulueke hone na uaęž‰pate ametaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ weki yaapo kone pa handono laęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 12 Kutupa Diosepemaęž‰ mo weki yaapo Dieikopenaęž‰ palekenaęž‰ pitipi alenaęž‰ mea Dieikope pitiaęž‰ alenaęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 13 Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ Ipoteimitaęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰ nanemaęž‰ pitao Maęž‰naęž‰saęž‰taęž‰ popeke nanemaęž‰ pitaeyekeme.
\v 14 Pate Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki yaapo palaęž‰saęž‰ pu alu pea mo Ipoteimitaęž‰ wetepe weki kone ipikaęž‰ popeke nane kikitaęž‰ mo wekinaęž‰ ambokenaęž‰ wia kutupa mo ipikaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰ nane kikitaęž‰ mo mupeke wekinaęž‰ younaęž‰ wiekeme.
\v 15 Kutupa Diosepe epeaaso dupa leekeme.
\b
\q1 Mo hande yaka apaęž‰mei yaapo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke yaapomaęž‰ yeni pu haepeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do weki yaapo epeaenaęž‰e.
\q1 Ame do di sikinaęž‰ kone IĚ± hatuku aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiliki epeaenaęž‰e.
\q1 
\v 16 Mo hande tanda eleke eleke epeaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ meaęž‰tiki pia enisolomaęž‰ ipiliki epeaenaęž‰e.
\q1 Yaka biki make mo yaka apaęž‰mei yaapo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke yaaponaęž‰ biki make do weki yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ pa u tia pu haenaęž‰e.
\q1 Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ wekiwandiki wopu make mendia ipilikaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki wopu haenaęž‰e laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ atekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ popeke nane kikitaęž‰ mo Ipoteiminaęž‰ younaęž‰ wiaęž‰eki hando haotaęž‰ puki tandamaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ pao mea mo Maęž‰naęž‰saęž‰naęž‰ younaęž‰ winaęž‰yeke atekenaęž‰ kiki pao miekeme.
\v 18 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Apaęž‰o. Kutupa diaęž‰me. Dotaęž‰ mupeke weki yaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ popeke nane kikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ambokenaęž‰ wie laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Koto leekepate atekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi na opitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka wekio. IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulume. Maęž‰naęž‰saęž‰naęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ piliaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki make tapake tieke halo paęž‰laęž‰pate pa ipikaęž‰ wetepe nane hamekemaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ ankulaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ piliaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ tutu tiekemanu halieke.
\p 
\v 20 Koto ekinaęž‰ koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰ mo weki yaapo epeaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Isulai tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ Ipilikaęž‰ biki alo hataęž‰taęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ pi dupa lelimikie. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neketaęž‰ Ipoteimi pitaęž‰ Maęž‰naęž‰saęž‰ yaapomaęž‰ handaenaęž‰e laa lelimikie leekeme. Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰ Dieikopemaęž‰taęž‰ Ipoteimitaęž‰ Maęž‰naęž‰saęž‰naęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ leekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± homolo poloeki teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do handelepate Kodaęž‰taęž‰ neke yaapo hataęž‰ neketaęž‰ nakaęž‰ apaęž‰meinaęž‰ kenke nane paa hatuku pelieke.
\v 22 Mo IĚ±maęž‰ yaka bainasi pitaęž‰ aęž‰ndeli yaapomaęž‰ muaęž‰ hande Amo tapakenaęž‰ Sekeme kenke epeketaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kametonu paęž‰taęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa IĚ±maęž‰ neke kitolome leekeme.
\c 49
\s1 Dieikopenaęž‰ paeyaaso pimanu
\p 
\v 1 Dieikopemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekitonu wi laęž‰ mea alotaęž‰ IĚ± hopaęž‰lia pitaęž‰pe laa alotaęž‰ mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu IĚ±maęž‰ iki la kulukumaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\q1 
\v 2 Dieikopenaęž‰ eiyeke tonuo. Homeke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa taeyao pitaęž‰ opuaęž‰pe. Ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ Isulainaęž‰ pi opuaęž‰pe.
\b
\q1 
\v 3 Lubeni neketaęž‰ yaka mupeke weki make yaka honkopue. Kutupa IĚ± wekihali hataęž‰ mondolo mupeke wekie.
\q1 Yaka weki paeyao ankulake neketaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa honkopu wopu haleme.
\q1 
\v 4 Neketaęž‰ mo hande taęž‰tiki ipulaęž‰ ikalimaęž‰ handeleme. Pate neketaęž‰ mo titinaęž‰ halinaęž‰ biki na wilieke.
\q1 Pa ekipeke neketaęž‰ yaka wetepe wandaęž‰ yaapo pelia nakaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ da pandaęž‰ hoeyaeme.
\b
\q1 
\v 5 Simiono pitaęž‰ Lipai yaapotaęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰e. Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ale manumaęž‰ hali lu homaepeme.
\q1 
\v 6 Ipilikaęž‰ aęž‰mbaaso hataęž‰ pi pi lo halepeke IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ na apaęž‰taalueke. Kutupa ipilikaęž‰ pi hotilipi ale paęž‰taęž‰ make IĚ± na apaęž‰tiki pulueke.
\q1 Pa ekipeke ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mineke pankolo hataęž‰ haliweki lipime. Kutupa telepo alo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hali kao manutaęž‰ pa dolaęž‰pake peaepeme.
\q1 
\v 7 Ipilikaęž‰ mineke pankepe ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ paalaęž‰ pikieki yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ esihou pi winaęž‰e. Kutupa make ipilikaęž‰ lombeipiki mineke pankepe ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\q1 IĚ±maęž‰ ipilikitaęž‰ mo Isulai kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ putupaęž‰ alu pinaęž‰ lolueke. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ mo Isulai wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± kone taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pea halu pilipikie.
\b
\q1 
\v 8 Diuda neketaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kame tonumaęž‰ nakaęž‰ biki yeiyaęž‰ lalimikie. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki tapake manutaęž‰ make yolaęž‰ mea wia haleme. Nakaęž‰ kame tonumaęž‰taęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰punialimikie.
\b
\q1 
\v 9 Diudataęž‰ Laeonomaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ napeke ale liataęž‰ oni ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la pulaęž‰me.
\q1 Kiki anke tindipa tindipa pea polu pilaęž‰me. Paeyaomaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipiki penkilipaęž‰ tiatiki peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\q1 
\v 10 Diudamaęž‰taęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ minu halaęž‰ dolo miniki halieke. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ mondumaęž‰ piliaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ kini halimanu hoto paeyao handeteke hao hatiki pilimikie.
\q1 Tutu manumaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dakisi hambuluekemaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ mea aęž‰palimikie. Kutupa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ homu pitolo hataęž‰ pandaęž‰punialimikie.
\q1 
\v 11 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ panake donkitaęž‰ mo waini punaęž‰ endi baasaęž‰me. Pa pinaęž‰maęž‰ mo otaęž‰ epeke paeyao ankulake piki waini punaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\q1 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ akaęž‰ manutaęž‰ mo we au leke wepiki waini ikali paęž‰taęž‰ tandepo halaęž‰me.
\v 12 Mo waini ikali no haleke yalotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke we pupa paęž‰laęž‰mee. Ipikaęž‰ kaketaęž‰ andu no haleke yalotaęž‰ hake paęž‰laęž‰mee.
\b
\q1 
\v 13 Sebulonitaęž‰ dawala teaęž‰naęž‰ pelia haliekee. Ipikaęž‰ dawala teaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo kawasomanu epeke tupaęž‰ aęž‰pa pitinaęž‰ epeke alenaęž‰ yelieke. Ipikaęž‰ kilu tumbuao halo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ mo Saidoni da kenkenaęž‰ pua tombo pilieke.
\b
\q1 
\v 14 Isakataęž‰ mo hone na wiki donkimaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰ halie. Mo donki ipikitaęž‰ oni ipikaęž‰ hokinaęž‰ mendiaasaęž‰ numanu tukikinaęž‰ palaęž‰mbaęž‰ peliaęž‰laęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 15 Pate ipikaęž‰ handolotaęž‰ do hoto pilaęž‰ alenaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ do kenketaęž‰ otaęž‰ yole paęž‰laęž‰me alaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ tuluekemaęž‰ yeke ipikaęž‰ hoki pandaęž‰puniaasaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ some tupaęž‰ e pokenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.
\b
\q1 
\v 16 Daęž‰nitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ some halieke. Ikitaęž‰ mo hande mandane Isulai tapakemaęž‰ handilimikie.
\v 17 Daęž‰nitaęž‰ mo potaęž‰ teaęž‰naęž‰ pilaęž‰ keto wilieke. Mo potaęž‰ teaęž‰naęž‰ hali litaęž‰laęž‰ ketonaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Mo hosi hokinaęž‰ pita pulaęž‰ some ya handaęž‰liao lopenaęž‰yeke mo hosinaęž‰ kilolikinaęž‰ awaęž‰laęž‰ keto wilieke.
\b
\q1 
\v 18 Tekehalio nakaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaase eki yu wia halome.
\b
\q1 
\v 19 Kaęž‰daęž‰taęž‰ mo pake no haleme tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ lulu peliaęž‰pate paa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la mo tapake telipilieke.
\b
\q1 
\v 20 Aęž‰seanaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰taęž‰ epeke epeke nemanu opilieke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo kinimaęž‰ napeke yaęž‰laęž‰ epeke nemanu opalieke.
\b
\q1 
\v 21 Naęž‰petalitaęž‰ mo walekenaęž‰ pototo la pominaęž‰laęž‰ dia maęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke ikikimanu mondu halaęž‰me.
\b
\q1 
\v 22 Diosepetaęž‰ mo tunkulupa ulaęž‰ ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ halaęž‰ tikene donkimaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ mo yueli paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ panake hosi hali maęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 23 Ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ paalaęž‰piki tupaęž‰ aęž‰pa aęž‰ndaęž‰ pilimikie. Kutupa ikaęž‰ semoko aęž‰ndeli manumaęž‰ ipiki tolutia pomilimikie.
\v 24 Pate ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndelitaęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ kiki yaapo honkopu haowalaęž‰me. Koto hautaęž‰ mo Dieikopenaęž‰ Wele wopupiki Kodaęž‰naęž‰ honkopumaęž‰ piaęž‰me. Mo hande Sipisipi Handeteke Halaęž‰ some Isulainaęž‰ handeteke hao halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\b
\q1 
\v 25 Mo neke tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo Aneke Wele wopupiki Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke epeaasaęž‰me.
\q1 Oli ya nane lakomaęž‰ neke epeaasaęž‰me. Kutupa oni kenke oto nane opaęž‰laasaęž‰ ikali manumaęž‰ makee. Kaomanu wopu make wekiwandiki wopu make neke epeaasaęž‰me.
\q1 
\v 26 Widinaęž‰ kiliki pitaęž‰ palawasi yaapomaęž‰ make neke epeaasaęž‰me. Mo ambaęž‰ hao haemeke pote manumaęž‰ make neke epeaasaęž‰me. Kutupa mo pa u tia pu halaęž‰ elimanu paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ mo taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki epeke alemanu make neke paęž‰taęž‰ ipulaęž‰me. Do epeaasaęž‰ ekimanu paeyaotaęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ ambokenaęž‰ winaęž‰e. Mo ipikaęž‰ hamekemaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰ hali diaęž‰me laa maĚ±leke lilaęž‰ somenaęž‰ wenokonaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\b
\q1 
\v 27 Benisaminitaęž‰ mo hoke paalaęž‰ wopupiki tikene kikamaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Peliolo da kelepolotaęž‰ pa pitiki alemanu lia ombu naęž‰tiki pu halaęž‰me laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Koto mo hande Isulainaęž‰ 12 tapakee. Kutupa koto pi manutaęž‰ mo hande ateke Dieikopemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paeyaaso pi alo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki homeke homeke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ mandaęž‰ meaaso hataęž‰ leeke pie.
\s1 Dieikope homeeke hoimikieki
\p 
\v 29-30 Kutupa Dieikopemaęž‰ eiyeketonu takaęž‰lakemaęž‰ pi alo alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ametaęž‰ mo yaka wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao homolo pulume. Koto ekinaęž‰ dupaęž‰peke. IĚ±taęž‰ yaka apaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ mo Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ Maęž‰motenaęž‰ nate ipulaęž‰ nanemaęž‰ tilao Hidi hali Epotoninaęž‰ Maęž‰kaęž‰pila e paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ tikene da paęž‰taęž‰ hoiyaęž‰peke. Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ koto apaęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ hali hoitaęž‰laęž‰ lapaęž‰ winaęž‰ mo Epotoni paęž‰taęž‰ hambeeke ekimaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 31 Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰ weteke Seta yaapo hoilaęž‰me. Kutupa koto paęž‰taęž‰ ombutaęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke pitaęž‰ weteke Lepeka yaapo make hoilaęž‰me. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ maketaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ Lia hoiyuaęž‰me.
\v 32 Mo e make mo tikene da make mo Hidi tapake paęž‰taęž‰ hambeeke ekie. Koto paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± koto paęž‰taęž‰ hoiyaęž‰paęž‰peke laa leekeme.
\v 33 Dieikopemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eiyeketonu paęž‰taęž‰ manaęž‰manu halo paeyaotaęž‰ paa polu holaęž‰pakaęž‰naęž‰ homeekeme.
\c 50
\p 
\v 1 Diosepemaęž‰taęž‰ mo ateke toko manda lopa eĚ± alo hataęž‰ atekenaęž‰ leke popeleke nunu piekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ atekenaęž‰ loke tandaęž‰ paamaęž‰naęž‰ mulamula yankape laa leekeme.
\v 3 Koto mulamula yankaotaęž‰ mo Idiepi tapakemaęž‰ pu haemeke tupaęž‰ 40 natemanu pu paeyaemekeme. Kutupa mo Idiepi wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ 70 natenaęž‰ Dieikopenaęž‰ homaęž‰ wia pitimikime.
\p 
\v 4 Mo homaęž‰ wia pitimiki nate paeyeke handaataęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ mo kininaęž‰ mandane e pokaemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pilisio. Do pi mo kini paęž‰taęž‰ mea pupaęž‰e.
\v 5 Yaka apaęž‰ homuluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰taęž‰ mo Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ amu pea ulaęž‰ tikene da paęž‰taęž‰ pua hoiyaęž‰peke laataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiono leaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ pilisio. Yaka apaęž‰ hoilu pono lae. Kutupataęž‰ IĚ± paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipulueke laa lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Koto pi opua mo kinimaęž‰ hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mo nakaęž‰ pulueke laa laęž‰ wi tupaęž‰ nakaęž‰ apaęž‰ pua hoiyaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Koto leeke Diosepetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ hoilu peekeme. Mo kininaęž‰ handeteke haemeke haliweki paeyao make kininaęž‰ handeteke pilaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haleme tondiki haliweki make mo Idiepinaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ haliweki paeyao make Diosepe ameĚ±leĚ± pemekeme.
\v 8 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ wekiwandaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ hameketonu make mo ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ tapake paeyaosiki make ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± pemekeme. Pate ikaęž‰ hosiki wekiwandikisunu make ikaęž‰ sipisipimanu make nanikosimanu make kaomanu make homeke oni Kosene kenke paęž‰taęž‰ pa haemekeme.
\v 9 Mo hosimaęž‰ yolaęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰ alenaęž‰ pilaęž‰ haliweki make mo hosi hokinaęž‰ pilaęž‰ haliweki make Diosepe ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pemekeme. Motaęž‰ tapaketaęž‰ otaęž‰ tieke kiake yekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Mo tapake hande hoilu pimiki ale teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mo Diodaninaęž‰ nate ipulaęž‰ nanemaęž‰ tilao mo widi kilikinaęž‰ ambuku napeke yaapo putupa alu paęž‰laęž‰ hamaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ biki Atade opolo aęž‰paataęž‰ nate hokulunaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ homaęž‰ wia eĚ± lemekeme. Kutupa nate wataake hataęž‰naęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ homaęž‰ wia pitaęž‰ pu haemeke tupaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 11 Kutu pimikieki mo Keinani wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo Atade da homaęž‰ wimikieki handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Idiepi tapakemaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homaęž‰ wia pitaęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰piki hau tieke kiake pitelememe laa lemekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ koto patetaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Abele Miseteimi lemekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Dieikopenaęž‰ eiyeke tonumaęž‰taęž‰ atekemaęž‰ piaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeeki kone pimikime.
\v 13 Ipikaęž‰ toko tia puataęž‰ mo hande Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ hali lapaęž‰ winaęž‰yeke mo Keinani kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hande Hidi hali Epotoninaęž‰ e paęž‰taęž‰ wieke tikene da paęž‰taęž‰ mea pua lapaęž‰ pimikime. Koto tikene dataęž‰ mo Maęž‰motenaęž‰ nate ipulaęž‰ nanemaęž‰ Maęž‰kaęž‰pila da kenke paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 14 Diosepemaęž‰ ateke lapaęž‰ pea paeyeketaęž‰ hameke tonu make mo ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± homaęž‰ da pemeke tapake paeyao Idiepi nane laęž‰kaęž‰la paa pemekeme.
\s1 Diosepemaęž‰ hameke tonunaęž‰ puki epeayekeeki
\p 
\v 15 Mo ikaęž‰ ateke homeaęž‰ hoki nanetaęž‰ Diosepenaęž‰ hameke tonumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Diosepemaęž‰ hande nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pumaęž‰ hoke haunaęž‰ niki pa honditi pea mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ pumaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yenki mulueke laa potaęž‰manu wepiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ eki pumanaęž‰pe lemekeme.
\v 16 Koto ekinaęž‰ Diosepe paęž‰taęž‰ pi tapaaso alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ apaęž‰ homuluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰
\v 17 neke paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lotaęž‰ piomono leaęž‰me. Pilisio. Nakaęž‰ kame tonumaęž‰ neke luekemaęž‰ pimi ataęž‰kaęž‰ peake hautaęž‰ pa paeyaapeke leaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ pilisio. Ametaęž‰ mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ peake hau pumaęž‰eki pa paeyawapeke. Mo hande nakaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasomaęž‰ tapakemaęž‰ polomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me lemekeme. Diosepemaęž‰ koto pi mu haotaęž‰ eĚ± leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ hameke tonu aęž‰pa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ nakaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ nakaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasomaęž‰ tapake do handaęž‰e laa lemekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Pate Diosepemaęž‰ mo hameke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ yaka kone mo Kodaęž‰ topo peakaęž‰naęž‰ IĚ± hapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 20 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau pimipate Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto paa topo pea epekeeki au lalaęž‰me. Kutupa mo koto hau pimi ekitaęž‰ mo ame pa do haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ hao polu pelemeeki epeanoyeke paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 21 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰pekeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki make ikaęž‰ wekiwandiki make handeteke hao halueke leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo tapakemaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo tapakenaęž‰ puki liake koto homupiki pi manumaęž‰ epeayekeme.
\s1 Diosepenaęž‰ homeekeeki
\p 
\v 22 Diosepetaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ tapake ameĚ±leĚ± Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hao hayekeme. Kutupa bapi 110 haotaęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 23 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Ipoteiminaęž‰ wekiwandiki make ipikaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wekiwandiki make handaa homeekeme. Kutupa make mo ipikaęž‰ weki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Maęž‰naęž‰saęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke Meikanaęž‰ wekiwandiki mo ipikaęž‰ tapake paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambemekeeki handeekeme.
\v 24 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameketonu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ homolo poloeki teke paęž‰taęž‰ do yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke hao halieke. Kutupataęž‰ mo hande ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ make Aisaęž‰ke make Dieikope ameda paęž‰taęž‰ Do kenke kulueke laa laęž‰ wieke kenke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ iki hatuku pelieke laa leekeme.
\v 25 Kutupa Diosepemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ keke pi dupa lape laataęž‰ honke leekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ wipe laataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki koto kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka toko iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ mea polumekee laa laęž‰ wipee leekeme.
\v 26 Kotaęž‰ Diosepetaęž‰ 110 bapinaęž‰ Idiepi kenke paęž‰taęž‰ homeekeme. Mo tapakemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ na tandaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ mulamula anaęž‰naęž‰ yankao hali toko pambaęž‰laęž‰ bokisi paęž‰taęž‰ wimikime. 
